\id EXO - Asang Khongca Bible (2019)
\h EXODUS
\toc1 EXODUS
\toc2 EXODUS
\toc3 EXO
\mt1 EXODUS
\ip \it Exodus (ek-so-das) tiah kroek o. A thuih koehhaih loe, ‘tacawt’ tih haih ih ni. Hae cabu mah Israel caanawk Izip prae ah misong ohhaih thung hoi tacawthaih kawng to thuih. Mosi tapenhaih, Israel caanawk misong hoi loih thai hanah Sithaw mah kawbang maw toksak, tito hae cabu thungah amtueng. Mosi mah palunghahaih hoiah Faro lokcaekhaih im ah lok a thuih, praezaek ah khosakhaih hoi Israel caanawk praezaek thung hoiah a zaehhoih thai hanah palunghahaih to tawnh. Exodus cabu thungah loe Mosi hoi Faro lokramhaih kawng, tuipui kathim angkathaih kawng, Sinai mae phakhaih kawng, Sinai mae ah kaom hmuen hnetto kawng hoi kahni im sakhaih kawngnawk to hnuk thaih. Cabu thungah Sithaw kaminawk loe Sithaw lok hoi uk ih acaeng, to tih ai boeh loe Sithaw mah uk ih acaeng ah oh thai hanah, Sithaw angmah ni zaeh moe lak, tito kahoihah amtueng.\it*
\c 1
\s1 Israel qoenghaih hoi misong ah ohhaih
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt Genesis 46.8-27.\x*Jakob hoi Izip prae ah kalaem imthung takoh Israel kaminawk boih ih ahmin loe,
\v 2 Reuben, Simeon, Levi, Judah,
\v 3 Issakar, Zebulun, Benjamin,
\v 4 Dan, Naphtali, Gad hoi Asher.
\v 5 Jakob ih caanawk loe sangqum boih ah qui sarihto oh o; Joseph loe Izip prae ah oh hmaloe.
\v 6 Joseph hoi anih ih amyanawk, to nathuem ah kaom kaminawk doeh duek o boih.
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt Tsk 7.17.\x*Israel kaminawk loe caa sak o, paroeai pop o; pung o moe, thacak o parai.
\v 8 \x - \xo 1:8 \xt Tsk 7.18.\x*To pacoengah Joseph panoek ai kangtha siangpahrang mah Izip prae to uk.
\v 9 Anih mah angmah ih kaminawk khaeah, Khen oh, Israel kaminawk loe pop o parai moe, aicae pongah thacak o boeh.
\v 10 \x - \xo 1:10 \xt Tsk 7.19.\x*Angzo oh; nihcae hae palunghahaih hoiah tamet si, to tih ai nahaeloe nihcae loe pop o aep aep tih boeh; misa angtukhaih om nahaeloe, nihcae loe aicae ih misanawk khaeah ni athum o tih, aicae hae tuh o ueloe, aicae prae hae caeh o taak sut tih, tiah a thuih pae.
\v 11 To pongah nihcae pacaekthlaek hanah hmawsaeng ukkungnawk to suek o. Faro ih hmuenmae patunghaih vangpui, Pithom hoi Raamses to nihcae hanah saksak.
\v 12 Nihcae to paroeai pacaekthlaek o, toe nihcae loe pung o moe, qoeng o tahang aep aep; Israel kaminawk loe Izip kaminawk pongah paroeai palung boeng o.
\v 13 Izip kaminawk loe tahmenhaih tawn ai ah Israel caanawk to toksak o sak;
\v 14 Izip kaminawk mah nihcae to thlung kangphaek lakhaih, amlai long hmai qoenghaih hoi laikok thungah karai parai toknawk to a sak o sak moe, pacaekthlaek o.
\v 15 Izip siangpahrang mah nawkta omsakkung Hebru nongpata hnik, Shiphrah hoi Puah khaeah,
\v 16 Hebru nongpatanawk nawkta ohsak naah, kahoihah khen hoih loe, nongpa nahaeloe hum hoi roep ah, nongpata loe pathlung hoih, tiah a naa.
\v 17 Toe nawkta omsakkung Hebru nongpata hnik loe Sithaw to zit hoi pongah, Izip siangpahrang mah thuih ih lok baktih toengah sah hoi ai; caa nongpanawk to pathlung hoi.
\v 18 To pongah Izip siangpahrang mah nihnik to kawk moe, Tipongah hae tiah tok na sak hoi loe? Tipongah caa nongpanawk to na pathlung hoi loe? tiah a naa.
\v 19 Nawkta omsakkung hnik mah Faro khaeah, Hebru nongpatanawk loe Izip nongpatanawk baktiah om o ai; nihcae loe thacak o pongah, nawkta omsakkung pha ai naah nawkta tapen o ving boeh, tiah a naa hoi.
\v 20 Sithaw mah nawkta omsakkungnawk nuiah anghoehaih tawnh pongah, kami pung o moe, thacak o.
\v 21 Nawkta omsakkung hnik loe Sithaw to zit hoi pongah, Sithaw mah nihnik khaeah imthong hoi khosakhaih to paek.
\v 22 \x - \xo 1:22 \xt Tsk 7.19.\x*To naah Faro mah angmah ih kaminawk khaeah, Tapen caa nongpa to vapui thungah va o boih ah, nongpata loe pathlung o boih ah, tiah lok a paek.
\c 2
\s1 Mosi tapenhaih
\p 
\v 1 To nathuem ah Levi kami maeto mah, Levi canu to zu ah lak.
\v 2 \x - \xo 2:2 \xt Tsk 7.20; Heb 11.23.\x*A zu loe zokpom moe, caa nongpa maeto sak; a khet naah nawkta loe kranghoih parai; to pongah anih to khrah thumto thung a hawk.
\v 3 Toe hawk thai laek ai naah loe, sakrung kung hoiah sak ih thingkhong maeto a lak moe, tuipan hoi thing tangpri hoiah a bet caeng, nawkta to thingkhong thungah suek moe, vapui taengah a bangh.
\v 4 Anih ih tanuh mah kawbang maw oh, tiah panoek hanah, ahmuen kangthla hoiah khet.
\v 5 Faro canu loe tui amthluk hanah vapui ah caeh tathuk; to naah a tamna nongpatanawk loe tui taengah amkaeh o; anih mah tui taeng ih thingkhong to hnuk naah, a tamna nongpata maeto khaeah laksak.
\v 6 Anih mah thingkhong to paongh naah, nawkta to a hnuk; kaqah nawkta to a hnuk naah, tahmen moe, Hae loe Hebru nawkta bae hae, tiah a thuih.
\v 7 To naah anih ih tanuh mah Faro canu khaeah, Nang han nawkta khenzawnkung Hebru nongpatanawk to kang kawk pae han maw? tiah a naa.
\v 8 Anih mah, Caeh ah loe, kawk ah, tiah a naa. Tamna nongpata loe caeh moe, nawkta ih amno to kawk.
\v 9 Faro canu mah anih khaeah, Hae nawkta hae la ah loe, kai hanah com ah, atho kang paek han hmang, tiah a naa. To pongah nongpata mah nawkta to lak moe, khetzawn pae.
\v 10 \x - \xo 2:10 \xt Tsk 7.21.\x*Nawkta qoeng tahang naah loe, Faro canu khaeah caeh haih moe, anih ih capa ah angcoeng. Nongpata mah tui thung hoiah ka khuih, tiah a thuih pongah, anih to Mosi, tiah ahmin phui.
\s1 Mosi Midian prae ah cawnh
\p 
\v 11 \x - \xo 2:11 \xt Tsk 7.23-28.\x*\x - \xo 2:11 \xt Heb 11.24.\x*Mosi qoeng tahang naah loe, angmah ih acaeng nawkamyanawk toksakhaih ahmuen ah caeh; to nathuem ah nihcae loe karai parai tok a sak o, tiah Mosi mah hnuk; to naah Izip kami maeto mah anih ih nawkamya Hebru kami to boh.
\v 12 Ahnuk ahmaa a khet naah, mi doeh hnu ai pongah, Izip kami to a hum moe, savuet thungah aphum.
\v 13 Khawnbang ni hnetto naah a caeh let, to naah kangpanh Hebru kami hnik to a hnuk let bae; anih mah hmuen sah pazae kami khaeah, Tipongah nam pui Hebru kami to na boh loe? tiah a naa.
\v 14 To kami mah, Mi mah maw nang hae kaihnik ukkung hoi lokcaekkung ah suek? Izip kami na hum baktih toengah, kai doeh hum han nang patoem maw? tiah a naa. Mosi mah to lok to thaih naah tasoeh moe, Ka sak ih hmuen angphong tih boeh, tiah poek.
\v 15 \x - \xo 2:15 \xt Tsk 7.29; Heb 11.27.\x*Faro mah to kawng to thaih naah Mosi to hum hanah pakrong.
\p Toe Mosi loe Faro hmaa hoiah cawnh moe, Midian prae ah khosak; to ah tui khaw taengah anghnut.
\v 16 Midian prae ih qaima loe canu sarihto tawnh; anih ih canunawk loe tuidok hanah tui khaw ah caeh o moe, ampa ih tuunawk to tui a paek o.
\v 17 To naah tuu toep kaminawk to angzoh o moe, tuunawk to huih pae o ving; toe Mosi mah angdoet moe, nongpatanawk to angsak haih pacoengah, tuunawk to tui a naeksak.
\v 18 Tanglanawk loe ampa, Reuel khaeah amlaem o let, to naah ampa mah tikhoe vaihni loe nam laem o palang takan loe? tiah a naa.
\v 19 To naah nihcae mah, Izip kami maeto mah tuu toep kaminawk ih ban thung hoiah ang pahlong pongah kam laem o palang, anih mah ni tui dok moe, tuunawk doeh tui a paek, tiah a naa o.
\v 20 To naah anih mah a canunawk khaeah, Anih loe naa ah maw oh? Tikhoe na caeh o taak sut loe? Buhcaak han kawk o khae, tiah a naa.
\v 21 Mosi loe to kami ih im ah oh han koeh pongah, ampa mah a canu Zipporah to Mosi hanah zu ah paek.
\v 22 Zipporah mah anih han caa nongpa maeto sak pae, Minawk prae ah angvin ah ka oh, tiah a thuih pongah, Gershom, tiah ahmin phui.
\p 
\v 23 To tiah atue kasawk ah oh na thungah, Izip siangpahrang to duek; Israel kaminawk loe misong ah ohhaih to anghmawt o sut boeh pongah, a qah o; misong ah kaom kaminawk qahhaih lok to Sithaw mah thaih pae.
\v 24 \x - \xo 2:24 \xt Genesis 15.13,14.\x*Nihcae hanghaih lok Sithaw mah thaih naah, Abraham, Issak hoi Jakob khaeah sak ih lokkamhaih to a poek let.
\v 25 To pongah Sithaw mah Israel kaminawk to khet tathuk moe, nihcae han kho poek pae.
\c 3
\s1 Mosi hoi kabuk thing thung ih hmai
\p 
\v 1 Mosi loe Midian kami qaima, amsae Jethro ih tuu to toep pae; praezaek taeng ih mae ah tuunawk to a toep moe, Sithaw ih mae Horeb ahmuen ah a phak.
\v 2 \x - \xo 3:2 \xt Tsk 7.30-34.\x*To ah Angraeng ih van kami to hmai kangqong aqam kabuk thing thung hoiah anih khaeah angphong; Mosi mah khet naah, kabuk thing loe hmai angqong, toe thing loe hmai mah kangh ai tito a hnuk.
\v 3 To pongah Mosi mah, Tipongah kabuk thing loe hmai mah kang ai loe! Kalen parai kamtueng hmuen hae ka khet noek han, tiah a poek.
\v 4 To tiah kaom hmuen to Mosi mah caeh moe, khet, tiah Angraeng mah hnuk naah, Sithaw mah anih to aqam kabuk thing thung hoiah Mosi! Mosi! tiah kawk.
\v 5 Sithaw mah, Haeah anghnai hmah; na khokpanai to angkhring ah; nang doethaih ahmuen loe hmuenciim ah oh, tiah a naa.
\v 6 To pacoengah, Kai loe nam pa ih Sithaw, Abraham ih Sithaw, Issak ih Sithaw hoi Jakob ih Sithaw ah ka oh, tiah a naa. Mosi mah Sithaw khet han zit moe, a mikhmai to hawk ving.
\p 
\v 7 Angraeng mah, Izip prae ah kaom kai ih kaminawk patangkhanghaih to ka hnuk boeh; misong tawnkungnawk mah pacaekthlaek o pongah, a qah o haih lok to ka thaih boeh; nihcae palungsethaih to ka panoek.
\v 8 Izip kaminawk ban thung hoiah nihcae to ka pahlong moe, to prae thung hoiah ka zaeh pacoengah, tahnutui hoi khoitui longhaih, Kanaan prae, Hit, Amor, Periz, Hiv hoi Jebus kaminawk ohhaih prae ah caeh haih hanah, kang hum tathuk boeh.
\v 9 To pongah, khenah, Israel kaminawk qahhaih lok loe vaihi kai khaeah phak boeh; Izip kaminawk mah nihcae pacaekthlaekhaih doeh ka hnuk boeh.
\v 10 To pongah vaihi angzo ah, Izip prae thung hoiah kai ih kami, Israel caanawk to zaeh hanah, Faro khaeah kang patoeh han, tiah a naa.
\v 11 Toe Mosi mah Sithaw khaeah, Kai loe kawbaktih kami ah maw ka oh moe, Faro khaeah ka caeh pacoengah, Izip prae thung hoiah Israel kaminawk to ka zaeh han loe? tiah a naa.
\v 12 To naah Sithaw mah, Kai mah kang oh thuih han hmang! Hae loe nang, kang patoeh boeh, tiah angmathaih ah om tih; Kai ih kaminawk Izip prae thung hoi na zaeh pacoengah loe, hae mae nuiah Sithaw na bok o tih, tiah a naa.
\p 
\v 13 \x - \xo 3:13 \xt EXO 6.2,3.\x*Mosi mah Sithaw khaeah, Israel kaminawk khaeah ka caeh moe, nihcae khaeah, nangcae ampanawk ih Sithaw mah nangcae khaeah kai ang patoeh, tiah ka thuih pae naah, nihcae mah kai khaeah, Anih ih ahmin loe mi aa? tiah na dueng o nahaeloe, kawbang maw ka thuih pae han loe? tiah a naa.
\v 14 \x - \xo 3:14 \xt Lph 1.4,8.\x*Sithaw mah Mosi khaeah, \bd KAI LOE KAI NI\bd*, tiah Israel kaminawk khaeah thui paeh; KAI, tiah ahmin kaom mah, nangcae khae ah kai ang patoeh, tiah thui paeh, tiah a naa.
\v 15 To pacoengah Sithaw mah Mosi khaeah, Israel kaminawk khaeah, Nam panawk ih Angraeng Sithaw, Abraham Sithaw, Issak Sithaw hoi Jakob Sithaw mah nangcae khaeah kai ang patoeh, hae loe dungzan ah kaom Kai ih ahmin ah oh, angzo han koi kaminawk boih mah pahnet thaih han ai ih ahmin ah oh, tiah a thuih, tiah thui paeh, tiah a naa.
\v 16 Caeh ah, Israel kacoehtanawk to nawnto pakhueng ah loe nihcae khaeah, Nam panawk ih Angraeng Sithaw, Abraham, Issak hoi Jakob ih Sithaw to kai khaeah angphong moe, nangcae khaeah kang paqaih, Izip prae ah nangcae nuiah a sak o ih hmuen ka hnuk boeh;
\v 17 Izip prae patangkhanghaih thung hoiah nangcae to kang zaeh moe, Kanaan, Hit, Amor, Periz, Hiv hoi Jebus kaminawk ih prae, tahnutui hoi khoitui longhaih prae thungah kang caeh o haih han, tiah lok ka thuih boeh, tiah thui paeh, tiah a thuih, tiah a naa.
\v 18 Israel kacoehtanawk mah na lok to tahngai o tih; nang hoi Israel kacoehtanawk Izip siangpahrang khaeah caeh oh loe, anih khaeah, Hebru Angraeng Sithaw mah kaicae hae a tongh boeh; kaimacae ih Angraeng Sithaw khaeah, angbawnhaih ka sak o hanah, ni thumto thung praezaek ah na caehsak ah, tiah thui paeh.
\v 19 Toe Izip siangpahrang loe kalen parai thacakhaih hnu ai ah loe, nangcae to caehsak mak ai, tito ka panoek.
\v 20 To pongah ban ka payangh moe, Izip prae thungah dawnrai hmuennawk to ka sak boih han, to tiah prae to ka thuitaek han; to pacoengah ni Izip siangpahrang mah na caeh o sak vop tih.
\v 21 \x - \xo 3:21 \xt EXO 12.35,36.\x*Izip kaminawk mah hae kaminawk palung o thai hanah, tok ka sak han; to naah ni na tacawt o naah bangkrai ah na tacawt o mak ai;
\v 22 nongpata boih mah a imtaeng kami, a im ah kaom nongpatanawk hanah phoisa, sui hoi khukbuennawk to hni o ueloe, na capanawk hoi na canunawk to abuen o sak tih; to tiah Izip kaminawk ih hmuennawk to na la pae o tih, tiah a naa.
\c 4
\s1 Mosi tanoekhaih
\p 
\v 1 Mosi mah, Toe, khenah, nihcae mah kai na tang o ai moe, ka lok tahngai ai ah, nang khaeah Angraeng angphong ai, tiah na naa o nahaeloe? tiah a naa.
\v 2 To naah Angraeng mah, anih khaeah, Na ban ah timaw na tawnh? tiah a naa. Anih mah, Cunghet, tiah pathim pae.
\v 3 Angraeng mah, Long ah va tathuk ah, tiah a naa. Mosi mah cunghet to long ah vah tathuk naah, pahui ah angcoeng, to naah Mosi mah cawnhtak ving.
\v 4 Angraeng mah, anih khaeah, Na ban to payangh loe, tamai ah naeh ah, tiah a naa. To pongah Mosi mah a ban to payangh moe, pahui to naeh, to naah a ban pongah cunghet ah angcoeng let.
\v 5 Angraeng mah, To tiah na sak nahaeloe ampanawk ih Angraeng Sithaw, Abraham Sithaw, Isaak Sithaw, Jakob Sithaw loe nang khaeah angphong tangtang, tiah tanghaih tawn o tih, tiah a naa.
\v 6 To pacoengah Angraeng mah, Vaihi laihaw thungah na ban to tapawh ah, tiah a naa. Mosi mah laihaw thungah a ban to tapawh; khenah, a ban azuh let naah, a ban loe dantui baktih kanglung, ngansae ah angcoeng.
\v 7 Laihaw thungah na ban to tapawh let ah, tiah a naa. To pongah Mosi mah laihaw thungah a ban to tapawh let; a ban to lak let naah, khenah, a ban loe angmah ih ngan baktih toengah oh let.
\v 8 To pacoengah Angraeng mah, Nang to tang o ai moe, kaom hmaloe ih angmathaih to tang o ai cadoeh, hnukkhuem ih angmathaih loe nihcae mah tang o tih.
\v 9 Toe vai hnetto haih angmathaih to ni nihcae mah tang o ai moe, na lok to tahngai o ai nahaeloe, Vapui ih tui to doh ah loe, karoem long ah krai ah; to naah vapui ah na dok ih tui to karoem long nuiah athii ah angcoeng tih, tiah a naa.
\p 
\v 10 Mosi mah Angraeng khaeah, Aw Angraeng, kai loe lok ka thui thai ai; canghniah, na tamna khaeah lok nang thuih pacoengah doeh, lok hae ka thui thai ai; ka lok hae tongaah moe, lok ka pae thai ai, tiah a naa.
\v 11 Angraeng mah anih khaeah, Kami ih pakha, to tih ai boeh loe lokaa hoi naapang, to tih ai boeh loe kamtueng mik hoi mikmaeng to mi mah maw sak? Kai, Angraeng mah na ai maw sak?
\v 12 To pongah vaihi caeh ah, na pakha ah Ka oh moe, timaw thuih han tito kang patuk han, tiah a naa.
\v 13 Toe Mosi mah, Aw Angraeng, minawk kalah patoeh halat ah, tiah a naa.
\v 14 To naah Mosi nuiah Angraeng palungphui moe, Levi kami, nam ya Aaron oh maw? Anih loe lokthuih thaih, tiah ka panoek. Khenah, anih loe nang tongh hanah loklam ah angzoh li vop; anih mah nang to hnuk naah anghoe tih.
\v 15 Anih hoi lok aram hoiah loe, a thuih han koi lok to thui paeh; kai loe na pakha hoi anih ih pakha ah ka oh moe, na sak hoi han koi hmuen to kang patuuk han.
\v 16 Anih loe kaminawk hmaa ah nang han lokthui kami ah om tih; anih loe na pahni zuengah om ueloe, nang doeh anih han Sithaw zuengah om tih.
\v 17 Dawnrai angmathaih hmuennawk na sak hanah, hae cunghet hae na ban ah sin ah, tiah a naa.
\s1 Izip prae ah Mosi amlaem
\p 
\v 18 Mosi loe amsae Jethro khaeah amlaem moe, anih khaeah, Izip prae ah kaimah ih nawkamyanawk hing o vop maw, tiah khet hanah, na caehsak raeh, tiah a naa. Jethro mah, Lunghoihta hoi caeh ah, tiah a naa.
\v 19 Midian prae ah oh naah, Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah, Izip prae ah caeh let ah, na hinghaih pakrong kaminawk loe duek o boih boeh, tiah a naa.
\v 20 To pongah Mosi mah a zu hoi a capanawk to kawk moe, Laa hrang pongah angthuengsak, Sithaw ih cunghet to a ban ah sin moe, Izip prae ah amlaem let.
\p 
\v 21 Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah, Izip prae ah nam laem let naah, Na ban ah kang suek ih dawnrai hmuennawk to Faro hmaa ah sah paeh; toe anih mah Israel kaminawk caehsak han ai ah, anih ih palung to kam taksak han.
\v 22 To naah Faro khaeah, Angraeng mah, Israel loe ka capa hoi ka calu ah oh;
\v 23 \x - \xo 4:23 \xt EXO 12.29.\x*Ka capa mah ka tok to sak hanah, prawt ah, tiah lok kang thuih; to tiah na prawt ai nahaeloe, na capa, na calu to ka hum han, tiah thui paeh, tiah Mosi khaeah a thuih pae.
\p 
\v 24 A ohhaih im loklam ah caeh naah, Angraeng mah Mosi to hnuk moe, anih to hum hanah patoem.
\v 25 Toe Zipporah mah thlung kanoe to lak moe, a capa ih tangzat hin to aah pacoengah, Mosi khokkung ah akuep moe, Nang loe athii kalong ka sava ah na oh, tiah a naa.
\v 26 To pongah Angraeng mah Mosi to loihsak; tangzat hin aahhaih athii pongah ni, a zu mah nang loe athii kalong ka sava ah na oh, tiah a naa.
\p 
\v 27 Angraeng mah Aaron khaeah, Mosi tongh hanah praezaek ah caeh ah, tiah a naa. To pongah anih loe caeh, Mosi to Sithaw mae ah tongh moe, anih to mok.
\v 28 To naah Mosi mah Aaron khaeah, Anih patoehkung Angraeng mah thuih ih loknawk boih, a sak han koi dawnrai hmuennawk to a thuih pae boih.
\v 29 Mosi hoi Aaron loe caeh hoi moe, Israel kacoehtanawk to kawk boih pacoengah, nawnto amkhuengsak.
\v 30 Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah thuih ih loknawk to Aaron khaeah a thuih pae boih, kaminawk hmaa ah dawnrai hmuennawk doeh a sak pae.
\v 31 To naah kaminawk mah tang o; Angraeng loe Israel kaminawk khet hanah angzoh, tiah panoek o moe, nihcae patangkhanghaih to a hnuk pae, tiah a thaih o naah, nihcae mah long ah lu akuephaih hoiah bok o.
\c 5
\s1 Faro mah Israel pacaekthlaekhaih
\p 
\v 1 To pacoengah Mosi hoi Aaron loe Faro khaeah caeh hoi moe, Israel Angraeng Sithaw mah, Praezaek ah kai khae poihsak o hanah, kai ih kaminawk to tacawtsak ah, tiah a thuih, tiah a naa hoi.
\v 2 Faro mah, Angraeng ih lok to ka tahngaih moe, Israel kaminawk ka prawt hanah to Angraeng loe mi aa? Angraeng to ka panoek ai, Israel kaminawk doeh ka prawt mak ai, tiah a naa.
\v 3 To naah nihnik mah, Hebru kaminawk ih Sithaw mah kaihnik hae tongh boeh; ni thumto caehhaih praezaek ah, kaimacae ih Angraeng Sithaw khaeah, angbawnhaih sak hanah, na caeh o sak ah; to tih ai nahaeloe kaicae nuiah nathaih maw, to ai boeh loe sumsen hoiah maw na thuitaek moeng tih, tiah a naa hoi.
\v 4 Toe Izip siangpahrang mah nihnik khaeah, Tih hanah hae kaminawk toksak nam pra hoi sak loe? Na sak hoi ih tok to mah sah hoih, tiah a naa.
\v 5 To pacoengah Faro mah, Khenah, prae thungah kami paroeai pop o, toe nihcae khaeah toksak han ai ah na thuih pae hoiah, tiah a naa.
\v 6 To na niah Faro mah tamna khenzawn kaminawk hoi ukkungnawk khaeah, hae tiah lokthuih pae;
\v 7 amlai long to hmaiqoeng hanah, canghni ah na paek o ih baktiah, kaminawk hanah caphaeh to paek o hma lai ah; angmacae koehah caphaeh to akhuih hanah caeh o nasoe.
\v 8 Toe amlai long hmaiqoenghaih tok loe canghni ah sak ih baktih toengah nihcae to sahsak ah; tamsi o sak hmah; nihcae loe thaset o pongah ni, Sithaw khaeah angbawnhaih sak hanah, na caehsak ah, tiah a hang o.
\v 9 Toksak panki o moe, amsawn loknawk to a tang o han ai ah, nongpanawk to tok karai paek ah, tiah a naa.
\p 
\v 10 To naah tamna khenzawn kaminawk hoi ukkungnawk loe caeh o moe, kaminawk khaeah, Faro mah, nangcae caphaeh paek han ai ah thuih boeh.
\v 11 Caeh oh loe nangmacae koehah caphaeh to pakrong oh; toe toksak tamsi o sak hmah, tiah a thuih, tiah a naa.
\v 12 To pongah kaminawk loe Izip prae ah caeh o moe, caphaeh zuengah anghnoeng to pakrong hanah, Izip prae thung boih ah caeh o.
\v 13 Tamna khenzawn kaminawk mah nihcae to mongh aep aep; caphaeh oh nathuem ah ni thokkruek na sak o ih tok baktih toengah, pacoeng hanah tok to sah oh, tiah a naa.
\v 14 Faro ih tamna khenzawn kaminawk mah, zaehoikung ah suek ih Israel kaminawk khaeah, Tipongah cangduem hoi vaihni na sak o ih, amlai long loe canghni ah na sak o ih zetto pha ai loe? tiah a naa o.
\p 
\v 15 To naah Israel zaehoikungnawk loe Faro khaeah caeh o moe, Tipongah na tamnanawk hae tih khoek to nang pacaekthlaek loe?
\v 16 Na tamnanawk hanah caphaeh paek ai to mah, khenah, ukkungnawk loe kaicae khaeah amlai long sak hanah lok ang thuih o moe, na tamnanawk to boh o; zaehaih loe nangmah ih kaminawk nuiah ni oh, tiah a naa o.
\v 17 Toe Faro mah, Tha na set o, tha na set o! To pongah ni, Angraeng khaeah angbawnhaih sak hanah na caehsak ah, tiah na thuih o.
\v 18 To pongah vaihi caeh oh loe, tok to sah oh; caphaeh to kang paek o mak ai boeh; toe amlai long loe na sak o zetto sah o toengtoeng ah, tiah a naa.
\v 19 Nito thung sak ih amlai long to tamsi o sak hmah, tiah thuih ih lok to Israel kaminawk mah thaih o naah, raihaih a tongh o boeh, tiah panoek o.
\v 20 Faro khae hoi amlaem o naah, loklam ah nihcae tongh han kazing, Mosi hoi Aaron to a hnuk o;
\v 21 nihnik khaeah, Angraeng mah nang hnik to khen nasoe loe, lokcaek nasoe; Faro hoi anih ih toksah tamnanawk mah kaicae hae panuet moe, kaicae hae sumsen hoi hum hanah, na sak hoi boeh, tiah a naa o.
\s1 Pahlong han Sithaw lokkamhaih
\p 
\v 22 Mosi loe Angraeng khaeah amlaem moe, Angraeng, tipongah hae kaminawk khaeah raihaih na phaksak loe? Tih pongah kai nang patoeh loe?
\v 23 Na hmin hoi Faro khaeah lokthuih han ka caeh kruek, anih mah hae kaminawk khaeah raihaih a phaksak; nangmah ih kaminawk hae na pahlong ai, tiah a naa.
\c 6
\p 
\v 1 To naah Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah, Vaihi loe Faro khaeah ka sak han ih hmuen to na hnuh hoi tih boeh; ka ban thacakhaih rang hoiah nihcae to tacawtsak ueloe, ka ban thacakhaih rang hoiah a prae thung hoiah nihcae to haek tih boeh, tiah a naa.
\p 
\v 2 \x - \xo 6:2 \xt Genesis 17.1; 28.3; 35.11; EXO 3.13-15.\x*Sithaw mah Mosi khaeah, Kai loe Angraeng ah ka oh;
\v 3 Abraham, Issak hoi Jakob khaeah, Lensawk Sithaw ah kang phong pae; toe ka hmin JEHOVAH hoiah nihcae khaeah kang phong pae ai.
\v 4 Nihcae angvin ah oh o haih, nihcae khaeah Kanaan prae to paek hanah, nihcae hoi lokmaihaih ka sak boeh.
\v 5 To pacoengah, Izip kaminawk mah tamna ah suek o ih, Israel kaminawk hanghaih lok to ka thaih naah, ka sak ih lokmaihaih to ka poek.
\v 6 To pongah Israel kaminawk khaeah, Kai loe ANGRAENG ah ka oh; Izip kaminawk ih hmuenzit phawhhaih thung hoiah nangcae to kang loih o sak han; nihcae ih tamna ah ohhaih thung hoiah kang loih o sak moe, ban ka payangh pacoengah, thacak lokcaekhaih hoiah nangcae to kang loih o sak han.
\v 7 Kami maeto ah kaimah khaeah kang lak o han, Kai loe nangcae ih Sithaw ah ka oh han; to naah Kai loe nangcae ih Angraeng Sithaw, Izip kaminawk hmuenzit phawhhaih thung hoi zaehoikung ah ka oh, tiah na panoek o tih.
\v 8 Kai mah Abraham, Issak hoi Jakob khaeah ban ka payangh moe, paek han lokkam ih prae thungah, kang caeh o sak han; to prae to nangcae hanah qawk ah kang paek han; Kai loe Angraeng ah ka oh, tiah thui paeh, tiah a naa.
\v 9 Hae lok hae Mosi mah Israel kaminawk khaeah thuih pae; toe palungboeng o, tamna ah ohhaih nung parai pongah tahngai pae o ai.
\p 
\v 10 To pacoengah Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah,
\v 11 a prae thung hoi Israel kaminawk tacawtsak hanah, Faro khaeah caeh ah loe, thui paeh, tiah a naa.
\v 12 Toe Mosi mah Angraeng khaeah, Khenah, Israel kaminawk mah mataeng doeh ka lok hae tahngai o ai nahaeloe, lok tongaah kai ih lok cae loe kawbang maw Faro mah na tahngai pae tih? tiah a naa.
\v 13 Angraeng mah Mosi hoi Aaron khaeah, Israel kaminawk hoi Izip siangpahrang Faro kawng to thuih pae, Israel kaminawk Izip prae thung hoi tacawt haih hanah nihnik khaeah lok a paek.
\s1 Israel kaminawk anghumhaih
\p 
\v 14 Hae kaminawk loe acaeng lu koek ah oh o; Israel calu Reuben ih caanawk loe Hanok, Pallu, Hezro hoi Karmi; hae kaminawk loe Rueben ih imthung takoh ah oh o.
\v 15 Simeon ih capanawk loe Jemuel, Jamin, Ohad, Jachin, Zohar hoi Kanaan tanuh ih capa Shaul cae hae ni; hae kaminawk loe Simeon ih imthung takoh ah oh o.
\v 16 \x - \xo 6:16 \xt NAM 3.17-20; 26.57,58; 1 Dung 6.16-19.\x*Levi caanawk ih ahmin loe Gershon, Kohath hoi Merari; Levi loe saning cumvai qui thum, sarihto hing.
\v 17 Gershon capanawk hoi imthung takoh kaminawk loe Libni hoi Shimi.
\v 18 Kohath ih capanawk loe Amram, Izhar, Hebron hoi Uzziel; Kohath loe saning cumvai qui thum, thumto hing.
\v 19 Merari ih capa hnik loe Mahli hoi Mushi; hae kaminawk loe Levi imthung takoh ah oh o.
\v 20 Amram mah ampa ih tanuh Jokhebed to zu haih moe, anih mah Aaron hoi Mosi to a sak pae; Amram loe saning cumvai qui thum, sarihto hing.
\v 21 Izhar capanawk loe Korah, Nepheg hoi Zikri.
\v 22 Uzziel capanawk loe Mishael, Elzaphan hoi Zithri.
\v 23 Aaron mah Aminadab canu, Nashon ih tanuh, Elisheba to zu ah lak moe, anih mah Nadab, Abihu, Eleazar hoi Ithamar to sak.
\v 24 Korah ih capanawk loe Assir, Elkanah hoi Abiasaph; hae kaminawk loe Korah imthung takoh ah oh o.
\v 25 Aaron capa Eleazar mah Putiel ih canu maeto zu ah lak moe, anih mah Phinehas to sak pae; hae kaminawk loe Levi kaminawk ih acaeng ah oh o.
\p 
\v 26 Angraeng mah Aaron hoi Mosi khaeah, Israel kaminawk ih misatuh kaminawk to Izip prae thung hoi tacawt haih ah, tiah a naa.
\v 27 Nihnik loe Izip siangpahrang Faro khaeah Israel kaminawk Izip prae thung hoi tacawt haih hanah thuikung ah oh hoi; nihnik loe Mosi hoi Aaron hae ni.
\s1 Mosi zuengah Aaron mah lokthuih
\p 
\v 28 Angraeng mah Izip prae thungah, Mosi khae lokthuih pae naah,
\v 29 Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah, Kai loe Angraeng ah ka oh; kang thuih ih loknawk boih Izip siangpahrang Faro khaeah thui paeh, tiah a naa.
\v 30 Toe Mosi mah Angraeng khaeah, Khenah, kai loe lok tongaah kami ah ka oh pongah, kawbang maw Faro mah ka lok hae tahngai tih? tiah a naa.
\c 7
\p 
\v 1 To naah Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah, Khenah, Faro hmaa ah Sithaw baktiah kang suek boeh, nam ya Aaron loe nang ih tahmaa ah om tih.
\v 2 Kang paek ih loknawk boih to thui ah; Faro mah a prae thung hoi Israel kaminawk tacawtsak hanah, nam ya Aaron mah Faro khaeah lok na thui pae tih.
\v 3 \x - \xo 7:3 \xt Tsk 7.36.\x*Faro ih palung to kam taaksak moe, Izip prae thungah dawnrai hmuen hoi angmathaih to ka pungsak han.
\v 4 To pongah Faro mah na lok to tahngai mak ai; to pacoengah Izip nuiah ban ka phok moe, thacak lokcaekhaih hoiah kaimah ih misatuh kaminawk hoi Israel caanawk to Izip prae thung hoi ka tacawtsak han.
\v 5 Izip nuiah ban ka payangh moe, nihcae salak hoiah Israel kaminawk to ka zaehhoih naah, Izip kaminawk mah kai loe Angraeng ni, tito panoek o tih.
\v 6 Angraeng mah paek ih lok baktih toengah Mosi hoi Aaron mah sak hoi.
\v 7 Faro khaeah lokthuih hoi naah, Mosi loe saning qui tazetto oh boeh moe, Aaron loe saning qui tazet, thumto oh boeh.
\s1 Cunghet to pahui ah angcoeng
\p 
\v 8 Angraeng mah Mosi hoi Aaron khaeah,
\v 9 Faro mah nang hnik khaeah lokthuih naah, anih mah Dawnrai hmuen to sah hoi ah, tiah na thui nahaeloe, Aaron khaeah, Nangmah ih cunghet to la ah loe, Faro hmaa ah va ah, tiah thui paeh; to naah cunghet to pahui ah angcoeng tih, tiah a naa.
\v 10 To pongah Mosi hoi Aaron loe Faro khaeah caeh hoi moe, Angraeng mah thuih ih lok baktih toengah a sak hoi; Aaron mah angmah ih cunghet to Faro hoi a tamnanawk hmaa ah vah pae; to naah cunghet to pahui ah angcoeng.
\v 11 Faro mah angmah ih palungha kaminawk hoi lungh aah kop kaminawk to kawk: miklet kop kaminawk mah doeh miklet kophaih hoiah a sak o toeng.
\v 12 Nihcae mah angmacae ih cunghet to vah o naah, pahui ah angcoeng boih; toe Aaron ih cunghet mah nihcae ih cunghet to pa-aeh pae boih.
\v 13 Toe Angraeng mah thuih ih lok baktih toengah, Faro loe palungthah moe, nihnik mah thuih ih lok to tahngai pae ai.
\s1 Tui athii ah angcoeng
\p 
\v 14 Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah, Faro loe palungthah pongah, kaminawk caehsak han koeh ai.
\v 15 Khenah, Faro loe khawnthaw ah tui ohhaih ahmuen ah caeh, to naah anih khaeah caeh hoih; anih angzo ai naah vapui taengah zing hoi ah loe, pahui ah kangcoeng na ban ih cunghet to sin hoih.
\v 16 To naah anih khaeah, Hebrunawk ih Angraeng Sithaw mah nang khaeah lokthuih han ih ang patoeh; praezaek ah kai bok o hanah, kai ih kaminawk to tacawtsak ah, tiah ang thuisak, toe vaihi khoek to lok na tahngai ai.
\v 17 \x - \xo 7:17 \xt Lph 16.4.\x*Angraeng mah hae tiah thuih; Ka ban ah kaom cunghet hoi vapui to ka boh moe, athii ah angcoeng naah, kai loe Angraeng ni, tito na panoek tih.
\v 18 To naah vapui thung ih tahnganawk to dueh o boih ueloe, vapui to ahmui sae tih; Izip kaminawk loe tui nae o thai mak ai, tiah a thuih, tiah ang thuihsak, tiah a naa.
\v 19 Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah, Aaron khaeah, Cunghet to lak hanah thui paeh loe, Izip prae ih tuinawk, vacongnawk hoi vapuinawk, kangbuem tuinawk hoi pauem ih tuilinawk nuiah na ban to payangh ah, tuinawk loe athii ah angcoeng o boih tih; Izip prae thung boih ah athii to om ueloe, thing sabae hoi thlung hoiah sak ih laom thung khoek to athii to om tih, tiah thui paeh, tiah a naa.
\p 
\v 20 Angraeng mah thuih ih lok baktih toengah, Mosi hoi Aaron mah sak hoi; Faro hoi anih ih tamnanawk hmaa ah, angmah ih cunghet to phok moe, vapui tui to a boh; to naah vapui tuinawk loe athii ah angcoeng boih.
\v 21 Vapui thung ih tanganawk loe duek o boih; vapui tui loe ahmui set parai pongah, Izip kaminawk mah tui to nae o thai ai; Izip prae thung boih ah athii to oh.
\v 22 Toe Izip prae thung ih miklet sah kop kaminawk doeh, miklet kophaih hoiah to baktih hmuen to a sak o toeng; to pongah Faro loe palungthah aep aep; Angraeng mah thuih ih lok baktih toengah, Mosi hoi Aaron mah thuih ih lok to tahngai pae ai.
\v 23 Faro loe angqoi moe, nihnik to angmah im ah caehtaak; nihnik mah sak ih hmuen to tiah doeh sah pae ai.
\v 24 Vapui tui to nae o thai ai boeh pongah, Izip kaminawk boih mah, vapui taengah naek han tui to takaeh o.
\p 
\v 25 Angraeng mah vapui to boh pacoengah, ni sarihto laemhsak.
\c 8
\p 
\v 1 To pacoengah Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah, Faro khaeah caeh loe, Angraeng mah, Praezaek ah kai bok hanah, kai ih kaminawk to tacawtsak lai ah.
\v 2 Nihcae to na tacawtsak ai nahaeloe, Khenah, na prae thung boih ukong hoiah raihaih kang paek han;
\v 3 pop parai ukongnawk loe vapui thung hoiah tacawt o ueloe, na ohhaih siangpahrang im, na iihhhaih ahmuen, na iihhaih imthung, na tamnanawk ih imthung, nangmah kaminawk ih imthung, buh laom thung hoi takaw naephaih laom thung khoek to daw o tih.
\v 4 Nangmah hoi na tamnanawk, nangmah kaminawk ih takpum nui boih ah ukongnawk to daw o tih, tiah a thuih, tiah thui paeh, tiah a naa.
\v 5 Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah, Aaron hanah, Na ban ih cunghet to vacongnawk, vapui tuinawk hoi kangbuem tuinawk nuiah payangh ah loe, Izip prae boih ah ukongnawk to tacawtsak ah, tiah thuih pae han a naa.
\v 6 To pongah Aaron mah Izip prae thung ih tuinawk nuiah a ban to payangh naah, ukongnawk to tacawt o moe, Izip prae thung boih ah koi o.
\v 7 Toe miklet kop kaminawk mah doeh angmacae miklet kophaih hoiah to baktih hmuen to sak o moe, Izip prae thungah ukongnawk to tacawt o sak toeng.
\p 
\v 8 To pacoengah Faro mah Mosi hoi Aaron to kawk moe, Angraeng mah kai hoi kaimah ih kaminawk khaeah kaom ukongnawk to lak let hanah, Angraeng khaeah lawkthui paeh; to tiah nahaeloe nang ih kaminawk mah Angraeng khaeah angbawnhaih to sak hanah, kang caeh o sak han, tiah a naa.
\v 9 Mosi mah Faro khaeah, Ukongnawk loe vapui ah khue oh o moe, nangmah hoi na tamnanawk, nangmah ih kaminawk, nangmah im hoi nangmah kaminawk imthung ah kaom ukongnawk to dueksak hanah, lawk ka thuihaih atue to na pahoe paeh, tiah a naa.
\v 10 Faro mah, Khawnbang ah soe, tiah a naa. Mosi mah Kaicae Angraeng Sithaw baktih mi doeh om ai, tiah na panoek thai hanah, na thuih ih lok baktiah om tih.
\v 11 Ukongnawk loe nangmah hoi na imnawk, na tamnanawk, nangmah ih kaminawk khae hoiah tacawt o boih tih, toe vapui ah khue ni om o tih boeh, tiah a naa.
\v 12 Mosi hoi Aaron mah Faro to caeh hoi taak pacoengah, Faro khae hoi ukongnawk anghmat o hanah, Mosi mah Sithaw khaeah lawkthuih.
\v 13 Mosi mah hnik ih baktih toengah, Angraeng mah sak pae; imthung, avangnawk hoi lawknawk ah kaom ukongnawk loe duek o.
\v 14 Kadueh qok to nawnto tapop o pongah, prae thung boih ah ahmui set.
\v 15 Toe hoikhang boeh, tiah Faro mah panoek naah, palungthahsak let moe, Angraeng mah thuih ih lok baktih toengah, Mosi hoi Aaron ih lok to tahngai pae ai.
\s1 Alungh punghaih
\p 
\v 16 To pacoengah Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah, Aaron han, Na cunghet to payangh sak tahang ah loe, long ih maiphu to bopsak ah; to naah Izip prae thung boih ih maiphunawk to alung ah angcoeng tih, tiah a thuihsak.
\v 17 To tiah a sak hoi. Aaron mah a ban ih cunghet to payangh tahang moe, long ih maiphu to boh; to naah kaminawk hoi moinawk nuiah alungh to oh; Izip prae thung boih ih maiphunawk loe alungh ah angcoeng.
\v 18 Toe Izip prae thung ih miklet kop kaminawk mah angmacae kophaih hoiah alungh ah angcoengsak hanah a sak o, toe angcoeng o sak thai ai; to pongah alungh loe kami hoi moinawk nui boih ah acuk o.
\v 19 \x - \xo 8:19 \xt Luk 11.20.\x*To pacoeng loe miklet kop kaminawk mah Faro khaeah, Hae hmuen loe Sithaw ih ban rang hoiah ni oh boeh, tiah a naa o. Toe Angraeng mah thuih ih lok baktih toengah, Faro ih palung to thahsak toengtoeng vop pongah, nihnik mah thuih ih lok to tahngai pae ai.
\s1 Taksae punghaih
\p 
\v 20 To pacoengah Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah, Khawnthaw ah angthawk ah loe, Faro vapui ah caeh naah anih to tongh hanah zing ah; Angraeng mah, Kai a bok o hanah, kai ih kaminawk to tacawtsak ah, tiah Angraeng mah thuih, tiah a thuisak.
\v 21 Kai ih kaminawk na tacawtsak ai nahaeloe, Khenah, nangmah hoi na tamnanawk, nangmah ih kami hoi na imthung ah, taksae to kang patoeh han; Izip kaminawk ih imthung boih ah taksae to koi tih, nihcae ohhaih long ah doeh taksae cing ah om tih.
\v 22 Toe Kai loe Angraeng ni, tiah long um li ah na panoek o hanah, to na ni hoi kamtong kaimah ih kaminawk ohhaih Goshen to, kalah ta ah ka pahoe han, to ahmuen ah loe taksae roe om mak ai.
\v 23 Kai ih kami hoi nang ih kaminawk to ka tapraek han; hae dawnrai hmuen loe khawnbang ah om amtong tih, tiah a thuih, tiah thuih pae han a naa.
\v 24 Angraeng mah to tiah hmuen to ohsak pongah, Faro siangpahrang ih im, a tamna ih im hoi Izip prae thung boih ah taksae to koi.
\p 
\v 25 To naah Faro mah Mosi hoi Aaron to kawk moe, Caeh oh loe, na Sithaw khaeah sak ih angbawnhaih to hae prae thungah sah oh, tiah a naa.
\v 26 Toe Mosi mah, To tiah loe amsoem mak ai; Kaicae Angraeng Sithaw khaeah, ka sak o ih angbawnhaih loe Izip kaminawk hanah panuet thok hmuen ah om tih; khenah, nangcae mikhnuk ah Izip kaminawk panuet thok ah angbawnhaih to ka sak o nahaeloe, thlung hoi na va o mak ai maw?
\v 27 To pongah ni thumto caehhaih praezaek ah ka caeh o moe, ang thuih ih lok baktih toengah, kaicae Angraeng Sithaw khaeah, angbawnhaih to ka sak o han, tiah a naa.
\v 28 Faro mah, Praezaek ah nangmacae ih Angraeng Sithaw khaeah, angbawnhaih sak hanah kang caeh o sak han; toe kangthla ah caeh o hmah; vaihi kai hanah lawk na thui paeh, tiah a naa.
\v 29 Mosi mah, Khenah, nang khae hoi ka tacawt pacoengah, khawnbang hoi kamtong, taksaenawk mah Faro hoi a tamnanawk, angmah ih kaminawk to tacawt taak hanah, Angraeng khaeah lawk ka thuih roep han; toe Israel kaminawk Angraeng khaeah angbawnhaih sak o thai hanah, Faro mah na ling hmah nasoe loe, caehsak ai ah om hmah nasoe, tiah a naa.
\v 30 To pacoengah Mosi mah Faro to caehtaak moe, Angraeng khaeah lawk a thuih.
\v 31 Mosi mah hnik ih lok baktih toengah, Angraeng mah sak pae; taksaenawk loe Faro hoi a tamnanawk, anih ih kaminawk khae hoiah tacawt o; to pacoeng hoiah loe taksae to om ai boeh.
\v 32 To nathuem ah doeh Faro loe palung thah vop moe, kaminawk to caehsak ai.
\c 9
\s1 Izip kaminawk ih maitaw duekhaih
\p 
\v 1 To pacoengah Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah, Faro khaeah caeh ah loe, Hebrunawk ih Angraeng Sithaw mah, Kai a bok o hanah, kai ih kaminawk to tacawtsak lai ah, tiah a thuih, tiah thuih paeh, tiah ang naa.
\v 2 Nihcae to na caehsak ai ah, na patawn caeng nahaeloe,
\v 3 khenah, Angraeng loe lawk ah kaom pacah ih moinawk, hrangnawk, laa hrangnawk, kaengkuu hrangnawk, maitaw taenawk, tuunawk nuiah ban to phok ueloe, karai parai nathaih to phasak tih.
\v 4 Toe Angraeng mah, Israel kaminawk ih moinawk hoi Izip kaminawk ih moinawk to ka tapraek han, Israel kaminawk ih moi loe maeto doeh dueh mak ai, tiah a thuih, tiah thui paeh, tiah a naa.
\v 5 Angraeng mah atue to pahoe boeh, Angraeng mah khawnbang ah hae hmuen hae prae thungah sah tih, tiah thuih.
\v 6 Angraeng mah khawnbang ah to hmuen to sak; Izip kaminawk ih moi loe duek o boih; toe Israel kaminawk ih moinawk loe maeto doeh dueh ai.
\v 7 Faro mah kami to patoeh naah, khenah, Israel kaminawk ih moi loe maeto doeh dueh ai, tito panoek; toe Faro loe palung amtaaksak toengtoeng vop moe, Israel kaminawk to tacawtsak ai.
\s1 Ahlut manhaih
\p 
\v 8 To pacoengah Angraeng mah Mosi hoi Aaron khaeah, Takoeng ih maiphu to ban tamsum maeto la hoih, Mosi mah Faro hmaa ah van bangah haeh nasoe.
\v 9 To maiphu loe Izip prae thung boih ah koi ueloe, Izip prae thungah kaom kaminawk hoi moinawk to, ahlut mansak boih tih, tiah a naa.
\v 10 \x - \xo 9:10 \xt Lph 16.2.\x*To pongah nihnik mah takoeng pong ih maiphu to a lak hoi moe, Faro hmaa ah angdoet hoi; Mosi mah maiphu to van ah haeh naah, kaminawk hoi moinawk nuiah ahlut to oh.
\v 11 Miklet kop kaminawk hoi Izip kaminawk boih ahlut manh o pongah, Mosi hmaa ah angdoe o thai ai.
\v 12 Mosi khaeah Angraeng mah thuih ih lok baktih toengah, Angraeng mah Faro to palung thahsak, to pongah Mosi hoi Aaron ih lok to tahngai pae ai.
\s1 Qaetui hoi hmai kraksak
\p 
\v 13 To pacoengah Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah, Khawnthaw ah angthawk ah loe, Faro hmaa ah angdoe ah, anih khaeah, Hebru kaminawk ih Angraeng Sithaw mah, Kai a bok o hanah, kai ih kaminawk to tacawtsak lai ah, tiah a thuih, tiah thui pae hanah a naa.
\v 14 Vaihi loe long pum ah kai baktih mi doeh om ai, tiah na panoek hanah, na palung thungah maw, na tamnanawk hoi kaminawk nuiah maw, raihaihnawk to ka phaksak han boeh.
\v 15 Vaihi ban ka payangh moe, nangmah hoi nang ih kaminawk nuiah raihaih ka phaksak han, nang loe long hoiah kang hmatsak han boeh.
\v 16 \x - \xo 9:16 \xt Rom 9.17.\x*Toe na nuiah ka thacakhaih to kam tuengsak moe, long boih ah ka hmin taphong han ih ni, nang hae kang pathawk tahang.
\v 17 Toe nang mah kai kaminawk ih lok to na aek, nangmah hoi nangmah to nam koeh moe, kai ih kaminawk prawt ai ah na oh han maw?
\v 18 Khenah, khawnbang hae atue ah, Izip prae oh tangsuek nathuem hoi kamtong vaihi khoek to kaom vai ai, kanung parai qaetui to ka kraksak han.
\v 19 To pongah vaihi kami to patoeh ah loe, lawk ah kaom moinawk hoi na tawnh ih hmuennawk boih pakuemsak ah; im ah hoih ai ih lawk ah kaom kami hoi moinawk loe qaetui mah va boih ueloe, dueh o boih tih, tiah thuih, tiah a thuisak.
\v 20 Angraeng ih lok zii kami, Faro ih tamnanawk loe angmacae ih tamnanawk hoi pacah ih moinawk to im ah hoih o.
\v 21 Toe Angraeng ih lok tidoeh sah ai kaminawk loe, angmacae tamnanawk hoi pacah ih moinawk to lawk ah caeh o taak.
\p 
\v 22 To pacoengah Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah, Kaminawk, moinawk hoi Izip prae boih ah kaom lawk ih aannawk nuiah qaetui to kraksak hanah, van bangah na ban to payang ah, tiah a naa.
\v 23 Mosi mah angmah ih cunghet to van ah phok tahang naah, Angraeng mah khopazih hoi qaetui to patoeh, hmai to long ah krak; Angraeng mah Izip prae thungah qaetui to kho baktiah angzohsak.
\v 24 \x - \xo 9:24 \xt Lph 8.7; 16.21.\x*To tiah kakrah qaetui loe, hmai hoiah angbaeh; Izip prae oh tangsuek nathuem hoiah to baktih kanung parai, qaetui to om vai ai vop.
\v 25 Qaetui mah Izip prae thung boih ih lawk, kami, pacah ih moi, lawk ah kamprawk aannawk to vah boih moe, lawk ih thingnawk doeh angkhaehsak boih.
\v 26 Israel kaminawk ohhaih Goshen ahmuen khue ah ni, qaetui krah ai ah oh.
\p 
\v 27 To pacoengah Faro mah Mosi hoi Aaron to kawk hanah kami to patoeh, nihnik khaeah, Vaihi hmuen kasak pazae boeh, Angraeng loe toeng, kai hoi kai ih kaminawk loe ka set o boeh.
\v 28 (Khawt boeh); khopazih hoi qaetui to dip thai hanah, Angraeng khaeah lawkthui ah; kang caeh o sak han boeh hmang; kasawk ah na om o mak ai boeh, tiah a naa.
\v 29 Mosi mah anih khaeah, Vangpui zaeh ah ka caeh moe, Angraeng khaeah ban ka payangh han, to naah khopazih hoi qaetui to dii roep tih; to tiah ni long loe Angraeng ih ni, tito na panoek tih.
\v 30 Toe nang hoi na tamnanawk mah Angraeng to na zii o mak ai vop, tito ka panoek, tiah a naa.
\v 31 Buri sakhaih akung hoi barli cang loe amro boeh; barli cang loe aquih tacawt boeh moe, buri sakhaih akung doeh apawk pawk boeh.
\v 32 Takaw dip sakhaih cang hoi bungaih loe amprawk ai vop pongah, amro ai.
\v 33 To pacoengah Mosi loe Faro khae hoiah tacawt moe, vangpui zaeh ah a caeh; Angraeng khaeah a ban to payangh, to naah khopazih hoi qaetui to dip moe, long nuiah kho angzo ai boeh.
\v 34 Khotui, qaetui hoi khopazih to dip boeh, tiah Faro mah hnuk naah, zaehaih a sak let bae vop; angmah hoi a tamnanawk doeh palungthah o let.
\v 35 Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah thuih ih lok baktih toengah, Faro loe palungthah moe, Israel kaminawk to tacawtsak ai.
\c 10
\s1 Pakhuh punghaih
\p 
\v 1 To pacoengah Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah, Faro khaeah caeh ah; anih hmaa ah hae baktih dawnrai hmuennawk kam tuengsak hanah, anih hoi a tamnanawk ih palungthin to kam taksak boeh;
\v 2 Izip prae nuiah ka sak ih hmuen hoi nihcae khaeah ka sak ih dawnrai hmuennawk to, na capa hoi na capa ih capa patoeng khaeah thui paeh, tiah a naa.
\p 
\v 3 To pongah Mosi hoi Aaron loe Faro khaeah caeh hoi moe, anih khaeah, Hebru kaminawk ih Angraeng Sithaw mah, Ka hmaa ah poek pahnaem hanah nasetto maw nang maak han vop? Kai a bok o hanah, kai ih kaminawk to tacawtsak lai ah.
\v 4 Na tacawtsak ai nahaeloe, khenah, khawnbang ah na prae thung boih ah pakhuh kang tacawtsak han;
\v 5 pakhuh loe long ah koi o boih tih, long to na hnu o thai mak ai; nihcae loe qaetui mah bop ai ih kanghmat, lawk ah kamprawk aannawk hoi thingnawk to caa o king tih.
\v 6 Nam panawk hoi nam panawk ih ampanawk mah hae long nuiah khosak o tangsuek nathuem hoi kamtong vaihni ni khoek to hnu o vai ai ih, to baktih pakhuhnawk loe na im, na tamnanawk ih im hoi Izip kaminawk ih im boih ah koi o tih, tiah a thuih, tiah a thuih pae hoi; to pacoengah Mosi mah Faro to caehtaak.
\p 
\v 7 Faro ih tamnanawk mah anih khaeah, Hae kami mah aicae han nasetto maw thaang patung o vop tih? Angmacae ih Angraeng Sithaw to a bok o hanah, nihcae to tacawtsak lai ah; Izip prae loe amro boeh, tiah na panoek ai vop maw? tiah a naa o.
\v 8 To pacoengah Mosi hoi Aaron to Faro khaeah kawk o let; Faro mah nihnik khaeah, Caeh hoi ah loe, na Angraeng Sithaw to bok oh; toe mi kawbaktih kaminawk maw caeh o tih? tiah a naa.
\v 9 Mosi mah, Angraeng khaeah poihsak han oh pongah, thendoengnawk, mitongnawk, kaimacae ih capa hoi canunawk, tuunawk hoi maitawnawk hoi nawnto ka caeh o han, tiah a naa.
\v 10 To naah Faro mah, Caeh hanah nangcae hoi nawktanawk kang prawt o baktih toengah, nangcae khaeah Angraeng to om nasoe; acoe oh; kasae sak han na poek o bae hae!
\v 11 To tiah poek han om ai! Nongpanawk khue caeh o nasoe loe, canghni ah nang hnik o ih baktih toengah, Angraeng to bok o nasoe, tiah a naa. To naah Mosi hoi Aaron to Faro hmaa hoiah haek o ving.
\p 
\v 12 To naah Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah, Izip prae thungah pakhuh angzoh moe, qaetui mah tahmat ih, long ah amprawk aankungnawk to caak boih hanah, na ban to Izip prae nuiah payangh ah, tiah a naa.
\v 13 To pongah Mosi mah a ban ih cunghet to Izip prae nuiah phok; to na niah aqum athun Angraeng mah ni angzae bang ih takhi to songsak; khawnbang phak naah loe takhi mah pakhuhnawk to caeh haih boih.
\v 14 \x - \xo 10:14 \xt Lph 9.2,3.\x*Izip prae thung boih ah pakhu to koi, Izip prae angzithaih ramri taeng khoek to, kroek laek ai ah oh o; to baktih pakhuhnawk loe natuek naah doeh to tiah om vai ai; angzo han koi atue ah doeh to tiah om mak ai.
\v 15 Long boih ah koi o pongah, long loe amnum ving; qaetui mah bop ai ih kanghmat, lawk ah kamprawk aankungnawk hoi thingkung pong ih kanghmat thingthainawk to a caak o boih; Izip prae thung boih ah thingkung kahing, to ai boeh loe lawk ih aannawk roe om ai boeh.
\v 16 Faro mah Mosi hoi Aaron to karangah kawk moe, Nangcae ih Angraeng Sithaw hoi nanghnik nuiah zaehaih ka sak moeng boeh.
\v 17 To pongah vaihi ka zaehaih to tahmen ah loe, na Angraeng Sithaw mah hae duekhaih maeto hae kai khae hoiah takhoe ving hanah, lawk na thui paeh, tiah a naa.
\v 18 Mosi mah Faro to tacawt taak moe, Angraeng khaeah lawk a thuih.
\v 19 To naah Angraeng mah thacak takhi to niduem bang hoiah songsak moe, pakhuhnawk to tuipui kathim thungah hmuh pae boih; Izip prae thung boih ah pakhuh maeto doeh anghmat ai boeh.
\v 20 Toe Angraeng mah Faro to palungthahsak toengtoeng vop pongah, Israel kaminawk to prawt ai.
\s1 Khoving phaksakhaih
\p 
\v 21 To pacoengah Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah, Khoving mah Izip prae to khuk khoep hanah, van bangah na ban to payangh ah, tiah a naa.
\v 22 \x - \xo 10:22 \xt Saam 105.28; Lph 16.10.\x*To pongah Mosi mah van bangah ban to payangh; to naah kathah parai khoving mah Izip prae to ni thumto thung khuk khoep.
\v 23 Maeto hoi maeto ang hnuh o thai ai moe, ni thumto thung naa ah doeh caeh o thai ai; toe Israel kaminawk ohhaih ahmuen ah loe aanghaih to oh.
\v 24 To naah Faro mah Mosi to kawk moe, anih khaeah, Caeh oh loe Angraeng to bok oh; nongpata hoi nawktanawk doeh caeh o boih ah; tuunawk hoi maitawnawk khue to caeh o taak ah, tiah a naa.
\v 25 Toe Mosi mah anih khaeah, Kaicae Angraeng Sithaw khaeah angbawnhaih hoi hmuen paekhaih ka sak o haih hanah moi hoi hmuennawk to na paek ah.
\v 26 Ka pacah o ih moinawk doeh ka caeh o haih han; maeto doeh ka caeh o taak mak ai; to moinawk loe kaimacae ih Angraeng Sithaw to bok hanah ka patoh o han; to ahmuen ka pha o ai karoek to, kaimacae ih Angraeng Sithaw to kawbaktih moi hoiah maw ka bok o han, tito ka panoek o ai vop, tiah a naa.
\v 27 Toe Angraeng mah Faro palungthahsak pongah, nihcae to caehsak han koeh ai.
\v 28 Faro mah Mosi khaeah, Ka hmaa hoi tacawt ah, kai tongh hanah angzo let hmah lai ah! Ka mikhmai na hnuk lethaih ni loe, na duekhaih niah om tih boeh, tiah a naa.
\v 29 Mosi mah, Na thuih ih lok loe hoih; na hmaa ah kam tueng let mak ai boeh, tiah a naa.
\c 11
\s1 Calu dueksakhaih
\p 
\v 1 Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah, Faro hoi Izip prae nuiah raihaih maeto ka phaksak han vop; to pacoengah loe hae ahmuen hoiah na tacawtsak tih boeh; to tiah nawnto na haek o boih ueloe, na tacawt o sak tih boeh.
\v 2 Israel nongpa maw, nongpata maw, mi kawbaktih mah doeh angmacae imtaeng kami khaeah sui hoi sum kanglungnawk hnik hanah, kaminawk khaeah thui paeh, tiah a naa.
\v 3 Kai mah Izip kaminawk khaeah kami tahmenhaih palungthin to ka paek han; Mosi doeh Faro tamnanawk hmaa hoi Izip prae thungah paroeai ka lensak han.
\p 
\v 4 To pongah Angraeng mah khoving ah Izip prae um ah ka caeh han, tiah thuih, tiah Mosi mah thuih.
\v 5 Izip prae thungah caa lu to ka dueksak boih han; angraeng tangkhang nuiah anghnu, Faro ih caa lu hoi amtong ueloe, cang kaehhaih set hnuk ah anghnu tamna nongpata ih caa lu khoek to ka dueksak han; tapen tangsuek moinnawk doeh ka dueksak boih han.
\v 6 Izip prae thung boih canghnii ah kaom vai ai, hmabang ah doeh kaom han ai, qahhaih to om tih.
\v 7 Toe Israel kaminawk ohhaih ahmuen ah loe kami, to tih ai boeh loe moi mataeng doeh ui mah uk mak ai; to naah Angraeng mah Izip kaminawk hoi Israel kaminawk tapraek boeh, tito na panoek o tih, tiah a thuih.
\v 8 Hae ih na tamnanawk boih kai khaeah angzoh o moe, ka hmaa ah akuep o pacoengah, nangmah hoi na hnukbang kaminawk to tacawt o boih lai ah, tiah na thuih pacoengah ni ka caeh han vop, tiah a naa. Mosi loe palungphui moe, Faro to tacawt taak.
\v 9 Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah, Izip prae thung boih ah Kai ih dawnrai hmuen to pung han oh pongah, Faro mah na lok to tahngai mak ai, tiah a naa.
\p 
\v 10 Mosi hoi Aaron mah Faro hmaa ah hae baktih dawnrai hmuennawk boih a sak hoi; toe Angraeng mah Faro ih palung thahsak pongah, a prae thung hoiah Israel kaminawk tacawtsak ai toengtoeng vop.
\c 12
\s1 Loihhaih poih
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 12:1 \xt LEV 23.5; NAM 9.1-5; 28.16; Deu 16.1,2.\x*Izip prae ah Angraeng mah Mosi hoi Aaron khaeah,
\v 2 Vaihi khrah loe nangcae han khrah tangsuek ah om tih; nangcae han saning amtong tangsuekhaih khrah ah om tih.
\v 3 Vaihi khrah ni hato naah, kami boih, angmacae imthung takoh maeto mah, tuucaa maeto sin hanah, amkhueng Israel kaminawk boih khaeah thui ah, tiah a naa.
\v 4 Imthung takoh maeto hanah tuucaa maeto khawt ai nahaeloe, a imtaeng ih kami hoi angcuu o nasoe loe, kami khawt ah tuucaa to sin o nasoe.
\v 5 Coek koi kaom ai, saningto kaom Tuu tae to sin oh; to loe Tuu, to tih ai boeh loe Ma-eh thung hoiah qoi oh;
\v 6 to khrah ni hatlai palito pha ai karoek to tuucaa to kahoih ah khen oh loe, ani phak naah amkhueng Israel kaminawk mah to tuucaa to khoving ah bop o tih.
\v 7 Athii to la oh loe, tuu moi na caak o haih im thok ranuih hoi thok tung ranui ah nok oh.
\v 8 To na ni duembang ah, hmai pakhaem ih moi to, kakhaa aan hoi taeh thuh ai ih takaw hoiah nawnto caa oh.
\v 9 Kahaeng moi maw, to tih ai boeh loe tui hoiah bueh ih moi to caa o hmah; toe a lu moi, a khok hoi palung pathinnawk loe hmai pakhaem pacoengah caa oh.
\v 10 Moi to khawnbang khoek to suem o hmah; kamthlai zetta om nahaeloe, hmai hoiah qoeng oh.
\v 11 Moi na caak o naah, kaengkaeh to angzaeng oh, khokpanaibum abuen oh loe, ban ah cunghet to sin pacoengah, karangah caa oh; hae loe Angraeng ih loihhaih poih ah oh.
\v 12 To na ni qum ah Izip prae thung boih ah ka caeh moe, kaminawk ih caa lu hoi tapen tangsuek moi to ka dueksak boih han; Izip sithawnawk to lok ka caek boih han; Kai loe Angraeng ah ka oh.
\v 13 Athii loe nangcae ohhaih im ah, angmathaih maeto ah om tih; athii ka hnuk naah, nangcae to kang takanh taak han; Izip prae ka tuk naah, nangcae nuiah kasae nathaih pha mak ai.
\p 
\v 14 \x - \xo 12:14 \xt EXO 23.15; 34.18; LEV 23.6-8; NAM 28.17-25; Deu 16.3-8.\x*Hae ani hae pakuem o poe ah; na caanawk dung khoek to hae ani phak naah, Angraeng khaeah buh raenghaih poih to sah oh; sakzong ih atawk baktih toengah, to poih to dungzan khoek to sah oh.
\v 15 Ni sarihto thung taeh thuh ai ih takaw to caa oh; ni amtong tangsuek naah imthung ih taeh to va oh; ni amtong tangsuek hoi ni sarihto thung taeh thuh ih takaw caa kami loe, Israel acaeng thung hoiah pahnawt oh.
\v 16 Amtong tangsuekhaih ni hoi sarihto niah, kaciim amkhuenghaih to sah oh; caaknaek khue ai ah loe tok kalah roe sah o hmah.
\v 17 Hae na ni roe ah Izip prae thung hoiah kang tacawt o haih pongah, taeh thuh ai ih takaw caakhaih poih to sah oh; sakzong ih atawk baktih toengah, na caanawk dung khoek to hae ani hae zaa o poe ah.
\v 18 Khrah tangsuek, to akhrah ni hathlai palito duembang hoi kamtong ni pumphaeto pacoeng, nito duembang karoek to taeh thuh ai ih takaw to caa oh.
\v 19 Ni sarihto thung na imthung ah taeh to suem o hmah; angvin maw, to tih ai boeh loe prae thung tapen kami mah maw, taeh thuh ih takaw to caa nahaeloe, Israel acaeng thung hoiah pahnawt oh.
\v 20 Taeh hoi sak ih takaw to caa o hmah; na ohhaih ahmuen kruekah taeh thuh ai ih takaw to caa oh, tiah a naa.
\p 
\v 21 To pacoengah Mosi mah Israel kacoehtanawk to kawk boih moe, nihcae khaeah, Caeh oh, nangmacae imthung takoh kakhawt ah, tuucaa maeto la oh loe, loihhaih poih sak hanah bop oh.
\v 22 Hissop thing tadok tamsum maeto la oh, sabae kathuk pong ih tuu thii thungah nup oh loe, thok ranui hoi thok tung ranui boih ah nok oh; khawnbang khoek to mi doeh thok tasa bangah caeh o hmah.
\v 23 \x - \xo 12:23 \xt Heb 11.28.\x*Angraeng loe Izip kaminawk hum hanah Izip prae thung boih ah caeh tih; thok ranuih hoi thok tung ranuih boih ah nok ih athii to a hnuk naah, Angraeng mah to im thok to takan taak tih, to tiah kami humkung loe nangcae hum hanah imthung ah akunsak mak ai.
\v 24 Sakzong ih atawk baktih toengah, hae hmuen hae nangmacae hoi na caanawk mah doeh pazui o poe ah.
\v 25 Angraeng mah lokkam ih baktih toengah, anih mah paek han thuih ih prae thungah na kun o naah, hae tok hae sah o poe ah.
\v 26 Na caanawk mah, Hae tok loe tih thuih koehhaih ih maw? tiah na dueng o nahaeloe,
\v 27 nangcae mah nihcae khaeah, Hae loe Angraeng mah Izip kaminawk to hum moe, kaicae ih im loe pathlung, Izip prae ih Israel kaminawk ih im takan taakhaih, Angraeng ih loihhaih poih ah oh, tiah thui pae oh, tiah a naa. To pacoengah kaminawk mah akuep hoiah bok o.
\p 
\v 28 Angraeng mah Mosi hoi Aaron khaeah thuih ih lok baktih toengah, Israel kaminawk mah sak o.
\v 29 \x - \xo 12:29 \xt EXO 4.22,23.\x*Aqum naah Angraeng mah Izip prae ih caa lu boih, angraeng tangkhang nuiah anghnu, Faro caa lu hoi kamtong thongkrah kami ih caa lu, tapen tangsuek moinawk to dueksak boih.
\v 30 Faro, anih ih tamnanawk hoi Izip kaminawk loe qum ah angthawk o boih, Izip prae thungah qahhaih to oh; kadueh ai kami im roe maeto doeh om ai.
\s1 Loih amtonghaih
\p 
\v 31 Aqum ah Faro mah Mosi hoi Aaron to kawk, Angthawk hoih! Nangmah hnik hoi Israel kaminawk to angthawk oh loe, kai kaminawk khae hoiah caeh o lai ah! Nang hnik hoi ih baktih toengah, Angraeng to bok oh.
\v 32 Nangmacae ih tuunawk hoi maitawnawk doeh la oh loe, na thuih o ih baktih toengah caeh oh! Kai doeh tahamhoihaih na paek o toengah, tiah a naa.
\p 
\v 33 Izip kaminawk mah, Kaicae loe kadueh kami ah ni ka oh o boih boeh, tiah a thuih o pongah, Israel kaminawk to Izip prae thung hoi karangah haek hanah, kaminawk to karangah pahruek o.
\v 34 To pongah kaminawk mah taeh thuh ai ih takaw kahaeng to lak o moe, takaw naephaih boengloengnawk doeh kahni hoiah tapawk o pacoengah, palaeng ah aput o.
\v 35 \x - \xo 12:35 \xt EXO 3.21,22.\x*Mosi mah thuih ih lok baktih toengah, Israel kaminawk mah sak o; Izip kaminawk khaeah sui, sum kanglungnawk hoi khukbuennawk to a hnik o;
\v 36 Angraeng mah Izip kaminawk khaeah tahmenhaih palungthin to paek pongah, nihcae mah hnik ih hmuen boih to a paek o. Nihcae mah Izip kaminawk ih hmuen to lak pae o.
\p 
\v 37 Israel kaminawk loe Rameses hoi Sukkoth ah caeh o; to ah caeh kaminawk loe nongpata hoi nawkta thui ai ah, kami sang cumvai tarukto oh o.
\v 38 Congca kaminawk loe tuunawk, maitawnawk, paroeai pop moinawk hoi nawnto caeh o.
\v 39 Izip prae hoi sin o ih, taeh thuh ai ih takaw to lak o moe, taeh thuh ai ih takaw to hmai paop o; nihcae to Izip prae thung hoi karangah haek o, angmacae caak han mataeng doeh sak patok o pongah, takaw to taeh thuh ai ah a sin o.
\p 
\v 40 \x - \xo 12:40 \xt Genesis 15.13; Kal 3.17.\x*Israel kaminawk loe Izip prae thungah saning cumvai pali, qui thumto oh o.
\v 41 Angraeng ih misatuh kaminawk loe saning cumvai pali, qui thumto boeng na niah, Izip prae thung hoiah tacawt o.
\v 42 Aqum ah Izip prae thung hoi caeh haih hanah, Angraeng mah nihcae to toep pongah, to aqum loe Israel caanawk boih mah zah han koi Angraeng ih aqum ah oh.
\s1 Loihhaih poihsakhaih dan
\p 
\v 43 Angraeng mah Mosi hoi Aaron khaeah, Hae loe loihhaih poih sakhaih atawk ah oh; to pongah kawbaktih angvin mah doeh caa thai mak ai.
\v 44 Toe misong ah na qan ih kami loe, tangzat hin aah pacoengah ni, caa tih.
\v 45 Prae kalah kami, toksak han na tlai ih kaminawk loe caa o thai mak ai.
\v 46 \x - \xo 12:46 \xt NAM 9.12; Jhn 19.36.\x*Im maeto ah caa oh; moi to im tasa bangah sin o hmah; ahuh doeh angkhaek o sak hmah.
\v 47 Israel kaminawk boih mah to poih to sah oh.
\v 48 Nangcae thung kaom angvin mah Angraeng loihhaih poih to sak koeh nahaeloe, a imthung takoh ih nongpanawk boih tangzat hin aat o nasoe; to pacoengah ni prae kaminawk baktiah sah o thai tih; tangzat hin aat ai kami loe mi doeh caa thai mak ai.
\v 49 Prae thung tapen kami hoi nangcae salakah kaom prae kalah kami hanah, kanghmong daan maeto patoh oh, tiah a naa.
\p 
\v 50 Angraeng mah Mosi hoi Aaron khaeah thuih ih lok baktih toengah, Israel kaminawk boih mah sak o.
\v 51 To na niah Angraeng mah Israel misatuh kaminawk to, Izip prae thung hoiah a caeh haih.
\c 13
\s1 Caa lu paekhaih
\p 
\v 1 Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah,
\v 2 \x - \xo 13:2 \xt NAM 3.13; Luk 2.23.\x*caa lu boih kai khaeah ciimcai o sak ah; Israel kaminawk ih zok thung hoi tapen tangsuek loe, kami doeh, moi doeh, kai ih ni, tiah a naa.
\v 3 To naah Mosi mah kaminawk khaeah, Angraeng mah a ban thacakhaih hoiah to prae thung hoi ang zaeh o pongah, misong ah na oh o haih Izip prae thung hoi na tacawt o haih ni, hae ni hae pakuem o poe ah; taeh thuh ih takaw to caa o hmah.
\v 4 Vaihni Abib khrah thungah, na caeh o tih boeh.
\v 5 Angraeng mah nangcae paek hanah nam panawk khaeah lokkam ih, tahnutui hoi khoitui longhaih Kanaan, Hit, Amor, Hiv hoi Jebus kaminawk ih prae thungah ang caeh o haih naah, hae khrah ah hae tiah toksak hanah pahnet o hmah.
\v 6 Ni sarihto thung taeh thuh ai ih takaw to caa oh loe, ni sarihto naah Angraeng khaeah hae poih hae sah oh.
\v 7 Ni sarihto thung taeh thuh ai ih takaw to caa oh; nangcae salakah taeh thuh ih takaw tidoeh suem o hmah; na oh o haih a taengah doeh taeh hoi sak ih takaw to amtueng o sak hmah.
\v 8 To na niah na capa khaeah, Kaicae Izip prae thung hoi ka tacawt o naah, Angraeng mah tahmenhaih hoi kaicae nuiah hmuen to sak pongah, hae baktih hmuen hae ka sak o, tiah thui pae oh.
\v 9 Hae hmuen loe nangcae ban ah angmathaih ah om tih, na mik salak ih lupataeh ah panoeksakkung ah om ueloe, na pakha ah Angraeng ih kaalok to om tih; Angraeng mah a thacakhaih rang hoiah Izip prae thung hoiah ang zaeh o.
\v 10 Saningto pacoeng saningto, hae tue phak khruek, hae sakzong ih atawk hae sah oh.
\v 11 Angraeng mah nangcae hoi nam panawk khaeah sak ih lokkamhaih baktih toengah, Kanaan prae ah ang caeh o haih moe, prae ang paek o naah,
\v 12 \x - \xo 13:12 \xt EXO 34.19,20; Luk 2.23.\x*zok thung hoi tapen tangsuek caa to Angraeng han pahoe oh; na tawnh ih tapen tangsuek moi doeh, ataenawk loe Angraeng ih ni.
\v 13 Tapen tangsuek laa hrang to tuucaa hoiah akrang oh; akrang koeh o ai nahaeloe, laa hrang ih tahnong to khaek oh; na caanawk thungah caa lu to akrang oh.
\v 14 Hmabang ah na caanawk mah, Hae hmuen loe tih thuih koehhaih ih maw? tiah na dueng o nahaeloe, Misong ah ohhaih Izip prae thung hoiah Angraeng mah a ban thacakhaih hoiah zaehhaih niah oh;
\v 15 Faro mah aicae tacawtsak han koeh ai naah, Angraeng mah Izip prae thung ih caa lu boih, tapen tangsuek moi to dueksak boih; to pongah zok thung hoi tapen tangsuek moi boih Angraeng khaeah ka paek moe, caalunawk to ka krang, tiah thui pae oh, tiah a naa.
\v 16 Angraeng mah a ban thacakhaih rang hoiah Izip prae thung hoi zaeh pongah, hae loe na ban hoi na mik salak ih lupataeh ah, angmathaih ah om tih, tiah a naa.
\s1 Tuipui kathim angkathaih
\p 
\v 17 Faro mah kaminawk caehsak naah, Philistin prae caehhaih loklam loe anghnaih kue, toe to loklam hoiah Angraeng mah nihcae to caeh haih ai; Angraeng mah kaminawk misatukhaih tongh o naah, poekhaih amkhraih o ueloe, Izip prae ah amlaem o let moeng tih, tiah thuih.
\v 18 To pongah Sithaw mah kaminawk to tuipui kathim caehhaih praezaek loklam bang hoiah caeh haih lat; Israel kaminawk loe misatukhaih khukbuen angkhukhaih hoiah ni Izip prae thung hoiah tacawt o.
\v 19 \x - \xo 13:19 \xt Genesis 50.25; Josh 24.32.\x*Joseph mah Israel caanawk khaeah, Nangcae abomh hanah Sithaw angzo tih; to naah kai ih ahuh to hae ahmuen hoiah la o let ah, tiah lokkam baktih toengah, Mosi mah Joseph ih ahuh to laksak.
\v 20 Nihcae leo Sukkoth hoi caeh o moe, praezaek taeng, Etham vangpui ah atai o.
\v 21 Angraeng mah nihcae to khodai ah tamai hoiah zaeh moe, nihcae aanghaih paek hanah, khoving ah hmaithaw hoiah zaeh.
\v 22 Khodai naah tamai tung, khoving naah hmaithaw hoiah kaminawk to hmabang ah a caeh haih.
\c 14
\p 
\v 1 Angraengh mah Mosi khaeah,
\v 2 Israel kaminawk khaeah, Migdol vangpui hoi tuipui salak, Baal-Zephon vangpui taeng, tuipui taeng Pi-Hahiroth ah amlaem oh loe, tuipui taengah atai o han, thui paeh.
\v 3 Faro mah Israel kaminawk kawng pongah, Nihcae loe saoeng ah raihaih tongh o, praezaek mah pakaa khoep boeh, tiah thui tih.
\v 4 Faro to palung ka thahsak moe, nihcae ka patomsak let han; toe Faro hoi anih ih misatuh kaminawk nuiah, ka lensawkhaih to kam tuengsak han; to naah Izip kaminawk mah kai loe Angraeng ah ka oh, tito panoek o tih, tiah a naa. To pongah Israel kaminawk mah to tiah sak o.
\p 
\v 5 Kaminawk cawnh o boih boeh, tiah Izip siangpahrang khaeah thuih pae o naah, Faro hoi a tamnanawk loe uthaih palungthin to tawnh o moe, kaminawk khaeah, Tikhoe hae tiah na sak o moe, aicae han toksah Israel kaminawk to na tacawt o sak boih loe? tiah a naa o.
\v 6 To pongah angmah ih hrang leeng to suek coek moe, angmah ih kaminawk to nawnto a caeh haih;
\v 7 kahoih koek hrang leeng cumvai tarukto a lak moe, Izip prae ih hrang angthueng kaminawk, misatuh angraengnawk to a kawk.
\v 8 Angraeng mah Izip siangpahrang, Faro ih palung to thahsak pongah, anih mah Israel kaminawk to patom; toe Israel kaminawk loe amoekhaih hoiah caeh o.
\v 9 Izip kaminawk, Faro ih hrangnawk hoi hrang leengnawk, hrang angthueng kaminawk hoi misatuh kaminawk mah Israel kaminawk to patom o moe, Bal-Zephon hmaa ih, vapui taeng Pi-Hariroth ah anghak o naah a kae o.
\p 
\v 10 Israel kaminawk mah doeng o naah, Faro loe anghnai daek ah phak boeh; to naah Izip kaminawk mah nihcae patom boeh, tito panoek o, Israel kaminawk loe paroeai zit o moe, Angraeng khaeah hangh o.
\v 11 Israel caanawk mah Mosi khaeah, Izip prae ah taprong om ai pongah maw, duek hanah praezaek ah nang caeh haih? Tipongah hae tiah sak hanah, Izip prae thung hoi nang caeh haih loe?
\v 12 Izip prae ah, Na caeh o taak ah, kaicae loe Izip kaminawk ih tok to ka sak pae o halat han boeh, tiah kang thuih o na ai maw? Praezaek ah ka duek o pongah loe, Izip kaminawk ih toksak to kaicae han hoih kue, tiah a naa o.
\v 13 Mosi mah kaminawk khaeah, Zii o hmah, kacakah angdoe oh, vaihni ah Angraeng mah nangcae hnuksak han ih, pahlonghaih to khen oh; vaihni ah na hnuk o ih Izip kaminawk loe, dungzan khoek to na hnu o let mak ai boeh.
\v 14 Nangcae loe anghngai o duem ah, Angraeng mah nangcae han misa na tuh pae tih, tiah a naa.
\v 15 To pacoengah Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah, Tipongah kai khaeah na hang o loe? Israel kaminawk khaeah hmabang caeh o poe hanah thui pae oh;
\v 16 toe na cunghet to phok tahang ah, tuipui nuiah na ban to payang ah loe, tuipui to pakhoih ah; to naah Israel kaminawk loe tuipui um li ah saoeng baktiah caeh o tih.
\v 17 Khenah, nihcae mah nangcae patom o hanah, Izip kaminawk to palung ka thahsak han; Faro hoi angmah ih misatuh kaminawk, hrang leengnawk hoi hrang angthueng kaminawk boih nuiah, ka lensawkhaih to amtueng tih.
\v 18 Faro hoi angmah ih hrang leeng, anih ih hrang angthueng kaminawk nuiah ka lensawkhaih to kam tuengsak naah, Kai loe Angraeng ah ka oh, tito Izip kaminawk mah panoek o tih, tiah a naa.
\p 
\v 19 Israel misatuh kaminawk ataihaih hmaa ah kacaeh, Sithaw ih van kami loe amlaem moe, nihcae hnuk ah a caeh; nihcae hmaa ah kacaeh tamai tung doeh nihcae hnukbang ah angdoet sut;
\v 20 Izip misatuh kaminawk ataihaih ahmuen hoi Israel kaminawk ataihaih ahmuen salakah a caeh; tamai loe maeto hanah vinghaih ah oh moe, maeto hanah loe aanghaih ah oh pongah, nihcae loe aqum puek maeto hoi maeto khaeah caeh o thai ai.
\p 
\v 21 To pacoengah Mosi mah tuipui bangah ban to payangh, to naah Angraeng mah aqum puek ni angyae bang hoiah takhi kaham to songsak, tui to saoeng ah angcoengsak moe, tui to hnetto ah amkhoih.
\v 22 \x - \xo 14:22 \xt 1 Korin 10.1,2; Heb 11.29.\x*Israel kaminawk loe tuipui um li ah, saoeng ih lam caeh baktih toengah a caeh o; tui loe banqoi bantang im tapang baktiah oh.
\v 23 Izip kaminawk loe Faro ih hrang, hrang leeng, hrang angthueng kaminawk hoiah nihcae to patom o moe, tuipui um li ah a caeh o.
\v 24 Akhawnbang ah loe Angraeng mah tamai hmai thung hoiah Izip misatuh kaminawk to khet tathuk, to naah Izip misatuh kaminawk to raihaih paek.
\v 25 Hrang leeng caeh thaih han ai ah, hrang leeng khoknawk to angmongsak boih; to naah Izip kaminawk mah, Israel kaminawk khae hoi cawn o ving si boeh; Angraeng mah hae kaminawk hanah Izip kaminawk to misa tuk pae boeh, tiah a thuih o.
\p 
\v 26 To naah Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah, Izip kaminawk, hrang leengnawk hoi hrang angthueng kaminawk nuiah, tui angcuu let moe, khuk hmoek hanah, tuipui nuiah na ban to payangh ah, tiah a naa.
\v 27 Mosi mah tuipui nuiah a ban to payangh; akhawnbang ah loe tuipui kathuk ah tui to angcuu let; Izip kaminawk loe cawnh o; toe Angraeng mah Izip kaminawk to tuipui um ah uemsak king.
\v 28 Tui loe angcuu let moe, Nihcae patom Faro ih misatuh kaminawk, hrang leengnawk hoi hrang angthueng kaminawk to uem boih; kami maeto doeh anghmat o ai.
\v 29 Toe Israel kaminawk loe tuipui um li ah saoeng baktiah caeh o poe; tui loe nihcae han banqoi bantang im tapang baktiah oh.
\p 
\v 30 To na niah Angraeng mah Israel kaminawk to Izip kaminawk ih ban thung hoiah pahlong; tuipui taengah kadueh Izip kaminawk ih qok to Israel kaminawk mah hnuk o.
\v 31 Izip kaminawk nuiah Angraeng mah kalen parai toksakhaih to amtuengsak, tito Israel kaminawk mah hnuk o naah, Angraeng to zit o moe, Angraeng hoi a tamna Mosi nuiah tanghaih to tawnh o.
\c 15
\s1 Mosi ih laa
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 15:1 \xt Lph 15.3.\x*To pacoengah Mosi hoi Israel kaminawk mah Angraeng khaeah hae laa hae a sak o;
\p Angraeng mah lensawkhaih hoiah pazawk boeh pongah, anih khaeah laa to ka sak han; anih mah hrang hoi a nuiah angthueng kaminawk tui thungah vah boih boeh.
\p 
\v 2 \x - \xo 15:2 \xt Saam 118.14; Isaiah 12.2.\x*Agraeng loe ka thacakhaih hoi kai ih laa ah oh moe, kai pahlonghaih ah oh; anih loe ka Sithaw ah oh pongah, anih to ka pakoeh han; kam pa ih Sithaw ah oh pongah, ka pakoeh han.
\p 
\v 3 Angraeng loe misatuh kami ah oh, anih ih ahmin loe Angraeng, tiah oh.
\p 
\v 4 Anih mah Faro ih hrang leeng hoi misatuh kaminawk to tui thungah vah boih boeh; Faro mah kahoih koek qoih ih misatuh angraengnawk loe kathim tuipui thungah uem o boih boeh.
\p 
\v 5 Kathuk tuili mah nihcae to khuk khoep, nihcae loe thlung baktiah tui thungah krak o tathuk boeh.
\p 
\v 6 Aw Angraeng, thacak na bantang ban hoiah na misanawk to kadip pueng ah na hnoih.
\p 
\v 7 Na lensawk na thacakhaih hoiah na misanawk to na vah phaeng, nihcae to na palungphuihaih mah anghnoeng baktiah kangh boeh.
\p 
\v 8 Na hnahkhaw ih takhi hoiah tuinawk to nang cuusak; tuiphu to im tapang baktiah nang doetsak moe, kathuk tuipui um li ah tui to tha na caksak.
\p 
\v 9 Misanawk mah, nihcae kae hanah, ka patom o moe, lomh ih hmuennawk to kam zet o han, to naah loe ka koehhaih akoep tih boeh; ka sumsen to ka phongh moe, nihcae to ka ban hoiah ka hum han, tiah a thuih o.
\p 
\v 10 Toe nang hahhaih takhi hoiah na hmuh, nihcae loe tuipui mah khuk khoep; nihcae loe kalen parai tuinawk thungah, kimlok baktiah krak o zuep boeh.
\p 
\v 11 Aw Angraeng, sithawnawk thungah mi maw nang baktiah kaom? Mi maw nang baktiah, lensawk ciimcaihaih, zit kathok pakoehhaih hoiah dawnrai hmuennawk to sah thaih?
\p 
\v 12 Na bantang ban na payangh naah, long mah nihcae to paaeh.
\p 
\v 13 Kaboeng thai ai na palung nathaih hoiah na krang ih kaminawk to na zaeh; na thacakhaih hoiah na ohhaih hmuenciim to nihcae hanah na patuek.
\p 
\v 14 Kaminawk mah thaih o naah, zii o tih; Philistin kaminawk loe tasoehhaih hoiah om o tih.
\p 
\v 15 Edom ukkungnawk loe dawnrai o ueloe, Moab zaehoikungnawk doeh tasoeh o tih; Kanaan kaminawk loe palungboeng o tih.
\p 
\v 16 Zithaih hoi tasoehhaih to nihcae nuiah krah tih; Aw Angraeng, nangmah ih kaminawk to poeng o moe, na qan ih kaminawk poeng o pacoengah, kalensawk na ban thacakhaih rang hoiah nihcae to thlung baktiah angtawt ai ah nang hngaisak duem tih.
\p 
\v 17 Aw Angraeng, qawk ah na toep ih mae, oh hanah na sak ih ahmuen thungah, nangmah ih kaminawk to na kun haih tih; Aw Angraeng, na ban hoi sak ih hmuenciim ah nihcae to na omsak tih.
\p 
\v 18 Angraeng mah dungzan hoi dungzan khoek to uk poe tih, tiah laa to a sak o.
\p 
\v 19 Faro ih hrangnawk, hrang leengnawk hoi hrang angthueng kaminawk loe, tuipui thungah caeh o pacoengah, Angraeng mah nihcae nuiah tuipui to amlaemsak let; toe Israel kaminawk loe tuipui um li ah saoeng baktiah caeh o.
\v 20 To naah Aaron ih tanuh, tahmaa nongpata Miriam mah, cingceng to ban ah sin moe, nongpatanawk boih anih hnuk ah cingceng bohhaih hoiah hnawh o.
\v 21 Miriam mah, Angraeng khaeah laa to sah oh;
\q1 anih mah lensawkhaih hoiah pazawk boeh;
\q2 hrang hoi a nuiah angthueng kaminawk to
\q2 tuipui thungah a vah boih boeh, tiah laa to sak.
\s1 Tui kakhaa hoi tui kaluep
\p 
\v 22 Mosi mah Israel kaminawk tuipui kathim hoiah zaeh moe, Shur praezaek ah a caeh haih; ni thumto thung tui om ai ah, praezaek ah a caeh o.
\v 23 Marah ahmuen to a phak o naah, tui loe khaa pongah, Marah ih tui to nae o thai ai; to pongah to ahmuen to Marah, tiah kawk o.
\v 24 To pongah kaminawk mah Mosi khaeah, Timaw ka naek o han? tiah laisaep o thuih.
\v 25 To naah Mosi mah Angraeng khaeah hangh, to naah Angraeng mah thing maeto a hnuksak; anih mah to thing to tui thungah vah naah, tui to luep; to ahmuen ah Anih mah nihcae to tanoek, a sak o zong ih hmuen hoi daan to a sak pae.
\v 26 Nihcae khaeah, Na Angraeng Sithaw ih lok kahoih ah na tahngaih o, a mikhnuk ah katoeng hmuen to na sak o moe, ang paek o ih lok to na tahngaih o pacoengah, anih ih daannawk to na pazui o nahaeloe, Izip kaminawk nuiah ka phaksak ih nathaih to, nangcae nuiah ka phasak mak ai; Kai loe nangcae ngantuisakkung, Angraeng ah ka oh, tiah a naa.
\p 
\v 27 Nihcae loe tui khaw hathlai hnetto hoi ungsikung qui sarihto ohhaih, Elim ahmuen ah caeh o moe, tui taengah anghak o.
\c 16
\s1 Manna hoi kuikoem paekhaih
\p 
\v 1 Israel kaminawk boih, Elim ahmuen hoiah angthawk o moe, Elim hoi Sinai salakah kaom, Sin praezaek ah a caeh o; Izip prae hoi tacawthaih khrah hnetto haih ni hatlai pangato naah to ahmuen to a phak o.
\v 2 Praezaek ah kaminawk boih mah Mosi hoi Aaron to laisaep o thuih.
\v 3 Israel kaminawk mah nihnik khaeah, Izip prae ah moi thonghaih laom taengah anghnut moe, zok kamhah ah ka caak o naah, Angraeng ih ban hoi ka duek o nahaeloe hoih kue han to mah! Nanghnik mah haeah amkhueng kaminawk hae zok kamtlam ah dueksak hanah, hae praezaek ah na hoih hoi, tiah a naa o.
\p 
\v 4 \x - \xo 16:4 \xt Jhn 6.31.\x*To naah Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah, Khenah, nangcae han van hoiah takaw kho baktiah kang zohsak han; kaminawk to caeh o nasoe loe, nito caak kakhawt ah takaw to akhui o nasoe; ka paek ih lok tahngai o maw, tahngai o ai, tito hae tiah ka tanoek han.
\v 5 Ni tarukto naah loe, ni kalah ah akhuih ih pongah kamtlai alet hnetto ah akhui o nasoe loe, suem o nasoe, tiah a naa.
\v 6 To pongah Mosi hoi Aaron mah Israel kaminawk boih khaeah, Izip prae thung hoi nangcae zaehoikung loe Angraeng ni, tito vai duem ah na panoek o tih;
\v 7 akhawnbang ah doeh Angraeng lensawkhaih to na hnu o tih; na laisaep o haih to Angraeng mah thaih boeh; kaihnik loe kawbang maw ka oh hoi moe, nang laisaep o thuih? tiah a naa hoi.
\v 8 Mosi mah, Angraeng mah caak han ih moi to duembang ah na paek o ueloe, akhawnbang ah zok amhah hanah takaw to na paek o tih; to naah, Na laisaep o haih lok Angraeng mah thaih boeh, tiah thuih ih lok to akoep tih; kaihnik loe kawbang maw ka oh hoi moe, nang laisaep o thuih? Laisaep kaminawk loe kaihnik laisaep thuih ai ah, Angraeng ni na laisaep o thuih, tiah a naa hoi.
\p 
\v 9 To naah Mosi mah Aaron khaeah, Na laisaep o haih lok to Angraeng mah thaih boeh pongah, anih khaeah angzo oh, tiah thuih pae han a naa.
\v 10 Aaron mah amkhueng Israel kaminawk boih khaeah lok to thuih pae, nihcae praezaek bangah doeng o naah, tamai nuiah Angraeng lensawkhaih to amtueng.
\v 11 Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah,
\v 12 Israel kaminawk laisaephaih lok to ka thaih boeh; nihcae khaeah, Duembang ah moi to na caa o ueloe, akhawnbang ah takaw to zok kamhah ah na caa o tih; to naah kai loe nangcae ih Angraeng Sithaw ah ka oh, tito na panoek o tih, tiah thui paeh, tiah a naa.
\p 
\v 13 To na ni duembang ah kuikoemnawk loe nihcae ohhaih ahmuen taeng koimong ah angzoh o tahang; akhawnbang ah loe misatuh kaminawk ataihaih ahmuen taengah dantui to krak.
\v 14 Dantui anghmat pacoengah, khenah, praezaek ih long nui ah, dantui baktih kangbuet luet tetta kaom, hmuen to oh.
\v 15 \x - \xo 16:15 \xt 1 Korin 10.3.\x*To hmuen to Israel kaminawk mah hnuk o naah, hae loe manna maw? tiah maeto hoi maeto a thuih o. To hmuen loe timaw, tito panoek o ai. Mosi mah nihcae khaeah, Hae loe na caak o hanah Angraeng mah paek ih takaw ni.
\v 16 Angraeng mah, Kami boih mah caak kakhawt ah akhui oh; kahni im ah kaom a caanawk caak khawt ah, kami maeto mah omer maeto akhui o hanah a thuih pae.
\v 17 A thuih ih lok baktih toengah Israel kaminawk mah sak o; thoemto kaminawk loe kapop ah akhuih o, thoemto kaminawk mah loe zetta ah akhuih o.
\v 18 \x - \xo 16:18 \xt 2 Kor 8.15.\x*To tiah akhui o ih manna to omer hoi tah o naah, kapop ah akhui kami doeh amtlai ai; zetta akhui kami doeh vawt ai; kami boih mah caak khawt ah akhuih o.
\v 19 To naah Mosi mah nihcae khaeah, Mi kawbaktih doeh akhawnbang khoek to amtlai o sak hmah, tiah a naa.
\v 20 Toe thoemto kaminawk mah Mosi mah thuih ih lok to tahngai o ai; akhawnbang khoek to a suek o; toe qong moe, ahmui set pae; to pongah Mosi loe nihcae nuiah palungphui.
\v 21 Akhawnbang kruek kami boih mah angmacae caak khawt ah akhui o; ni bet naah loe, amkaw boih.
\p 
\v 22 Ni tarukto naah loe kaminawk mah takaw baktiah alet hnetto kamtlai ah akhui o; kami maeto hanah omer hnetto akhuih o; rangpui ukkungnawk loe caeh o moe, to hmuen to Mosi khaeah thuih pae o.
\v 23 \x - \xo 16:23 \xt EXO 20.8-11.\x*Mosi mah nihcae khaeah, Angraeng mah, khawnbang loe kaciim Angraeng anghakhaih ni, Sabbath ah oh, to pongah hmai paaem koi hmuen to hmai paaem oh ah loe, bueh koi to buet o coek ah; kamtlai to akhawnbang khoek to kahoih ah pakuem oh, tiah a thuih, tiah a naa.
\v 24 To pongah Mosi mah thuih ih lok baktih toengah, akhawnbang caak hanah a suek o; toe hmuisae ai, qong doeh qong ai.
\v 25 Mosi mah nihcae khaeah, to takaw to vaihniah caa oh; vaihni loe Angraeng ih Sabbath ah oh pongah, to hmuen to long ah na hnu o mak ai.
\v 26 Ni tarukto naah akhui oh loe patung oh; toe ni sarihto Sabbath niah loe maeto doeh na hnu o mak ai, tiah a naa.
\v 27 Toe thoemto kaminawk loe akhuih han caeh o nganga; toe maeto doeh hnu o ai.
\v 28 To naah Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah, Nangcae mah nasetto maw kang paek o ih lok hoi kai ih kaalok to na aek o han vop?
\v 29 Angraeng mah Sabbath to ang paek o; to pongah ni tarukto ni ah ni hnetto caak hanah takaw to ang paek o; kami boih ni sarihto naah loe angmah ohhaih ahmuen ah om o boih nasoe loe, mi doeh a ohhaih ahmuen hoi tasa bangah tacawt hmah nasoe, tiah a naa.
\v 30 To pongah kaminawk loe ni sarihto naah anghak o.
\p 
\v 31 \x - \xo 16:31 \xt NAM 11.7,8.\x*Israel kaminawk mah to ih takaw to manna, tiah kawk o; to takaw loe coriander amu baktiah oh, anglung moe, khoitui hoi sak ih takaw baktiah luep.
\v 32 Mosi mah Angraeng mah paek ih lok loe hae tiah oh; Izip prae thung hoiah kang zaeh o naah, praezaek ah kang pacah o ih takaw to angzo han koi na caanawk mah hnuk o thai hanah, manna to omer maeto kakoi ah suem oh, tiah a thuih, tiah a naa.
\v 33 \x - \xo 16:33 \xt Heb 9.4.\x*To pongah Mosi mah Aaron khaeah, Boengloeng maeto la ah loe, to thungah manna omer maeto kakoi ah thaeng ah; na caanawk han pakuem pae hanah, Angraeng hmaa ah suem ah, tiah a naa.
\v 34 Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah thuih ih lok baktih toengah pakuem hanah, hnukung hmaa ah Aaron mah thaengh.
\v 35 \x - \xo 16:35 \xt Josh 5.12.\x*Anghakhaih prae pha o ai karoek to Israel kaminawk mah saning qui palito thung manna to caak o; Kanaan prae phak khoek to manna to a caak o.
\v 36 Ephah hato thungah maeto loe omer maeto ah oh.
\c 17
\s1 Lungsong thung ih tui
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 17:1 \xt NAM 20.2-13.\x*Israel kaminawk loe Angraeng mah thuih ih lok baktih toengah, Sin praezaek hoi tacawt o moe, ahmuen kalah bangah kholong caeh o; Rephidim ahmuen ah anghak o; to ahmuen ah loe kaminawk mah naek o hanah tui to om ai.
\v 2 Topongah kaminawk mah, Ka naek o hanah tui na paek ah, tiah Mosi to zoeh o. Mosi mah nihcae khaeah, Tikhoe kai nang zoeh o moe, Angraeng to na tanoek o loe? tiah a naa.
\v 3 Toe kaminawk loe tui anghaeh o boeh pongah, Mosi to laisaep o thuih; nihcae mah, Tipongah kaimah hoi ka caanawk khue ai ah, ka tawnh o ih moinawk doeh duek hanah, Izip prae thung hoi hae praezaek ah nang caeh haih loe? tiah a naa o.
\v 4 To naah Mosi mah Angraeng khaeah, Hae kaminawk hae kawbang maw ka naa han? Kai thlung hoi ang vah o tom boeh, tiah a hang.
\v 5 To naah Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah, Kaminawk hmaa ah caeh ah, Israel kacoehtanawk hoi nawnto caeh ah, tuipui na bohhaih cunghet to sin ah loe, caeh ah.
\v 6 Khenah, Na hmaa ih Horeb lungsong nuiah kang doet han; lungsong to bop ah, kaminawk mah naek o hanah, lungsong thung hoiah tui to tacawt tih, tiah a naa. Mosi mah to tiah Israel kaminawk mikhnuk ah sak.
\v 7 Israel kaminawk mah, Aicae salakah Angraeng oh maw, om ai? tiah Angraeng to tanoek o moe, zoeh o pongah, to ahmuen to Massah hoi Meribah, tiah ahmin paek o.
\s1 Amalek kaminawk pazawkhaih
\p 
\v 8 Amalek kaminawk loe angzoh o moe, Rephidim ahmuen ah Israel kaminawk hoiah angtuk o.
\v 9 Mosi mah Joshua khaeah, Aicae thung hoi thoemto kaminawk to qoi ah loe, Amalek misatuk hanah caeh ah; khawnbang ah Sithaw ih cunghet to ban ah ka sin moe, mae nuiah kang doet han, tiah a naa.
\v 10 To pongah Mosi mah thuih ih lok baktih toengah, Joshua mah Amalek kaminawk to tuk; to naah Mosi, Aaron hoi Hur loe mae nuiah dawh o.
\v 11 Mosi ban payangh naah, Israel kaminawk mah misa pazawk o; toe anih ih ban pakhrak tathuk naah, Amalek kaminawk mah pazawk o.
\v 12 Mosi ban khah naah thlung to lak o moe, anih tlim ah suek pae o; anih to thlung nuiah anghnut o sak pacoengah, Aaron hoi Hur mah anih ih ban to hae bang hoi ho bang, niduem khoek to, pakhrah ai ah atoengh pae hoi.
\v 13 To pongah Joshua mah Amalek misa to sumsen hoiah tuk pazawk.
\p 
\v 14 \x - \xo 17:14 \xt Deu 25.17-19; 1 Sam 15.2-9.\x*To naah Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah, Hae hmuen hae panoek poe hanah cabu pongah tarik ah loe, Joshua han kahoih ah kroek paeh; Amalek kaminawk poekhaih loe van tlim hoiah kang hmatsak han, tiah a naa.
\v 15 Mosi mah hmaicam maeto sak moe, Jehovah-nissi, tiah ahmin paek.
\v 16 Mosi mah, A caanawk adung maeto pacoeng maeto khoek to Angraeng mah Amalek kaminawk to tuh tih, tiah Angraeng mah lokkam boeh, tiah thuih.
\c 18
\s1 Jethro paqaihaih
\p 
\v 1 Sithaw mah Mosi hoi Angraeng ih Israel kaminawk han sak pae ih hmuennawk boih hoi kawbang maw Angraeng mah Israel kaminawk Izip prae thung hoiah zaeh, tiah Mosi ih amsae, Midian kami qaima Jethro mah thaih naah,
\v 2 \x - \xo 18:2 \xt EXO 2.21,22.\x*Jethro loe Mosi mah patoeh let ih a zu Zipporah hoi,
\v 3 \x - \xo 18:3 \xt Tsk 7.29.\x*a capa hnik to lak let; Mosi mah minawk prae ah angvin ah ka oh, tiah poek pongah, maeto loe Gershom, tiah ahmin paek;
\v 4 kam pa ih Sithaw loe kai bomkung ah oh, anih mah Faro ih sumsen thung hoiah ang pahlong, tiah a thuih pongah, a capa kalah maeto loe Eliezer, tiah ahmin sak.
\v 5 Mosi ih amsae Jethro loe Mosi ih zu, capa hnik hoi nawnto Mosi anghakhaih Sithaw mae taeng ih praezaek ah caeh o;
\v 6 to naah Jethro mah, Nam sae, kai, Jethro loe na zu, na capa hnik hoi nawnto nang khaeah kang zoh o boeh, tiah a naa.
\v 7 To pongah Mosi mah amsae to hnuk hanah a dawt, akuep moe, anih to mok; loklang angdueng o pacoengah, kahni imthung ah akun o.
\v 8 Mosi mah amsae khaeah, Angraeng mah Israel kaminawk hanah, Faro hoi Izip kaminawk nuiah sak pae ih hmuennawk boih, loklam ah a tongh o ih raihaihnawk hoi Angraeng mah Israel kaminawk kawbang maw pahlong, tito a thuih pae boih.
\v 9 Jethro loe Angraeng mah Israel kaminawk nuiah sak ih kahoih hmuennawk boih hoi nihcae to Izip kaminawk ih ban thung hoi pahlong pongah anghoehaih a tawnh.
\p 
\v 10 Anih mah, Izip kaminawk hoi Faro ih ban thung hoiah pahlongkung, Izip kaminawk ih ban thung hoi pahlongkung, Angraeng loe tahamhoihaih om nasoe.
\v 11 Angraeng loe kalah sithawnawk boih pongah len kue, tito ka panoek boeh; kaminawk amoekhaih loe anih mah pazawk boeh, tiah a naa.
\v 12 To pacoengah Mosi amsae Jethro mah hmai angbawnhaih sak hanah moi hoi kalah hmuennawk to Sithaw khaeah sinh; to naah Aaron hoi Israel kacoehtanawk loe Mosi amsae hoi nawnto Sithaw hmaa ah takaw caak hanah angzoh o.
\p 
\v 13 Mosi loe kaminawk lokcaek hanah akhawnbang ah anghnut; kaminawk loe akhawnbang hoi duembang khoek to Mosi taengah angdoet o.
\v 14 Mosi mah kaminawk nuiah sak ih hmuen to amsae mah hnuk naah, kawbang maw kaminawk nuiah hae tiah hmuen hae na sak? Tikhoe kaminawk loe akhawnbang hoi duembang khoek to na taengah anghnut o moe, nangmah bueng lok na caek loe? tiah a naa.
\v 15 Mosi mah Sithaw koehhaih pakrong han ih ni kai khaeah angzoh o;
\v 16 lok angaekhaih oh naah, kai khaeah angzoh o; kai mah nihcae to maeto pacoeng maeto lok ka caek moe, Sithaw zaehhoihhaih daan hoi loknawk to ka thuih pae, tiah a naa.
\v 17 Mosi amsae mah anih khaeah, Na sak ih hmuen hae hoih ai.
\v 18 Hae tok loe nang hanah azit hmoek pongah, nangmah hoi na taengah kaom kaminawk loe thazok o tangtang tih; nangmah bueng na pazawk thai mak ai.
\v 19 Vaihi ka lok hae tahngai ah, poekhaih kang paek han; nang khaeah Sithaw om nasoe; nang loe Sithaw hmaa ah laicaeh ah om ah loe, lok angaekhaih Sithaw khaeah thuikung ah om ah;
\v 20 kaminawk khaeah zaehhoihaih daan hoi kaaloknawk to patuk ah; nihcae caeh han koi loklam to patuek ah loe, nihcae mah sak han koi hmuen to thui paeh.
\v 21 Kaminawk thung hoiah Sithaw zii kami, oepthok kami, kamtlai koeh hmoek ai kaminawk to qoih loe, sangto, cumvaito, qui pangato hoi pangato ukkungnawk to suem ah.
\v 22 To kaminawk mah hmuen boih nuiah lokcaek o nasoe loe, karai hmuen khue to nang khaeah angzo o haih nasoe; toe kazoi hmuen loe nihcae mah lokcaek o nasoe; to tiah na sak nahaeloe nihcae mah na tok to lawnh o ueloe, na phawh ih hmuen doeh anghoep kue tih.
\v 23 Sithaw mah paek ih lok baktih toengah, hae tiah na sak nahaeloe, kacakah nang doe thai ueloe, hae ih kaminawk boih doeh, lunghoihta hoiah angmacae im ah amlaem o tih, tiah a naa.
\v 24 Mosi mah amsae ih lok to tahngaih moe, a thuih ih lok baktih toengah sak.
\v 25 Mosi loe Israel kaminawk boih thung hoiah toksah thaih kaminawk to qoih moe, sangto ukkung, cumvaito ukkung, qui pangato ukkung, hato ukkung hoi pangato ukkung, tiah a suek boih.
\v 26 Nihcae loe kawbaktih atue ah doeh lokcaek kami ah oh o; karai hmuen to Mosi khaeah caeh o haih moe, kazoi hmuen loe angmacae mah pathlaeng o.
\v 27 To pacoengah Mosi mah amsae to amlaemsak let; Jethro loe angmah prae ah amlaem let.
\c 19
\s1 Sinai mae ah
\p 
\v 1 Israel kaminawk Izip prae thung hoi tacawt o pacoeng, khrah thumto naah, Sinai praezaek to phak o.
\v 2 Israel kaminawk loe Rephidim hoi amsak o moe, Sinai praezaek phak o pacoengah, mae hmaa ah atai o.
\v 3 Mosi mah Sithaw khae caeh tahang naah, Angraeng angmah khaeah angzoh hanah mae nui hoiah a kawk moe, Jakob imthung takoh hoi Israel kaminawk khaeah hae tiah a thui paeh;
\v 4 Izip kaminawk khaeah ka sak ih hmuen na hnuk o boeh; kawbang maw tahmu ih pakhraeh pongah kang hnut o sak moe, kaimah khaeah kang hoih o, tito na panoek o boeh.
\v 5 \x - \xo 19:5 \xt 1 Pt 2.9.\x*\x - \xo 19:5 \xt Deu 4.20; 7.6; 14.2; 26.18; Titu 2.14.\x*To pongah vaihi ka lok hae na tahngaih o moe, ka lokkamhaih na aek o ai nahaeloe, nangcae loe kaminawk boih salakah kai ih qawk ah na om o tih; long pum loe kai ih ni;
\v 6 \x - \xo 19:6 \xt Lph 1.6; 5.10.\x*nangcae loe kai han kaciim acaeng hoi siangpahrang ukhaih prae ah kai ih qaima ah na om o tih, tiah a thuih pae. Hae loknawk hae Israel kaminawk khaeah thui paeh, tiah a naa.
\p 
\v 7 To pongah Mosi loe amlaem let moe, Israel kacoehtanawk to kawk pacoengah, Angraeng mah anih khaeah thuih ih loknawk to nihcae hmaa ah thuih pae boih.
\v 8 Kaminawk mah, Angraeng mah thuih ih lok to ka sak o boih han, tiah nawnto a thuih o. Nihcae ih lok to Mosi mah Angraeng khaeah tathlangh pae let.
\v 9 Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah, Khenah, nang hoi thuih ih lok kaminawk mah thaih o moe, nang to dungzan khoek to tang o thai hanah, tamai thung hoi nang khaeah kang zoh han, tiah a naa. Kaminawk mah thuih ih loknawk to Mosi mah Angraeng khaeah tathlangh pae.
\v 10 To pacoengah Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah, Kaminawk khaeah caeh ah loe, nihcae to vaihni hoi khawnbang ah ciimcaisak ah; angmacae ih khukbuennawk to pasuk o nasoe loe,
\v 11 ni thumto naah om o coek nasoe; ni thumto naah loe kaminawk boih hmaa ah, Sinai mae nuiah Angraeng to anghum tathuk tih.
\v 12 \x - \xo 19:12 \xt Heb 12.18-20.\x*Kaminawk mah mae sang to poeng o han ai ah sah paeh, mae sang nuiah daw o hmah, mae sang amtonghaih long doeh sui o hmah; mae sang to ban hoi sui kami loe paduek tangtang ah om tih.
\v 13 Anih to ban hoi sui hmah, sui kami loe thlung hoi vah maat ai boeh loe, palaa hoi kah maat han oh; kami maw, to tih ai boeh loe moi maw hing o sak hmah, tiah a thuih, tiah thui paeh; atue kasawk ah mongkah ueng pacoengah ni, kaminawk to mae nuiah daw o vop tih, tiah a naa.
\v 14 Mosi mae nui hoi kaminawk khaeah anghum tathuk pacoengah, kaminawk to amprik caisak; nihcae mah khukbuennawk to pasuk o.
\v 15 To pacoengah kaminawk khaeah, Ni thumto hanah amsak o coek ah, na zunawk khaeah iip o hmah, tiah a naa.
\p 
\v 16 \x - \xo 19:16 \xt Lph 4.5.\x*\x - \xo 19:16 \xt Deu 4.11,12.\x*Ni thumto akhawnbang ah loe, khopazih hoi tangphra to puek moe, kathah parai tamai mah mae to khuk khoep, mongkah lok loe tuen parai pongah, ataihaih im ah kaom kaminawk to tasoeh o boih.
\v 17 To naah Mosi mah Sithaw tongh hanah, kaminawk to ataihaih im hoiah caeh haih, nihcae loe mae tlim ah angdoet o.
\v 18 To naah Angraeng loe hmai thung hoiah angzoh pongah, Sinai mae to hmaikhue mah ayaw hmoek; takoeng hoi tacawt hmaikhue baktih toengah, mae to anghuenh boih.
\v 19 Mongkah to kasawkah ueng naah, lok to len aep aep; Mosi mah lok to thuih, to naah Sithaw mah lok hoiah pathim pae.
\v 20 Angraeng loe Sinai mae nuiah anghum tathuk moe, Mosi to mae nuiah kawk; to pongah Mosi loe dawh tahang.
\v 21 Angraeng mah anih khaeah, Kaminawk loe Angraeng khet hanah caeh o nganga moe, a duek o han ai ah, anghum tathuk ah loe kaminawk to thuitaek ah.
\v 22 Angraeng khaeah angzo qaima boih angmacae hoi angmacae to amprik cai o nasoe; to tih ai nahaeloe Angraeng mah nihcae to thuitaek moeng tih, tiah a naa.
\v 23 Mosi mah Angraeng khaeah, Kaminawk mah mae to poeng o han ai ah angzithaih ramri to sah paeh loe, amprik caisak ah, tiah na thuih pongah, kaminawk Sinai mae nuiah angzo o thai ai, tiah a naa.
\v 24 Angraeng mah caeh tathuk ah loe, Aaron to angzo haih ah; toe qaimanawk hoi kaminawk loe Angraeng khaeah angzo o nganga hmah nasoe; to tih ai nahaeloe nihcae to danpaekhaih tong o moeng tih, tiah a naa.
\v 25 To pongah Mosi loe kaminawk khaeah anghum tathuk moe, lok to thuih pae.
\c 20
\s1 Kaalok ha to
\p 
\v 1 Hae loknawk boih Sithaw mah thuih;
\v 2 kai loe misong ah na ohhaih, Izip prae thung hoi nangcae zaehoikung, Angraeng Sithaw ah ka oh.
\v 3 Ka hmaa ah Sithaw kalah tawn hmah.
\v 4 \x - \xo 20:4 \xt EXO 34.17; LEV 19.4; 26.1; Deu 4.15-18; 27.15.\x*Van ranui ah kaom krang maw, to tih ai boeh loe long tlim ah kaom krang maw, to tih ai boeh loe tui thungah kaom hmuen hoi kanghmong, kawbaktih krang doeh sah hmah;
\v 5 \x - \xo 20:5 \xt EXO 34.6,7; NAM 14.18; Deu 7.9,10.\x*nihcae hmaa ah akuep o hmah loe, bok o hmah; na Angraeng Sithaw, Kai loe ut panoek Sithaw ah ka oh moe, kai hnuma ampanawk ih zaehaih pongah, a caanawk adung thumto hoi palito karoek to thuitaekkung ah ka oh.
\v 6 Toe kai palung moe, ka thuih ih lok pazui kaminawk loe a caanawk ih adung sangto pong kapop adung khoek to amlunghaih patuekkung ah ka oh.
\v 7 \x - \xo 20:7 \xt LEV 19.12.\x*Avang ai ah na Angraeng Sithaw ih ahmin to patoh hmah; anih ih ahmin tidoeh na ai ah patoh rumram kami loe, Angraeng mah anih to khen sut mak ai.
\v 8 \x - \xo 20:8 \xt EXO 16.23-30; 31.12-14.\x*Sabbath ni to ciimsak hanah pakuem poe ah.
\v 9 \x - \xo 20:9 \xt EXO 23.12; 31.15; 34.21; 35.2; LEV 23.3.\x*Ni tarukto thung toksah ah, na tok to sah boih ah.
\v 10 Toe ni sarihto naah loe, na Angraeng Sithaw ih Sabbath niah oh; to niah loe tih tok doeh sah hmah; nangmah doeh, na capa doeh, na canu doeh, na tamna nongpa doeh, na tamna nongpata doeh, na tawnh ih moinawk hoi na khongkha thungah kaom angvin doeh toksak o han om ai;
\v 11 \x - \xo 20:11 \xt Genesis 2.1-3; EXO 31.17.\x*Angraeng mah ni tarukto thung van hoi long, tuipui hoi a thungah kaom hmuennawk boih to sak moe, ni sarihto naah loe anghak; to pongah Angraeng mah Sabbath ni to tahamhoihaih paek moe, ciimcaisak.
\v 12 \x - \xo 20:12 \xt Deu 27.16; Mathai 15.4; 19.19; Mark 7.10; 10.19; Luk 18.20; Efi 6.2; \xt Efi 6.3.\x*Nam no hoi nam pa khingya ah; to tih nahaeloe Angraeng Sithaw mah paek ih, prae thungah hinglung na sawk tih.
\v 13 \x - \xo 20:13 \xt Genesis 9.6; LEV 24.17; Mathai 5.21; 19.18; Mark 10.19; Luk 18.20; Rom 13.9; Jkb 2.11.\x*Kami hum hmah.
\v 14 \x - \xo 20:14 \xt LEV 20.10; Mathai 5.27; 19.18; Mark 10.19; Luk 18.20; Rom 13.9; Jkb 2.11.\x*Zu sava laep ah nongpa nongpata zaehaih sah hmah.
\v 15 \x - \xo 20:15 \xt LEV 19.11; Mathai 19.18; Mark 10.19; Luk 18.20; Rom 13.9.\x*Paqu hmah.
\v 16 \x - \xo 20:16 \xt EXO 23.1; Mathai 19.18; Mark 10.19; Luk 18.20.\x*Na imtaeng kami nuiah amsawn hnukung ah angdoe hmah.
\v 17 \x - \xo 20:17 \xt Rom 7.7; 13.9.\x*Na imtaeng kami ih im to khit hmah; na imtaeng kami ih zu to khit hmah, to tih ai boeh loe anih ih tamna nongpa, to tih ai boeh loe anih ih tamna nongpata, anih ih maitaw doeh, anih ih laa hrang doeh, na imtaeng kami ih kawbaktih hmuen doeh khit hmah, tiah lok a paek.
\v 18 \x - \xo 20:18 \xt Heb 12.18,19.\x*Khopazih tuen, tangphrapuekhaih hoi mongkah lok to kaminawk mah thaih o, mae thung hoi tacawt hmaikhue to a hnuk o naah, angnawn o moe, kangthla ah angdoet o.
\v 19 Mosi khaeah, Kaicae khae lok na thui ah, kang tahngaih pae o han; Sithaw mah kaicae khaeah lokthui hmah nasoe, ka dueh o moeng tih, tiah a naa o.
\v 20 Mosi mah kaminawk khaeah, Zii o hmah; mikhmai ah anih zithaih na tawnh o moe, zaehaih na sak o han ai ah, nangcae tanoek han ih Sithaw angzoh tathuk boeh, tiah a naa.
\s1 Long hoi sak ih hmaicam
\p 
\v 21 Kaminawk loe kangthla ah angdoet o, toe Mosi loe Sithaw ohhaih kathah parai tamai kamnum ohhaih bangah a caeh.
\v 22 To naah Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah, Israel kaminawk khaeah, Kai mah van hoiah kang thuih ih lok to na hnuk o boeh, tiah thui paeh, tiah a naa.
\v 23 Kai nang bok o naah, nangmacae hanah sui sithaw doeh, sum kanglung sithaw doeh sah o hmah.
\v 24 Kai hanah long hoiah hmaicam mae to sah ah loe, to long hmaicam nuiah hmai angbawnhaih, angdaeh angbawnhaih to tuu hoi maitaw taenawk hoiah sah ah; kai ih ahmin pakoehhaih ahmuen kruekah, nang khaeah kang zoh moe, tahamhoihaih kang paek han.
\v 25 \x - \xo 20:25 \xt Deu 27.5-7; Josh 8.31.\x*Kai hanah thlung hmaicam to na sak nahaeloe, thuk ih thlung kangphaek nuiah hmaicam to sah hmah; thlung kangphaek thukhaih sum to na phok tahang naah, hmaicam to nam hnongsak ah oh boeh.
\v 26 Bangkrai ah na ohhaih amtueng han ai ah, hmaicam ranui ah dawhhaih thlak to sah hmah, tiah a naa.
\c 21
\p 
\v 1 Hae daan hae nihcae hmaa ah suem paeh;
\v 2 \x - \xo 21:2 \xt LEV 25.39-46.\x*Hebru kami to tamna ah na qan nahaeloe, anih mah saning tarukto thung na tok to sah tih; toe saning sarihto naah loe, atho tidoeh hni ai ah loihsak han oh.
\v 3 Angmah bueng tamna ah om nahaeloe, angmah bueng loih han oh; to kami loe zu tawn nahaeloe, a zu hoi nawnto loih tih.
\v 4 Angmah ih angraeng mah anih han zu to lak pae moe, caa nongpa maw, to tih ai boeh loe canu maw sah nahaeloe, anih ih caanawk loe angmah angraeng ih hmuen ah om tih; a tamna loe angmah bueng ah loih tih.
\v 5 Toe a tamna mah, Ka Angraeng, ka zu hoi ka caanawk to palung pongah, tacawt han koeh ai, tiah thui nahaeloe,
\v 6 angmah ih angraeng mah anih to lokcaekkungnawk hmaa ah caeh haih tih; anih mah khongkha, to tih ai boeh loe khongkha tung ohhaih ahmuen ah caeh haih ueloe, angmah ih angraeng mah a tamna ih naa to moihin aqawthaih phungvang hoiah aqawt pae tih, to tiah anih loe a hing thung angraeng ih tamna ah om tih.
\p 
\v 7 Kami maeto mah a canu to tamna ah zaw nahaeloe, to nongpata to nongpa baktiah prawt sut han om ai.
\v 8 Anih qankung angraeng mah to nongpata to zu ah lak han koeh ai nahaeloe, angmah hoi angmah to angkrangsak ah; angraeng mah to nongpata to aling pongah, kalah prae kami khaeah zaw thai mak ai.
\v 9 To nongpata to a capa han paek nahaeloe, anih to a canu baktiah khet han oh.
\v 10 Anih mah kalah nongpata to zu ah la let nahaeloe, hmaloe ih a zu nongpata ih caaknaek maw, to tih ai boeh loe sava sak nathuem ih khukbuen maw, khring pae han om ai.
\v 11 Hae hmuen thumto sah ai nahaeloe, tangka paek angaih ai ah, nongpata to loih han oh.
\s1 Kami hum han sak ih daan
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 21:12 \xt LEV 24.17.\x*Minawk hum kami loe, paduek han oh.
\v 13 \x - \xo 21:13 \xt NAM 35.10-34; Deu 19.1-13; Josh 20.1-9.\x*Pacaenghaih om ai ah, anih ban ah Sithaw mah to kami to paek nahaeloe, anih cawnhaih ahmuen ka suek pae han.
\v 14 Toe pacaenghaih hoiah a imtaeng kami to hum nahaeloe, ka hmaicam ah abuep cadoeh anih loe duek han oh.
\p 
\v 15 Amno hoi ampa hum kami loe, paduek han oh.
\v 16 \x - \xo 21:16 \xt Deu 24.7.\x*Kami paqu kami loe, kami to zawh maw, to tih ai boeh loe angmah ban ah maw suem cadoeh, paduek han oh.
\v 17 \x - \xo 21:17 \xt LEV 20.9; Mathai 15.4; Mark 7.10.\x*Amno hoi ampa tangoeng kami loe paduek han oh.
\v 18 Kami hnik loe angpan hoi moe, maeto mah kalah maeto thlung hoiah vah maw, to tih ai boeh loe ban pathluem moe a thong, toe to kami loe dueh ai, iihkhun nuiah angsong sut,
\v 19 toe to kami loe angthawk moe, cunghet hoiah lam caeh thaih nahaeloe, anih bop kami to loihsak han oh; toe to kami loe ahmaa ca nahaeloe, ngantui ai ah a oh nathung, patoh ih kaboeng hmuennawk boih to laem tih.
\p 
\v 20 Kami maeto mah a tamna nongpa maw, nongpata maw boh pongah dueh nahaeloe, anih to danpaek han oh.
\v 21 Toe tamna to dueh ai moe, ni hnetto maw, ni thumto maw oh pacoengah angthawk let nahaeloe, a tamna loe anih ih phoisa ah oh pongah, bop kami to danpaek han om ai.
\p 
\v 22 Nongpa hnik loe angpan hoi naah, zokpomh nongpata to nganbawh kana paek hoi moeng pongah, nawkta to khrah akoep ai ah zun moeng nahaeloe, nongpata ih sava mah thuih ih baktih toengah, danpaek han oh; lokcaekkung mah thuih ih baktih toengah paek tih.
\v 23 Toe kalah ahmaa casak nahaeloe, hinghaih to hinghaih hoiah pathok han oh.
\v 24 \x - \xo 21:24 \xt LEV 24.19,20; Deu 19.21; Mathai 5.38.\x*Mik pongah mik, haa pongah haa, ban pongah ban, khok pongah khok,
\v 25 hmai hoi thlaek pongah hmai hoi thlaek, ahmaa caksak pongah ahmaa caksak, nganbawh kana paek pongah nganbawh kana paek han oh.
\p 
\v 26 Kami maeto mah a tamna nongpa maw, nongpata maw mik ah boh pongah, mik amro nahaeloe, mik amrosak kami to danpaekhaih thung hoi loihsak han oh.
\v 27 Kami maeto mah a tamna nongpata maw, to tih ai boeh loe nongpa ih haa maw, angkhaeksak nahaeloe, haa angkhaehsak pongah tamna to loihsak han oh.
\p 
\v 28 Maitaw tae mah nongpa maw, nongpata maw takhueng moe, dueh nahaeloe, maitaw tae to thlung hoi vah maat han oh; to maitaw moi to caak han om ai; toe maitaw tawnkung loe loihsak han oh.
\v 29 Toe to maitaw tae loe canghnii ah kami daeng vai boeh, tito maitaw tawnkung khaeah thuih pae boeh, toe tawnkung mah kahoih ah khenzawn ai pongah, nongpa maw, nongpata maw takhueng maat bae nahaeloe, maitaw tae to thlung hoi vah maat pacoengah, tawnkung doeh paduek han oh.
\v 30 Toe phoisa rong nasoe, tiah thui o nahaeloe, thuih ih lok baktih toengah, a hinghaih to pahlong moe, atho rongsak han oh.
\v 31 Maitaw tae mah capa maw, canu maw daeng nahaeloe, lokcaekhaih baktih toengah sak han oh.
\v 32 Maitaw tae mah tamna nongpa maw, nongpata maw daeng nahaeloe, maitaw tae tawnkung mah maitaw tawnkung hanah phoisa shekel qui thumto paek pacoengah, maitaw tae to thlung hoi vah maat han oh.
\p 
\v 33 Kami maeto mah tangqom to aphroe moe, suek sut maw, to tih ai boeh loe tangqom to takaeh moe, kraeng ai ah suek sut pongah, maitaw tae maw, laa hrang maw krah moeng nahaeloe,
\v 34 tangqom toepkung mah maitaw hoi laa hrang ih atho to rong ueloe, kadueh maitaw to la tih.
\p 
\v 35 Kami maeto ih maitaw tae mah minawk kalah ih maitaw tae to daeng moe, dueh nahaeloe, kahing maitaw tae to zaw hoi ueloe, atho amzet hoi pacoengah, kadueh maitaw tae ih atho doeh kangvan ah amzet hoi tih.
\v 36 Toe to ih maitaw tae loe hmawhsaeng parai moe, canghnii ah doeh maitawnawk daeng tuektuek boeh, tiah panoek boeh, toe tawnkung mah pathlet ai ah suem sut nahaeloe, kadueh maitaw to angmah la ueloe, maitaw tae hoiah rong pae let tih.
\c 22
\s1 Hmuenmae daan
\p 
\v 1 Kami maeto mah maitaw tae maw, to tih ai boeh loe tuu maw, paquk moe boh ving, to tih ai boeh loe zaw ving nahaeloe, maitaw tae maeto zuengah maitaw tae pangato, tuu maeto zuengah tuu palito hoi rong han oh.
\p 
\v 2 Kamqu mah im muk nathuem ah kamqu to bop maat nahaeloe, a nuiah athii palonghaih om mak ai.
\v 3 Toe ni tacawt boeh nahaeloe, athii longsak pongah anih loe zae ah oh; kamqu loe paqukhaih atho to rong tih; toe tidoeh tawn ai nahaeloe, paqukhaih atho rong hanah angmah to angzawh han oh.
\v 4 A paquk ih maitaw maw, to tih ai boeh loe laa hrang maw, to tih ai boeh loe tuu maw angmah ban ah hing vop nahaeloe, alet hnetto rong let tih.
\p 
\v 5 Kami mah a tawnh ih moinawk to lawk ah maw, to tih ai boeh loe misur takha thungah maw pratsak, toe kahoih ah toep ai pongah, minawk ih lawk to caa nahaeloe, a lawk hoi misur takha thung ih kahoih koek hmuen hoiah pathok let tih.
\p 
\v 6 Hmai thlaek naah hmai to cawnh moe, lawk ih cangqui maw, to tih ai boeh loe cangkung maw, to tih ai boeh loe lawk to kangh boih nahaeloe, hmai thlaek kami mah rong let tih.
\p 
\v 7 Kami maeto mah a imtaeng kami khaeah phoisa maw, hmuen maw pakuemsak, toe anih imthung hoiah kamqu mah paquk pae ving moe, kamqu to naeh nahaeloe, anih mah alet hnetto rong nasoe.
\v 8 Toe kamqu to hnu ai nahaeloe, im tawnkung mah a imtaeng ih hmuen to lak maw, la ai, tito panoek hanah, anih to lokcaekkungnawk hmaa ah kawk moe, lokcaek han oh.
\p 
\v 9 Kami maeto mah maitaw tae maw, laa hrang maw, tuu maw, khukbuen maw, to tih ai boeh loe kanghmaa hmuen maw amsoem ai ah, Hae hmuen loe kai ih ni, tiah thui nahaeloe, nihnik to lokcaekkung khaeah caeh haih hmaek han oh; lokcaekkungnawk mah paqu kami ah net ih kami mah a imtaeng kami hanah alet hnetto pathok pae tih.
\p 
\v 10 Kami maeto mah laa hrang maw, to tih ai boeh loe maitaw tae maw, to tih ai boeh loe tuu maw, to tih ai boeh loe kawbaktih moi doeh toepsak hanah a imtaeng kami khaeah aap, toe to moi to duek ving maw, to tih ai boeh loe ahmaa cak maw, to tih ai boeh loe minawk kalah mah huih ving pongah, mi mah doeh hnu ai nahaeloe,
\v 11 moi toepsak kami mah, a imtaeng kami ih hmuen to ka la ai tiah, Angraeng hmaa ah lokkam nahaeloe, nihnik salak lokpunghaih to boengsak han oh; moi tawnkung mah to lok to talawk han oh, moi toep kami doeh rongsak han om ai.
\v 12 Toe a imtaeng kami mah to moi to paqu nahaeloe, moi toep kami mah tawnkung hanah rong pae tih.
\v 13 Toep ih moi to kalah moisan mah kaek ving nahaeloe, moisan mah kaek ving boeh, tiah hnukung to kawk ah, to tiah nahaeloe moisan mah kaek ving pongah atho rong mak ai.
\p 
\v 14 Kami maeto mah hmuen maeto a imtaeng kami khaeah tlai, tawnkung om ai naah ahmaa cak, to tih ai boeh loe dueh ving nahaeloe, tlai kami mah pathok let tih.
\v 15 Toe tawnkung om toeng nahaeloe, tlaikung mah pathok mak ai; toe atho hoiah tlai nahaeloe, tawnkung mah tlaihaih atho khue to hnik han oh.
\s1 Kami mae to khosakhaih daan
\p 
\v 16 \x - \xo 22:16 \xt Deu 22.28,29.\x*Sava sak han ai ah lokkamhaih sah nongpata to nongpa maeto mah pacae khing moe, iip haih nahaeloe, nongpata avang to paek ueloe, nongpata to zu ah la tih.
\v 17 Nongpata ih ampa mah a canu to anih zusak han koeh ai cadoeh, anih mah tangla ih avang to paek toengtoeng tih.
\p 
\v 18 \x - \xo 22:18 \xt Deu 18.10,11.\x*Ma-uih loe hingsak han om ai.
\p 
\v 19 \x - \xo 22:19 \xt LEV 18.23; 20.15,16; Deu 27.21.\x*Mi kawbaktih doeh pacah ih moi hoiah zaehaih sah kami loe hum han roe oh.
\p 
\v 20 \x - \xo 22:20 \xt Deu 17.2-7.\x*Angraeng khae khue na ai ah, kalah sithaw khaeah angbawnhaih sah kami loe, paduek han oh.
\p 
\v 21 \x - \xo 22:21 \xt EXO 23.9; LEV 19.33,34; Deu 24.17,18; 27.19.\x*Angvin to pacaekthlaek hmah; anih to hnap doeh hnap hmah; nangcae doeh Izip prae thungah angvin ah ni na oh o toeng.
\v 22 Lamhmainawk, to tih ai boeh loe naqahnawk to pacaekthlaek hmah.
\v 23 Na pacaekthlaek pongah, nihcae mah kai khaeah qah o nahaeloe, nihcae qahhaih lok to ka tahngaih pae han.
\v 24 Palung ka phui moe, nangcae sumsen hoiah kang hum o han; na zunawk to lamhmai ah om o ueloe, na caanawk doeh ampa tawn ai ah om o tih.
\p 
\v 25 \x - \xo 22:25 \xt LEV 25.35-38; Deu 15.7-11; 23.19,20.\x*Na imtaeng ah kaom kamtang kai ih kaminawk khaeah phoisa na coisak nahaeloe, a caa kangpung paek hanah coisak hmah; kapung acaa na lak han om ai.
\v 26 \x - \xo 22:26 \xt Deu 24.10-13.\x*Na imtaeng kaminawk mah nang khaeah a khukbuen pawng nahaeloe, niduem ai naah thaak pae let ah;
\v 27 anih loe a takpum padap hanah to khukbuen khue ni a tawnh; to tih ai nahaeloe a iih naah, timaw angkhuk tih? Anih mah kai khaeah hang nahaeloe, kai loe minawk tahmen thaih kami ah ka oh pongah, a hanghaih lok to ka tahngaih pae han.
\p 
\v 28 \x - \xo 22:28 \xt Tsk 23.5.\x*sithawnawk to kasae thui hmah loe, nangmacae kami ukkung doeh tangoeng hmah.
\p 
\v 29 Kahmin tangsuek thingthai hoi na pasawh tangsuek ih thingthai tui to akra ai ah paek ah, hawk ving hmah; na caanawk thungah tapen tangsuek calu to na paek ah.
\v 30 To baktih toengah, maitaw tae hoi tuu doeh paek ah; amno khaeah ni sarihto omsak loe, ni tazetto naah kai khaeah na paek ah.
\p 
\v 31 \x - \xo 22:31 \xt LEV 17.15.\x*Nangcae loe kai khaeah ciimcai kami ah na om o tih; to pongah taw ah moisan mah kaek ih moi to caa o hmah; uinawk han paek oh.
\c 23
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 23:1 \xt EXO 20.16; LEV 19.11,12; Deu 5.20.\x*Amsawnlok to haeh hmah; katoeng ai kami hoi amyok hmah loe, amsawn lok hnukung ah angdoe hmah.
\v 2 Kasae hmuen sak hanah minawk hnuk ah bang hmah; lokcaekhaih hmuen ah nang doet naah, toenghaih amkhraeng taak hanah kapop kaminawk bang ah angdoe hmah;
\v 3 \x - \xo 23:3 \xt LEV 19.15.\x*lokcaek naah kamtang kami doeh mikhmai khen hmah.
\p 
\v 4 \x - \xo 23:4 \xt Deu 22.1-4.\x*Lam amkhraeng na misa ih maitaw tae maw, to tih ai boeh loe laa hrang maw na hnuk nahaeloe, angmah khaeah thaak pae let ah.
\v 5 Nang hnuma kami ih laa hrang to hmuen kazit mah taeh caeng nahaeloe, caehtaak hmah, anih to abom ah.
\p 
\v 6 \x - \xo 23:6 \xt LEV 19.15; Deu 16.19.\x*Kamtang nangmah ih kami to lok na caek naah, amsoem ai ah lokcaek hmah.
\v 7 Katoeng ai hmuen to ayae oh; kaom duem kami hoi zaehaih tawn ai kami to hum hmah; zaehaih sah kasae kami loe ka prawt sut mak ai.
\v 8 Bokhaih ah paek ih tangqum to talawk hmah; bokhaih mah palungha kami ih mik to maengsak moe, katoeng kami ih lok to angkawnsak.
\p 
\v 9 \x - \xo 23:9 \xt EXO 22.21; LEV 19.33,34; Deu 24.17,18; 27.19.\x*Angvin to pacaekthlaek hmah; nangcae doeh Izip prae ah angvin ah na oh o pongah, angvin ih palungthin to na panoek o.
\s1 Sabbath daan
\p 
\v 10 \x - \xo 23:10 \xt LEV 25.1-7.\x*Saning tarukto thung lawk sah oh loe, cang to aat oh;
\v 11 toe saning sarihto naah loe lawk sah ai ah, lawk hmuen to anghaksak ah loe, kongsak ah; nangmacae thung ih amtang kaminawk mah caaknaek pakronghaih ah patoh o nasoe loe; nihcae mah caehtaak ih kanghmat to moinawk mah caa o nasoe. To tiah misur takha hoi olive takha doeh sah oh.
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 23:12 \xt EXO 20.9-11; 31.15; 34.21; 35.2; LEV 23.3; Deu 5.13,14.\x*Ni tarukto thung nangmah ih tok to sah ah loe, ni sarihto naah loe anghak ah; nangmah ih maitaw tae hoi laa hrang doeh anghak ueloe, na imthung ah tapen na tamnanawk hoi angvin doeh anghak o nasoe.
\v 13 Kang thuih o ih loknawk boih pongah acoe oh; kalah sithawnawk ih ahmin to thui o hmah; na pakha hoi thuih ih lok doeh minawk han thaih o sak hmah.
\s1 Buh raenghaih daan
\p 
\v 14 Saningto naah vai thumto buh raenghaih to sah oh.
\v 15 \x - \xo 23:15 \xt EXO 12.14-20; LEV 23.6-8; NAM 28.17-25.\x*Taeh thuh ai ih buh raenghaih poih to sah oh; (kang paek o ih lok baktih toengah, atue khaeh ih Abib khrah thungah, ni sarihto thung taeh thuh ai ih takaw caakhaih poih to sah oh; nangcae loe to khrah naah ni Izip prae thung hoiah na tacawt o; to buh raenghaih poih sak nathung, mi kawbaktih doeh ka hmaa ah bangkrai ah angphong han om ai:)
\v 16 \x - \xo 23:16 \xt LEV 23.15-21; NAM 28.26-31; \xt LEV 23.39-43.\x*cangrawt tue ih poih loe na lawk thung hoi tacawt kathai tangsuek thingthai qumponawk hoiah sah oh loe, lawksak pacoeng, thingthai qumponawk lakhaih tue ah doeh sah oh.
\v 17 Nangcae thung ih nongpa boih saningto naah vai thumto Angraeng hmaa ah angphong oh.
\p 
\v 18 Angbawnhaih moi thii hoi taeh thuh ih takaw to nawnto na paek hmah. Angbawnhaih moithawk to akhawnbang khoek to anghmatsak hmah.
\v 19 \x - \xo 23:19 \xt Deu 26.2; EXO 34.26; Deu 14.21.\x*Na lawk thung ih hmaloe koek kathai kahoih koek thingthai to na Angraeng Sithaw im ah sin ah; maeh caa to amno ih tahnutui hoiah thong hmah.
\s1 Sithaw mah khetzawnhaih
\p 
\v 20 Khenah, ka sak ih ahmuen ah kang caeh o haih hanah, loklam ah nangcae khenzawnkung, van kami nangcae hmaa ah ka patoeh.
\v 21 Anih to khingya ah, a thuih ih lok to tahngai ah; anih to aek hmah; anih thungah Ka hmin oh pongah, anih mah na zaehaih to tahmen mak ai.
\p 
\v 22 Toe a lok kahoih ah na tahngaih moe, ka thuih ih loknawk boih na sak nahaeloe, na misanawk to ka misa ah om tih, nangcae pakaa kaminawk to ka pakaa han.
\p 
\v 23 Kai ih van kami to nangcae hmaa ah caeh ueloe, nangcae to Amor, Hit, Periz, Kanaan, Hiv hoi Jebus kaminawk ih prae ah na caeh haih tih; nihcae to kam rosak boih han.
\v 24 Nihcae ih sithawnawk hmaa ah akuep hmah, bok hmah loe, nihcae ih tok doeh sah hmah; to hmuennawk to phrae ah loe, krangnawk doeh phrae boih ah.
\v 25 Nang ih takaw hoi tui to tahamhoihaih ang paek hanah, na Angraeng Sithaw to bok oh; na tak thung ih nathaih doeh kang lak pae ving tih.
\v 26 Na prae thungah, caa kamro hoi caa kaak maeto doeh om mak ai; na hing thung khosakhaih ka koepsak han.
\v 27 Kai zithaih nangcae hmaa ah ka patoeh moe, na phak o ih ahmuen kruekah kaom kaminawk to kam rosak han; na misanawk to hnukbang ah kam laemsak boih han.
\v 28 Hiv, Kanaan hoi Hit kaminawk to haek hanah, nangcae hmaa ah khoilangae to ka patoeh han.
\v 29 Saningto thungah to kaminawk to nangcae hmaa hoi ka haek mak ai; to tiah ka sak nahaeloe prae thungah kami angqai krang ueloe, taw ih moinawk to pung o aep moeng tih.
\v 30 Nang pung o moe, prae thung boih na koi o ai karoek to, to kaminawk to zetta, zetta hoiah ni ka haek han.
\v 31 Na ramri loe tuipui kathim hoiah Philistin tuipui karoek to, praezaek hoiah vapui khoek to ka suek han; to prae thungah kaom kaminawk to na ban ah kang paek han, nangmacae hmaa hoiah nihcae to na haek o tih.
\v 32 Nihcae hoi maw nihcae ih sithawnawk hoiah maw lokkamhaih to sah hmah.
\v 33 Nihcae mah ka nuiah zaehaih ang sak o sak han ai ah, nihcae to na prae thungah omsak hmah; nihcae ih sithawnawk to na bok nahaeloe, nang han patung ih thaang ah om tih, tiah a naa.
\c 24
\s1 Lokkamhaih cak
\p 
\v 1 To pacoengah Mosi khaeah, Nangmah hoi Aaron, Nadab, Abihu hoi Israel kacoehta qui sarihto Angraeng khaeah angzo o tahang ah, nihcae loe ahmuen kangthla hoiah bok o nasoe.
\v 2 Mosi khue ni Angraeng taengah caeh tih; kalah kaminawk loe a taengah caeh o hmah; kaminawk doeh anih hoi nawnto caeh o hmah nasoe, tiah a naa.
\p 
\v 3 Mosi mah caeh moe, kaminawk khaeah lokcaekhaih hoi Angraeng ih loknawk boih to thuih naah, kaminawk boih mah, Angraeng mah thuih ih lok to ka sak o boih han, tiah nawnto a thuih o.
\v 4 Angraeng mah thuih ih loknawk boih loe Mosi mah tarik; khawnbang khawnthaw ah angthawk moe, mae tlim ah hmaicam maeto a sak pacoengah, Israel acaeng hathlai hnetto angmathaih thlung hathlai hnetto a tling.
\v 5 To pacoengah anih mah Israel thendoengnawk to patoeh, nihcae mah maitaw tae to lak o moe, Angraeng khaeah hmai angbawnhaih hoi angdaeh angbawnhaih to a sak o.
\v 6 Mosi mah athii ahap to lak moe, boengloeng pongah suek; athii ahap lak moe, hmaicam nuiah a haeh.
\v 7 Anih mah lokmaihaih cabu to lak pacoengah, kaminawk hanah kroek pae; kaminawk mah Angraeng mah thuih ih loknawk to ka sak o boih moe, lok ka tahngai o han, tiah a naa o.
\v 8 \x - \xo 24:8 \xt Mathai 26.28; Mark 14.24; Luk 22.20; 1 Korin 11.25; Heb 10.29; \xt Heb 9.19,20.\x*To pacoengah Mosi mah athii to lak moe, kaminawk nuiah haeh pacoengah, Khenah, hae ih loknawk baktih toengah, hae loe Angraeng mah nangcae hoi sak ih lokmaihaih athii ah oh, tiah a naa.
\p 
\v 9 Mosi, Aaron, Nadab, Abihu hoi Israel kacoehta qui sarihtonawk loe caeh o tahang moe,
\v 10 Israel Sithaw to a hnuk o; a khok atlim bangah loe sapphire thlung kanglung hoi baih het ih hmuen baktiah oh moe, kacai pin van baktiah amdueng.
\v 11 Toe Sithaw loe Israel kacoehtanawk bangah ban payangh ai; nihcae mah Sithaw to hnuk o, a caak o moe, naek o.
\p 
\v 12 Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah, Kai khaeah mae ah angzo tahang ah loe, haeah om ah; kaminawk to na patuk hanah, thlung kangphaek nuiah ka tarik ih, lokpaekhaih hoi kaalok to kang paek han, tiah a naa.
\v 13 To pacoengah Mosi loe anih bomkung Joshua hoi nawnto amsak hoi; Mosi loe Sithaw ih mae ah dawh tahang.
\v 14 Anih mah kacoehtanawk khaeah, Nangcae khae kang zo hoi let ai karoek to haeah na zing oh; khenah, Aaron hoi Hur loe nangcae hoi nawnto oh; lokthuih han tawn kami loe nihnik khaeah caeh oh, tiah a naa.
\p 
\v 15 Mosi mae ah caeh tahang naah, mae loe tamai mah khuk khoep.
\v 16 Angraeng lensawkhaih loe Sinai mae ah oh; ni tarukto thung tamai mah mae to khuk khoep; ni sarihto naah loe Angraeng mah Mosi to tamai thung hoiah kawk.
\v 17 Angraeng lensawkhaih loe, Israel kaminawk mikhnuk ah mae nuiah kangqong hmai baktiah aang.
\v 18 \x - \xo 24:18 \xt Deu 9.9.\x*Mosi loe tamai thungah caeh moe, mae nui a phak pacoengah, to ah ni qui palito hoi qum qui palito oh.
\c 25
\s1 Lokkam caksakhaih
\p 
\v 1 Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah,
\v 2 Israel kaminawk mah Kai khaeah hmuen sin o hanah thui paeh, tiah a naa. Kami boih mah palung huemhaih hoiah paek ih hmuen to kai hanah talawk ah.
\v 3 Nihcae khae hoi na lak han ih hmuennawk loe sui, sum kanglung hoi sum kamling,
\v 4 rong kam-iing, rong kamling hup hoi kathim kahni, puu tlangqui hoi maeh mui,
\v 5 kamling tui nup ih tuu tae ih ahin hoi caham hin, shittim thing,
\v 6 hmai paanghaih situi, bawh ih hmuihoih situi, hmai thlaek koi hmuihoih,
\v 7 Onyx thlungnawk, qaima ih kahni hoi saoek ah takaek ih thlungnawk to talawk ah.
\v 8 Nangcae salakah ka oh hanah, kai han hmuenciim to sah ah.
\v 9 Kang patuek ih kahni im hoi hmuennawk ih krang baktih toengah sah ah.
\s1 Thingkhong
\p 
\v 10 Kasawk dongto pacoeng ahap, ka kawk dongto pacoeng ahap, ka sang dongto pacoeng ahap kaom, thingkhong maeto shittim thing hoiah sah ah.
\v 11 To thingkhong to sui hoi pazut ah, athung doeh tasa bang doeh sui hoi pazut loe, aqai taeng boih sui hoiah sah ah.
\v 12 Sui hoiah aqai kangbuet luet palito sah ah loe, thingkhong takii palito ah suem boih ah; takii maeto pongah kangbuet luet hnetto suem ah.
\v 13 Shittim thing hoiah aputhaih thing to sah loe, sui tui pazut ah.
\v 14 Thingkhong aput hanah aputhaih thing loe sui hoi sak ih kangbuet luet akhaw thungah hawt ah.
\v 15 Aputhaih thingnawk loe thingkhong aqai ah suek ih kangbuet luet akhaw thungah suem poe ah, azuk ving hmah.
\v 16 To thingkhong thungah kang paek han ih hnukung to suem ah.
\v 17 \x - \xo 25:17 \xt Heb 9.5.\x*Kasawk dong hnetto pacoeng ahap, ka kawk dong maeto pacoeng ahap kaom, palungnathaih tangkhang loe kaciim sui hoiah sah ah.
\v 18 Cherubim hnetto sui hoiah sah loe, angtaeng koek palungnathaih tangkhang suekhaih ahmuen ah suem ah.
\v 19 Cherub maeto loe hae bang ih ahmuen kangtaeng ah suem ah loe, kalah maeto loe ho bang ih kangtaeng ahmuen ah suem ah; cherubim loe hae bang hoi ho bang ih palungnathaih tangkhang taengah suem hmaek ah.
\v 20 Cherubim ih pakhraehnawk to mikhmai kangtong ah suem ah loe, palungnathaih tangkhang bangah anghaesak ah; pakhraeh to phoksak tahang ah loe, palungnathaih tangkhang to pakhraeh hoi khuksak ah.
\v 21 Palungnathaih tangkhang to thingkhong nuiah suemh loe, to thingkhong thungah kang paek ih hnukung to suem ah.
\v 22 Hnukung suekhaih thingkhong nuiah kaom, cherubim hnetto salakah, nang to kang tongh moe, palungnathaih tangkhang ranuih hoiah nang khaeah lok ka thuih han; Israel kaminawk hanah ka paek ih loknawk boih nang khaeah kang paek han.
\s1 Caboi
\p 
\v 23 Kasawk dong hnetto, kakawk dong maeto, kasang dong maeto pacoeng ahap kaom, caboi maeto shittim thing hoiah sah ah.
\v 24 Kaciim sui hoi pazut ah loe, aqai taeng boih sui hoiah sah ah.
\v 25 Aqai karto sah ah loe, aqai taeng boih sui hoiah sah ah.
\v 26 To caboi aqai ah kangbuet luet palito sui hoiah sah loe, akhok palito ranuih caboi takii palito ah suem ah.
\v 27 To sui hoiah sak ih kangbuet luet palito loe, aqai ah oh pongah caboi aput han thing hawthaih akhaw ah om tih.
\v 28 Caboi aputhaih cung to shittim thing hoiah sah loe, to aputhaih thing to sui hoiah pazut ah.
\v 29 To ih caboi ah patoh han ih sabaenawk, kathlahnawk, kraenghaih akhuemnawk, sabae kathuknawk to sah ah; tui bawhhaih boengloeng doeh sui hoiah sah ah.
\v 30 \x - \xo 25:30 \xt LEV 24.5-8.\x*Ka hmaa ih caboi nuiah takaw to suem poe ah.
\s1 Hmaithawk
\p 
\v 31 Hmaithawk paanghaih to kaciim sui hoiah sah loe, tung hoi a bannawk, boengloengnawk, apawk hoi apawk tangmuem krangnawk to soi ah.
\v 32 Hmaithawk paanghaih tung maeto bangah a ban thumto tacawt ueloe, kalah maeto bangah doeh a ban thumto, sangqum boih ah tarukto tacawtsak ah.
\v 33 Hmaithawk paanghaih tung thung hoi tacawt ban thumto oh, a ban maeto naah almond apawk hoi apawk tangmuem baktih kaom, boengloeng krang thumto soi ah loe, kalah ban maeto pongah doeh almond apawk hoi apawk tangmuem baktih kaom, boengloeng krang thumto soi ah; to tiah hmaithawk paanghaih tung hoi tacawt ban tarukto nuiah soi boih ah.
\v 34 Hmai paanghaih tung pongah doeh almond apawk hoi apawk tangmuem baktih kaom, boengloeng krang palito soi han angaih.
\v 35 Hmaithawk paanghaih tung maeto thung hoiah ban tarukto tacawt baktih toengah, a ban maeto atlim ah apawk tangmuem krang maeto, a ban hnetto tlim ah apawk tangmuem krang maeto, a ban thumto tlim ah doeh apawk tangmuem krang maeto soi boih han oh.
\v 36 Apawk tangmuem hoi hmaithawk paanghaih tung hoiah tacawt a bannawk to anghmongsak boih ah; to hmuen to kaciim sui hoiah ah sah boih ah.
\v 37 To pacoengah hmai-im sarihto sah loe, caboi aangsak hanah, hmaiim to paang ah.
\v 38 Taitaeh hoi taitaeh suekhaih doeh kaciim sui hoiah sah ah.
\v 39 Hmai paanghaih tung hoi kalah hmuennawk sak haih boih hanah, sui talent maeto patoh ah.
\v 40 \x - \xo 25:40 \xt Tsk 7.44; Heb 8.5.\x*Mae ah kang patuek ih krang baktih toengah, sak azom ah, tiah a naa.
\c 26
\s1 Kahni im
\p 
\v 1 Kahni im loe rong kam-iing, kamling hup hoi kathim, bantok sak kop kaminawk mah sak ih cherubim kaom, imthung pakaahaih puu ngan kahni hato hoiah sah ah.
\v 2 Imthung pakaahaih kahni loe dong pumphae tazetto sawk moe, dong palito kawk han oh; imthung pakaahaih kahni loe dong tahhaih anghmong boih han oh.
\v 3 Imthung pakaahaih kahni pangato pacong boih ah loe, kalah kahni pangato doeh pacong bae ah.
\v 4 Imthung pakaahaih kahni tasa bang ih, kahni maeto hoi maeto patomhhaih aqai taengah, rong kam-iing hoiah kangbuet luet akhaw to sah ah; kalah kahni pongah doeh kahni maeto hoi maeto paconghaih aqai taengah, to tiah sah let ah.
\v 5 Payang ih kahni maeto pongah kangbuet luet akhaw qui pangato sah loe, kalah kahni paconghaih ahmuen ah doeh kangbuet luet akhaw qui pangato sah let ah.
\v 6 To pacoengah kahni ataephaih doeh sui hoiah qui pangato sah loe, to kahni ataephaih hoiah kahni to maeto pacoeng maeto pacong ah; to naah kahni im maeto ah angcoeng tih.
\p 
\v 7 Kahni im ranuih khuk hanah imthung pakaahaih kahni to maeh mui hoiah sah ah.
\v 8 Imthung pakaahaih kahni loe dong qui thumto sawk moe, dong palito kawksak han oh; kahni hathlaito loe kalen kasawk anghmong boih tih.
\v 9 Kahni pangato to maeto ah pacong ah loe, kalah kahni tarukto doeh maeto ah patomh ah; tarukto haih kahni loe hnetto ah pakhraep ah loe kahni im hmaa ah suem ah.
\v 10 Kahni maeto hoi maeto paconghaih aqai ah kangbuet luet akhaw qui pangato sah loe, kalah kahni maeto patomhhaih aqai ah doeh kangbuet luet akhaw qui pangato sah let ah.
\p 
\v 11 Sum kamling hoiah ataephaih to qui pangato ah sah loe, kangbuet luet akhaw qui pangato pongah pathlet boih ah.
\v 12 Kahni im ah payang ih kamtlai kahni ahap loe, kahni im hnukbang ah bang ah.
\v 13 Kahni im ah payang ih kamthlai kahni loe maeto bangah kasawk dong maeto, kalah maeto bangah doeh kasawk dong maeto om tih; to tiah kamtlai kahni hoiah kahni im to khuk ah.
\v 14 Kahni im khuk hanah tuu hin kamling to patoh ah loe, tuipui caham hin hoiah a nui to khuk ah.
\p 
\v 15 Kahni im tapang to shittim thingphaek hoiah sah ah.
\v 16 Thingphaek maeto loe dong hato sawk moe, dong maeto pacoeng, ahap kawksak han oh.
\v 17 Thingphaek maeto pongah akhok hnetto sah loe, kangvan ah suem ah; to tiah kahni im ih thingphaek boih pongah sah ah.
\v 18 Kahni im aloih bang pakaa hanah thingphaek pumphaeto sah ah;
\v 19 to thingphaek pumphaeto atlim ah thingphaek maeto pongah akhok hnetto pahnut hanah, sum kanglung hoiah akhok pahnuthaih akhaw qui palito sah ah.
\v 20 Kahni im aluek bang pakaa hanah thingphaek pumphaeto suem ah;
\v 21 akhok pahnut hanah sum kanglung hoiah akhaw qui palito sah ah; thingphaek maeto pongah akhok hnetto sah boih ah.
\v 22 Kahni im niduem bangah thingphaek tarukto sah ah.
\v 23 Kahni im boenghaih takii tapang haih hanah, thingphaek hnetto sah ah.
\v 24 Takii hnetto loe atlim hoi ranuih nawnto pacong tahang poe ah loe ahmuen maeto ah caehsak hmaek ah; takii hnetto loe to tiah om tih.
\v 25 Thingphaek tazetto om ueloe, sum kanglung hoi sak ih akhok pahnuthaih ahmuen hathlai tarukto oh han angaih; thingphaek maeto pongah akhok hnetto om ueloe, kalah thingphaek maeto pongah doeh akhok hnetto om toeng tih.
\p 
\v 26 Takraenghaih thing to shittim thing hoiah sah ah; kahni im maeto ah takraenghaih pangato sah ah.
\v 27 Kahni im maeto bangah takraenghaih pangato sah loe, kahni im boenghaih niduem bangah takraenghaih pangato sah let ah.
\v 28 A um takraenghaih thingphaek loe hae bang hoi ho bang boenghaih khoek to phasak ah.
\v 29 Thingphaeknawk loe sui tui hoi pazut boih ah; takraenghaih thingphaek hawthaih ahmuen doeh sui hoiah sah ah; takraenghaih thingphaek doeh sui tui pazut ah.
\v 30 Mae nuiah kang patuek ih krang baktih toengah, kahni im to sah ah.
\p 
\v 31 Pakaahaih kahni loe rong kamiing, kamling hup, kathim puu ngan hoiah sah loe, bantok sak kop kami khaeah cherubim krang to soisak ah;
\v 32 sui tui pazut ih shittim tung palito nuiah, to imthung pakaahaih kahni to bang ah; to tungnawk pongah sui hoi sak ih cakoih baktih kaom racahnawk, sum kanglung hoi sak ih akhok pahnuthaih ahmuen palito sah ah.
\v 33 \x - \xo 26:33 \xt Heb 6.19; 9.3-5.\x*Hnukung suekhaih thingkhong loe kahni hoi pakaa ih imthung ah suek hanah, payang ih kahni to sui hoi sak ih kahni ataephaih atlim ah bang ah; payang ih kahni mah hmuenciim hoi ciimcai koek ahmuen to pakaa khoep tih.
\v 34 Palungnathaih tangkhang loe kaciim koek ahmuen thung ih hnukung thingkhong nuiah suem ah.
\v 35 Payang ih kahni tasa bangah caboi to suem ah loe, kahni im aloih bangah hmaithawk, aluek bangah caboi to mikhmai kangtong ah suem ah.
\p 
\v 36 Kahni im akunhaih pakaa hanah, kahni loe rong kamiing, rong kamling hup hoi kathim puu ngan hoiah sah ah.
\v 37 Payang ih kahni to bangh hanah tung pangato shittim thing hoiah sah ah; to tungnawk to sui tui pazut ah; cakoih baktih kaom racahnawk doeh sui hoi sak han angaih; akhok pahnuthaih ahmuen pangato loe sum kanglung hoiah sah ah.
\c 27
\s1 Hmaicam
\p 
\v 1 Dong pangato ka sawk, dong pangato kawk, hmaicam maeto shittim thing hoiah sah ah; hmaicam loe kasawk hoi kalen anghmong moe, dong thumnto sang han oh.
\v 2 Hmaicam ih taki palito ah takii maeto sah boih loe, hmaicam pong ih takii loe anghmongsak boih ah; hmaicam to sum kamling tui hoiah pazut ah.
\v 3 To ah maiphu sohhaih laomnawk, kathuk sabaenawk, moi sohhaih cakoih baktih kaom sumnawk, hmaitikhaih laomnawk hoi laom sabaenawk boih sum kamling hoiah sah ah.
\v 4 Hmai hawhhaih loe sum kamling hoiah sah ah loe, hmai hawhhaih takii palito nuiah akhaw kangbuet luet to sum kamling hoiah sah ah.
\v 5 Hmai hawhhaih loe hmaicam angkoihaih atlim, a um ah suem ah.
\v 6 Hmaicam aputhaih thing loe shittim thing hoiah sah ah loe, sum kamling tui pazut ah.
\v 7 Hmaicam aputhaih thing loe hmaicam maeto bang hoi kalah maeto bang ih akhaw thungah hawt ah loe, to tiah suem poe ah.
\v 8 Hmaicam um ah akhaw pahoe ah, mae nuiah kang patuek ih krang baktih toengah sah ah.
\s1 Kahni im longhma
\p 
\v 9 Kahni im longhma to sah ah; dong cumvaito kasawk puu kahni hoiah aloih bang to pakaa ah.
\v 10 Tung pumphaeto sah ah loe, sum kamling hoiah tung pahnuthaih ahmuen pumphaeto sah ah, tung pong ih cakoih baktih kaom, sum hoi paehhaihnawk loe sum kamling hoiah sah ah.
\v 11 To baktih toengah aluek bangah doeh dong cumvaito kasawk payang ih kahni to sah ah; sum kamling hoiah tung pumphaeto hoi tung pahnuthaih ahmuen pumphaeto sah ah; tung pong ih cakoih baktih kaom, sum hoi paehhaihnawk loe sum kanglung hoiah sah ah.
\v 12 Longhma niduem bang loe dong qui pangato kawk tih, tung hato oh moe, tung pahnuthaih ahmuen doeh hato sak han oh.
\v 13 Ni tacawthaih ni angyae bang ih longhma doeh dong qui pangato kawk han angaih.
\v 14 Thok maeto bang pakaa hanah, dong hathlai pangato kasawk imthung pakaahaih kahni hoi nawnto ah, tung thumto hoi akhok pahnuthaih ahmuen thumto oh han ngaih.
\v 15 Kalah maeto bangah doeh dong hathlai pangato kasawk, pakaa ih kahni hoi nawnto ah, tung thumto hoi tung pahnuthaih ahmuen thumto oh han angaih.
\v 16 Longhma akunhaih thok taeng pakaa haih hanah rong kamiing, rong kamling hup hoi kathim puu ngan hoiah sak ih dong pumphaeto kasawk kahni to om tih; tung palito om ueloe, tung pahnuthaih ahmuen palito om tih.
\v 17 Sum kanglung hoiah longhma taeng kaom tungnawk hoi paehhaihnawk boih to sah ah; cakoih baktih kaom sum to sum kanglung hoiah sah ah loe, tung pahnuthaih ahmuen leo sum kamling hoiah sah ah.
\v 18 Longhmaa loe kasawk dong cumvaito, kakawk dong qui pangato om ueloe, kasang dong pangato om tih; puu ngan hoi tung pahnuthaih ahmuen loe sum kamling hoiah sah ah.
\v 19 Kahni imthung ah patoh ih hmuennawk boih, toksak naah patoh ih hmuennawk boih, kahni im sakhaih sumnawk boih, longhma ah patoh ih sumnawk boih to sum kamling hoiah sah ah.
\s1 Hmai paanghaih situi
\p 
\v 20 Hmaithawk paang poe thaih hanah, Israel kaminawk khaeah kaciim olive situi sin o hanah thui paeh.
\v 21 Aaron hoi a caanawk mah kaminawk amkhuenghaih kahni imthung, pakaa ih kahni tasa bang kaom hnukung thingkhong hmaa ah, duembang hoi akhawnbang khoek to Angraeng hmaa ah hmai paang o poe thai hanah, hae loe Israel kaminawk mah a caanawk dung khoek to pazui hanah paek ih lok ah om tih.
\c 28
\s1 Qaima ih kahninawk
\p 
\v 1 Anih mah qaima baktiah kai ih tok sak thaih hanah, Israel kaminawk salak hoiah nam ya Aaron, a capa Nadab, Abihu, Eleazer hoi Ithamar cae to, nangmah khaeah kawk ah.
\v 2 Nam ya Aaron lensawkhaih hoi kranghoihaih amtueng thai hanah, kaciim kahninawk to sah paeh.
\v 3 Aaron mah ka hmaa ah qaima toksak thaih moe, anih to pahoe pacoengah ciimsak hanah, ka paek ih palunghahaih tawn bantok sah kop kaminawk mah Aaron ih kahni to sak pae o hanah thui ah.
\v 4 A sak pae o han ih kahni loe, saoek padaphaih, palaeng ah avak ih kahni, anui ah khuk ih kahni, a aem takaek ih laihaw, lumuek hoi kaeng zaenghaih kaziinawk hae ni: nam ya Aaron hoi a capanawk mah qaima baktiah kai ih tok to sak o thai hanah, kaciim kahninawk to sah pae oh.
\p 
\v 5 Nihcae mah sui, rong kamiing, rong kamling hup hoi rong kathim puu ngan kahni to lak han angaih.
\v 6 A lak o ih sui, rong kamiing, rong kamling hup hoi rong kathim puu ngan kahni hoiah palaeng ah avak ih kahni to kahoih ah sah pae oh.
\v 7 To palaeng ah avak ih kahni loe, palaeng hnetto pongah avak han sahsak ah loe, atom hnetto zaeng hanah angqumsak ah.
\v 8 Kahni ranui ah sak ih kahoih kaengkaeh doeh, palaeng ah avak ih kahni hoi anghmong hanah, sui, rong kamiing, rong kamling hup hoi rong kathim puu ngan hoiah sahsak ah.
\v 9 Onyx thlung hnetto lah ah loe, to thlung pongah Israel caanawk ih ahmin to tarik ah;
\v 10 angmacae tapenhaih baktih toengah, thlung maeto pongah kami tarukto ih ahmin to tarik ah loe, kalah thlung maeto pongah kami tarukto ih ahmin to tarik ah.
\v 11 Thlung thuk kakop kaminawk mah, bantuek nuiah ca tarik o ih baktih toengah, Israel caanawk ih ahmin to thlung hnetto pongah tarik ah; to pacoengah to ih thlung to sui tui palong ih tabu thungah suem ah.
\v 12 Israel caanawk mah panoek poehaih thlung ah suek o hanah, palaeng ah avak ih kahni nuiah hui caeng ah; Israel caanawk mah panoek o poe hanah, Aaron mah Angraeng hmaa ah nihcae ih ahminnawk to palaeng ah avak tih.
\v 13 Thlung loe sui hoi sak ih tabu thungah suem ah;
\v 14 boenghaih aqai ah suek ih qui to kaciim sui hoiah pakhui ah loe, thlung suekhaih tabu hoi nawnto pathlet ah.
\s1 Saoek padaphaih
\p 
\v 15 Kahni to rong kamiing, rong kamling hup, rong kathim puu ngan hoi sak ih baktih toengah, saoek padaphaih doeh kahoih ah sah ah.
\v 16 To saoek padaphaih hmuen loe hnetto ah pakhraep ah, kasawk karto, kalen karto omsak ah; taki palito kangvan ah sah ah.
\v 17 To saoek padaphaih nuiah ahmuen palito kangphaeng ah thlung to pahungh ah; ahmuen maeto pongah, sardiz thlung, topaz thlung hoi beryl thlung to pahung ah loe,
\v 18 ahmuen hnetto haih pongah, emerald thlung, sarfai thlung hoi diamond thlung to pahung ah.
\v 19 Ahmuen thumto haih pongah, Jacinth thlung, agate thlung hoi amethi thlungnawk to pahung ah loe,
\v 20 ahmuen palito haih pongah loe, krisolin thlung, onyx thlung hoi jasper thlungnawk to pahung ah; to thlungnawk loe sui hoi sak ih thingkhong thungah suem ah.
\v 21 Israel acaeng hathlai hnetto oh moe, bantuek nuiah tarik ih ca baktih toengah, to thlung pongah, Israel acaeng hathlai hnetto ahmin to tarik ah; thlung maeto pongah Israel acaeng ahmin maeto tarik ah.
\v 22 Saoek padaphaih ranuih aqai ih takii hnetto pongah, kaciim sui hoi pakhui ih qui hnetto suem ah.
\v 23 Saoek padaphaih nuiah sui hoiah kangbuet luet akhaw hnetto sah ah loe, padaphaih aqai ah pathlet hmaek ah.
\v 24 Saoek padaphaih aqai hnetto pongah kaom sui hoi sak ih kangbuet luet akhaw hnetto thungah, sui hoi sak ih qui hnetto pathlet hmaek ah.
\v 25 Sui hoi sak ih qui hnetto loe thlung pahunghaih tabu hnetto pongah pathlet ah loe, palaeng ah avak ih kahni hmaa ah suem ah.
\v 26 Sui hoiah kangbuet luet akhaw hnetto sah ah loe, kahni thungah kaom saoek padaphaih tlim ih, aqai hnetto nuiah suem ah.
\v 27 Sui hoiah kalah kangbuet luet akhaw hnetto sah let ah loe, kahni hmaa bang ih atlim, kahoih ah sak ih kahni zaenghaih kazii ranuih, kahni aqai banqoi bangtang bangah suem hmaek ah.
\v 28 Saoek padaphaih nui ih sui hoi sak ih kangbuet luet akhaw hnetto loe, kahni nui ih sui hoi sak ih kangbuet luet akhaw hnetto hoi nawnto pathlet ah loe, saoek padaphaih to kahni hoi amhoe han ai ah, kahoih ah sak ih kahni zaenghaih kazii ranui ah, rong kamiing qui hoiah kom ah.
\v 29 Aaron hmuenciim thung akun kruek, Angraeng hmaa ah panoek poe hanah, lokcaekhaih saoek padaphaih kahni nuiah kaom, Israel caanawk ih ahmin to, angmah ih saoek nuiah avak poe tih.
\v 30 \x - \xo 28:30 \xt NAM 27.21; Deu 33.8; Ezr 2.63; Neh 7.65.\x*Urim hoi Thummin doeh avak ih saoek padaphaih kahni thungah suem ah; Aaron mah Angraeng hmaa ah akun kruek, Urim hoi Thummin to Aaron ih palung thuem ah oh poe han oh; Aaron mah Israel kaminawk nuiah sak ih lok takroekhaih to angmah ih palung thuem ah Angraeng hmaa ah avak poe tih.
\s1 Qaima ih kahni
\p 
\v 31 Palaeng ah avak ih kahni to rong kamiing tlangqui hoiah sah ah.
\v 32 A um ah lu suekhaih akhaw to suem ah; a um ah suek ih akhaw to angsih han ai ah, a taeng boih ban hoiah sak ih kahni hoiah abu ah.
\v 33 Kahni tlim ih atom ah tlangqui kamiing, tlangqui kamling hup, tlangqui kathim hoiah pomegranat thingthai krang to soi ah loe, salakah sui hoi sak ih dar krang to soi ah.
\v 34 Sui hoi sak ih dar maeto pacoengah, pomegranate thingthai krang maeto, kahni atom ranuih, a taeng boih ah soi ah.
\v 35 Aaron mah toksak hanah, Angraeng hmaa ah, hmuenciim thungah akun naah, dueh ai ah, tacawt hanah, to kahni to angkhuk moe, anih ih lok to thaih han angaih.
\p 
\v 36 Kaciim sui sabae maeto sah ah loe, bantuek nuiah tarik ih baktih toengah, to sabae nuiah, \bd ANGRAENG HAN CIIMCAIHAIH,\bd* tiah tarik ah.
\v 37 Lumuek hmaa ah kamiing tlangqui hoiah kom ah.
\v 38 To hmuen loe Aaron ih lupataeh ah om ueloe, Israelnawk mah paek ih kaciim tangqumnawk, kaciim hmuennawk nuiah kaom, zaehaih to anih mah phaw tih; Angraeng mah to hmuennawk talawk thai hanah, to hmuen to Aaron ih lupataeh ah oh poe han angaih.
\p 
\v 39 Laihaw loe puu ngan hoiah sah ah loe, lumuek doeh puu ngan hoiah sah paeh; kaeng ah angzaeng ih kazii loe kaengkaeh sah kop kami khaeah sahsak ah.
\p 
\v 40 Aaron capanawk lensawkhaih amtueng thai hanah, laihaw, lumuek hoi kaeng zaenghaih kazii to sah paeh.
\v 41 To tiah nam ya Aaron hoi a caanawk to khukbuen angkhuksak moe, ka tok a sak o thai hanah, situi hoiah bawh ah, nihcae to caksak ah loe, ciimcaisak ah.
\v 42 Nihcae ih takpum to khuk hanah, kaeng hoi phaih khoek to kapha, puu ngan kahni to sah pae ah.
\v 43 Aaron hoi a caanawk mah amkhuenghaih kahni im, to tih ai boeh loe hmuenciim ah toksak o hanah hmaicam taengah a caeh o naah, zaehaih mah phak thuih moe, a duek o han ai ah, to khukbuennawk to angkhuk o han angaih; hae loe Aaron hoi a caanawk hanah dungzan ah paek ih daan ah om tih.
\c 29
\s1 Qaimanawk ciimsakhaih
\p 
\v 1 Qaima baktiah nihcae mah kai ih tok to sak o hanah, nihcae to hae tiah ciimcaisak ah; coek koi kaom ai saning kanawk maitaw caa maeto hoi tuu tae hnetto la ah;
\v 2 situi hoi atok ih taeh thuh ai ih takaw dip, taeh thuh ai ih situi hoi atok ih takaw kae, taeh thuh ai ih situi hoi atok ih takaw kae kangphaek daek, taeh thuh ai ih situi hoi atok ih takaw karoem to la ah.
\v 3 To takawnawk to benthang maeto pongah suem ah loe, maitaw tae maeto, tuu tae hnetto hoi nawnto sin ah.
\v 4 To pacoengah Aaron hoi a caanawk to kaminawk amkhuenghaih kahni im akunhaih thok taengah hoi ah, nihcae to tui amhluhsak ah.
\v 5 Khukbuennawk to la ah loe, laihaw, kahni, palaeng ah avak ih kahni hoi saoek padaphaih hmuen to Aaron han angkhuksak pacoengah, kazii sah kami mah sak ih kaeng zaenghaih kazii hoiah palaeng ah avak ih kahni to zaeng paeh.
\v 6 A lu ah lumuek to hui pae ah loe, lumuek nuiah kaciim tacik to bet paeh.
\v 7 Bawhhaih situi to la ah loe, a lu ah bawh paeh.
\v 8 A capanawk to caeh haih ah loe, laihaw to angkhuksak ah.
\v 9 Aaron hoi a caanawk to lumuek angmueksak ah loe, kaeng ah kazii angzaengsak ah; dungzan ah paek ih daan baktih toengah, nihcae mah qaima ih tok to sah o poe tih; Aaron hoi a capanawk to kacak ah tok to paek ah.
\p 
\v 10 Kahni im akunhaih thok taengah maitaw tae to hoi ah, Aaron hoi a caanawk mah maitaw lu nuiah ban koeng han angaih.
\v 11 Kaminawk amkhuenghaih kahni im akunhaih thok taengah, Angraeng hmaa ah maitaw tae to bop oh.
\v 12 Maitaw tae ih athii to la ah loe, hmaicam nui ih takiinawk thungah na banpazung tadong hoiah thaeng ah; to pacoengah kamtlai athii to hmaicam kung ah krai ah.
\v 13 Zok thung ih athawknawk, pathin taeng ih athawknawk, pakae hnetto taeng ih athawk, a nuiah kaom athawknawk to la boih ah loe, hmaicam nuiah hmai pakhaem ah.
\v 14 Toe maitaw tae ih moi, ahin hoi a aek loe, kahni im tasa bangah hmai hoiah thlaek ah; to loe zae angbawnhaih ah oh.
\p 
\v 15 Tuu tae maeto la ah loe, Aaron hoi a capanawk to lu nuiah ban koengsak ah.
\v 16 Tuu tae to bop ah loe, athii lak pacoengah, hmaicam nuiih a taeng boih ah haeh ah.
\v 17 Tuu tae ih angan to takroek pueng ah loe, takoh moi hoi a khoknawk pasaeh pacoengah, a lu hoi kalah moinawk to nawnto suem ah.
\v 18 \x - \xo 29:18 \xt Efi 5.2; Flp 4.18.\x*Tuu loe hmaicam nuiah hmai hoi pakhaem ah; to loe Angraeng khaeah sak ih hmai angbawnhaih ah oh moe, Angraeng khaeah sak ih hmai angbawnhaih, hmuihoih hmuen ah oh.
\p 
\v 19 Kalah tuu tae maeto la ah loe, Aaron hoi a capanawk to lu nuiah ban koengsak ah.
\v 20 Tuu tae to bop ah loe, athii lak pacoengah, Aaron hoi a capanawk ih bantang naa ranuih, bantang banpui nui hoi bantang khokpui nuiah nok paeh; to pacoengah athii to hmaicam nui hoi a taeng boih ah haeh ah.
\v 21 Hmaicam nui ih athii hoi bawhhaih situi to la ah loe, Aaron hoi a capanawk ih khukbuennawk nuiah bawh paeh; to tiah nahaeloe angmah hoi a capanawk ih khukbuen to ciim tih.
\p 
\v 22 Tuu tae ih athawk, tamai thawk, takoh thung ih athawknawk boih, pathin kakhuk athawk, pakae hnetto nuiah kaom athawk hoi bantang palaeng to la ah; to loe caksakhaih tuu tae ah oh.
\v 23 Angraeng hmaa ah kaom, benthang thung ih taeh thuh ai ih takaw maeto, situi hoi haek ih takaw kae maeto hoi takaw karoem maeto la ah;
\v 24 to hmuennawk loe Aaron hoi a capanawk ih ban ah suem boih ah loe, Angraeng hmaa ah ahaek moe, paek ih hmuen baktiah paek ah.
\v 25 To hmuennawk to nihcae ban hoi la let ah loe, Angraeng hmaa ah hmuihoih to paek hanah, hmaicam nuiah hmai angbawnhaih to sah ah.
\p 
\v 26 Aaron to caksak hanah tuu tae ih saoek to la ah loe, Angraeng hmaa ah ahaek moe, paek ih hmuen ah paek ah; tuu ih saoek loe nang taham ah om tih.
\v 27 Aaron hoi a capanawk caksakhaih tuu thung hoiah ahaek moe, paek ih moi hoi ahaek ih saoek, paloep tahang moe, paek ih moi hoi paloep tahang ih palaeng to ciimcaisak ah.
\v 28 To saoek hoi palaeng loe dungzan ah paek ih lok baktih toengah, Israel kaminawk mah paek ih Aaron hoi a capanawk ih taham ah om tih; to moi loe Israel kaminawk mah angmacae angdaeh angbawnhaih paek ih hmuen thung hoiah Angraeng hmaa ah ahaek moe, ahaek ah paek ih hmuen ah oh.
\p 
\v 29 Situi hoi bawh moe, qaima toksakhaih to caksak hanah, Aaron ih kaciim khukbuennawk loe a caanawk mah toep o poe tih.
\v 30 Hmuenciim ah toksak hanah, angmah zuengah qaima ah kaom a capa mah amkhuenghaih kahni imthung ah caeh naah, to kahni to ni sarihto thung angkhuk tih.
\p 
\v 31 Caksak han boh ih tuu moi to la ah loe, hmuenciim ah moi to thong ah.
\v 32 Aaron hoi a caanawk loe tuu moi, benthang thung ih takaw, kaminawk amkhuenghaih kahni im thok taengah caa o tih.
\v 33 Nihcae to ciimcaisak moe, caksak hanah, zae tahmenhaih sak han paek o ih hmuen to nihcae mah caa o tih; toe to hmuen loe ciimcai pongah, minawk kalah mah caa thai mak ai.
\v 34 Caksakhaih tuu moi hoi takaw to khawnbang khoek to amtlai nahaeloe, hmai thungah va ah; to loe ciimcai hmuen ah oh pongah, mi mah doeh caa thai mak ai.
\p 
\v 35 Kang paek ih lok baktih toengah, Aaron hoi a capanawk hanah hmuen to sah pae boih ah; nihcae tok caksakhaih to ni sarihto thung sah ah.
\v 36 Zae loih hanah ni thokkruek maitaw tae maeto hoi zae angbawnhaih to sah ah; zae loihaih na sak naah hmaicam to ciimsak ah; ciimcaisak hanah situi hoiah bawh ah.
\v 37 Ni sarihto thung hmaicam han zae loihaih to sah ah loe, ciimcaisak ah; to pacoengah loe kaciim koek hmaicam ah om ueloe, hmaicam kasui hmuen boih doeh ciimcai tih.
\p 
\v 38 Apet ai ah ni thokkruek hmaicam nuiah paek koi hmuen loe, saning to kaom tuucaa hnetto la ah,
\v 39 akhawnbang ah maeto paek ah loe duembang khoving tom ah maeto paek ah.
\v 40 Tuucaa maeto na paek naah, takaw dip ephah hato thungah maeto, olive situi hint palito thungah maeto hoi abaeh pacoengah, naek koi hmuen ah misurtui hint palito thungah maeto hoi nawnto paek ah.
\v 41 Duembang khoving tom ah tuucaa maeto paek ah loe, na paek naah akhawnbang ah na paek ih baktih toengah, situi hoi atok ih takaw, naek koi hmuen ah misurtui to paek ah; to loe Angraeng hmaa ah hmuihoih ah paek ih hmai angbawnhaih ah om tih.
\v 42 Angzo han koi na caanawk boih mah, nang hoi kai anghnuk moe, lokpaehhaih ahmuen, Angraeng hmaa ah, kaminawk amkhuenghaih kahni im hmaa ah, boeng ai ah hmai angbawnhaih to sah ah.
\v 43 To ahmuen ah Israel kaminawk hoi angqum moe, ka lensawkhaih hoiah nihcae to ka ciimsak han.
\v 44 Amkhuenghaih kahni im hoi hmaicam to ka ciimsak moe, ka qaima tok a sak o thai hanah, Aaron hoi a capanawk to ka ciimsak han.
\v 45 Israel kaminawk salakah ka oh moe, nihcae ih Sithaw ah ka oh han.
\v 46 Nihcae salakah ka oh hanah, Kai loe Izip prae thung hoiah nihcae zaehoikung, nihcae ih Angraeng Sithaw ah ka oh, Kai loe nihcae ih Angraeng Sithaw ah ka oh, tito nihcae mah panoek o tih.
\c 30
\s1 Hmuihoih hmai thlaekhaih hmaicam
\p 
\v 1 Hmuihoih to thlaek hanah, shittim thing hoiah hmaicam maeto sah ah.
\v 2 To hmaicam loe takii palito om tih; dong maeto sawk ueloe, dong maeto kawk pacoengah, dong hnetto sang tih; takiinawk doeh anghmong boih tih.
\v 3 Hmaicam ranuih koek, ataeng hoi takiinawk to sui tui pazut ah loe, sui hoiah aqai taeng boih to sah ah.
\v 4 Sui hoi sak ih aqai tlim hae bang hoi ho bangah kangbuet luet akhaw hnetto sui hoiah sah ah; to kangbuet luet akhaw loe hmaicam aput naah thing hawthaih akhaw ah om tih.
\v 5 Aputhaih thing loe shittim thing hoiah sah ah loe, sui tui pazut ah.
\v 6 Kai mah nang kang tonghhaih ahmuen, hnukung nuiah kaom palungnathaih tangkhang, hnukung thingkhong pakaahaih kahni hmaa ah, to hmaicam to suem ah.
\v 7 Aaron mah akhawnbang kruek, hmaiim paang han sak naah, to hmaicam nuiah hmuihoih to thlaek tih.
\v 8 Duembang hmai paang naah doeh, to hmaicam nuiah hmuihoih to thlaek tih; angzo han koi a caanawk dung khoek to Angraeng hmaa ah thlaek koi hmuihoih ah om tih.
\v 9 To hmaicam nuiah kalah hmuihoih, hmai angbawnhaih, to tih ai boeh loe cang angbawnhaih to sah hmah, naek koi hmuen doeh krai hmah.
\v 10 Aaron mah saningto naah vaito zae loihaih moi thii to sin ueloe, to hmaicam ih takiinawk nuiah zae loih hanah angbawnhaih to sah tih; na caanawk dung khoek to zae loih hanah saning kruek sah ah; hae loe Angraeng hmaa ah ciimcai koek hmaicam ah oh, tiah a naa.
\s1 Zae loihaih phoisa
\p 
\v 11 To pacoengah Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah,
\v 12 Israel kaminawk pakoep hanah ahmin na lak naah, kami boih hinghaih to akrang hanah Angraeng khaeah phoisa to paek oh; to tiah na sak nahaeloe nihcae na kroek naah, nihcae salakah nathaih to om mak ai.
\v 13 \x - \xo 30:13 \xt EXO 38.25,26; Mathai 17.24.\x*Kroek tangcae ah kaom kaminawk boih loe, hmuenciim ih shekel ahap, (shekel maeto naah, gerah pumphaeto oh) paek tih; shekel ahap loe Angraeng han paek ih hmuen ah om tih.
\v 14 Kami kroek naah, saning pumphaeto pacoeng, ranui bang boih Angraeng khae hmuen paekhaih to sak han oh.
\v 15 Na hinghaih to akrang hanah, Angraeng khaeah angbawnhaih na sak naah, angraeng kaminawk mah kapop ah paek o mak ai ueloe, kamtang kaminawk mah doeh tamsi ah paek o mak ai; kami boih mah shekel ahap paek o han oh.
\v 16 Israel kaminawk khae hoi zae loih hanah akranghaih phoisa to la ah loe, amkhuenghaih kahni im toksak hanah patoh ah; hae loe Israel kaminawk mah Angraeng hmaa ah panoek poe hanah, na hinghaih loih thai hanah sak ih akranghaih ah om tih, tiah a naa.
\s1 Amsaehhaih sabae kathuk
\p 
\v 17 To pacoengah angraeng mah Mosi khaeah,
\v 18 \x - \xo 30:18 \xt EXO 38.8.\x*amsaehhaih kathuk sabae maeto sum kamling hoiah sah ah loe, pahnuthaih a khok doeh sum kamling hoiah sah ah; to ih sabae kathuk to amkhuenghaih kahni im hoi hmaicam salakah suem ah loe, tui to lawn ah.
\v 19 Aaron hoi a caanawk loe to ih tui hoiah ban amsae o tih.
\v 20 Amkhuenghaih kahni imthung ah a caeh o kruek, a duek o han ai ah, to ih tui hoiah amsae o tih; to tih ai boeh loe Angraeng khaeah hmai angbawnhaih sak hanah hmaicam hmaa ah caeh o naah,
\v 21 a duek o han ai ah, nihcae mah khok hoi ban to amsae o tih; hae loe Aaron hoi angzo han koi a caanawk mah sak o poe han ih atawk ah oh.
\s1 Angnok ih situi
\p 
\v 22 \x - \xo 30:22 \xt EXO 37.29.\x*To pacoengah Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah,
\v 23 kahoih koek hmuihoih to la ah, kaciim myrrh hmuihoih shekel cumvai pangato, cinnamon hmuihoih ahap shekel cumvai hnet, qui pangato,
\v 24 hmuenciim ih shekel baktih toengah, kasia shekel cumvai pangato, olive situi hint maeto sin ah;
\v 25 hmuihoih sah kop kami mah sak ih hmuihoih to kaciim angnok ih kaciim situi ah sah ah, to situi loe angnok ih kaciim situi ah om tih.
\v 26 To situi hoiah amkhuenghaih kahni im hoi hnukung thingkhong,
\v 27 caboi hoi laom sabaenawk boih, hmaithawk hoi hmaithawk paanghaih tungnawk, hmuihoih thlaekhaih hmaicam,
\v 28 hmai angbawnhaih hmaicam hoi laom sabaenawk boih, sabae kathuk hoi pahnuthaih a khoknawk to nok boih ah.
\v 29 To hmuennawk kaciim koek ah oh hanah, to tiah ciimsak ah; to hmuen kasui hmuen boih loe ciimcai tih.
\v 30 Aaron hoi a capanawk to bawh ah loe, kai ih qaima tok a sak o thai hanah, nihcae to pahoe ah.
\v 31 Israel kaminawk khaeah, Hae loe angzo han koi na caanawk dung khoek to angnok ih kaciim situi ah om tih.
\v 32 To situi hoiah takpum to bawh hmah loe, to situi hoi kanghmong kalah situi to sah hmah; to situi loe ciimcai pongah, nang hanah kaciim situi ah om tih.
\v 33 To situi hoi kanghmong kalah situi sah kami, asaenghaih om ai ah to situi hoi minawk kalah nok kami loe, acaeng thung hoi pahnawt ah, tiah a thuih, tiah thui paeh, tiah a naa.
\s1 Hmuihoih
\p 
\v 34 To pacoengah Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah, Hmuihoih, thing tangpri, hmuihoih onika, hmuihoih kalbanumnawk to la ah loe, to hmuihoih hoi kaciim hmuihoihnawk to kangvan ah noek ah;
\v 35 to hmuihoih hmuennawk hoiah hmai thlaek koi hmuihoih loe hmuihoih sah kop kami khaeah sahsak ah; paloi thuh ah, to pacoengah loe kathoeng hoi ciimcai hmuihoih ah om tih.
\v 36 Thoemtonawk to kadip puengah naep ah loe, nang kang hnukhaih, amkhuenghaih kahni im ih hnukung hmaa ah suem ah; hae loe nang hanah ciimcai koek ah om tih.
\v 37 To tiah sak ih hmuihoih hoi kanghmong ah, nangmah han kalah hmuihoih to sah hmah; to loe Angraeng hanah nangcae khaeah ciimcai hmuen ah oh han oh.
\v 38 Mi kawbaktih doeh hae baktih hmai thlaek koi hmuihoih to angmah hanah sah moe, patoh kami loe, acaeng thung hoiah pahnawt ah, tiah a naa.
\c 31
\s1 Bezalel hoi Oholiah
\p 
\v 1 To pacoengah Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah,
\v 2 khenah, Judah acaeng, Uri capa, Bazalel to ahmin hoiah ka kawk boeh;
\v 3 anih loe Sithaw ih Muithla, palunghahaih, kophaih, panoek thaihaih hoi congca bantok sak thaihaih hoiah ka koisak boeh.
\v 4 Anih khaeah sui, sum kanglung hoi sum kamling sak thaihaih tok,
\v 5 thlung aah kophaih hoi thing aah kophaih tok, tok congca sak thaihaih to ka paek boeh.
\v 6 Khenah, anih to abomh hanah Dan acaeng, Ahisamak capa Aholiah to ka paek boeh; palungha kaminawk mah kang thuih ih loknawk to sak o boih hanah, nihcae palung thungah palunghahaih to ka paek boeh;
\v 7 kaminawk amkhuenghaih kahni im, hnukung ah kaom thingkhong, to thingkhong nuiah kaom palungnathaih tangkhang hoi kahni im ih hmuennawk boih,
\v 8 caboi hoi hmuennawk, kaciim hmaithawk hoi paanghaih tungnawk boih, hmuihoih thlaekhaih hmaicam,
\v 9 hmai angbawnhaih hmaicam hoi hmuennawk boih, amsaehhaih sabae kathuk hoi pahnuthaih a khoknawk,
\v 10 toksakhaih khukbuennawk, qaima toksak naah, Aaron hoi a capanawk mah angkhuk han ih kaciim kahninawk,
\v 11 bawh ih situi hoi hmuenciim ah thlaek ih hmuihoih to sak hanah, nang khaeah kang thuih ih lok baktih toengah, nihnik mah sah hoi tih, tiah a naa.
\s1 Sabbath ni
\p 
\v 12 To pacoengah Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah,
\v 13 kai loe nangcae ciimsakkung, Angraeng ah ka oh, tiah na panoek o moe, angzo han koi na caanawk dung khoek to, nangcae hoi kai salakah angmathaih ah oh hanah, Kai ih Sabbath to zaa oh, tiah Israel kaminawk khaeah thui paeh.
\v 14 Sabbath ni loe nangcae han ciimcai pongah, zaa oh; Sabbath ni amhnongsak kami loe, paduek han oh; Sabbath niah toksah kami loe, acaeng thung hoiah pahnawt oh.
\v 15 \x - \xo 31:15 \xt EXO 20.8-11; 23.12; 34.21; 35.2; LEV 23.3; Deu 5.12-14.\x*Ni tarukto thung toksah oh, toe ni sarihto haih loe anghakhaih Sabbath niah oh moe, kaciim Angraeng ih niah oh; Sabbath niah toksah kami loe, paduek han oh.
\v 16 To pongah Israel kaminawk loe, angzo han koi a caanawk dung khoek to, dungzan lokkamhaih ah patoh hanah, Sabbath ni to zaa oh.
\v 17 \x - \xo 31:17 \xt EXO 20.11.\x*Hae loe Israel kaminawk hoi kai salakah dungzan angmathaih ah om tih; Angraeng mah ni tarukto thung van hoi long to sak moe, ni sarihto naah loe, toksah ai ah anghak pongah, tha oh let, tiah thui paeh, tiah a naa.
\p 
\v 18 Sinai mae ah Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah lokthuih pacoengah, Sithaw ih banpazung hoi tarik ih, hnukung ah kaom, thlung kangphaek hnetto, Mosi hanah a paek.
\c 32
\s1 Sui hoi sak ih maitaw caa
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 32:1 \xt Tsk 7.40.\x*Mae hoiah Mosi angzo tathuk ai boeh, tito kaminawk mah panoek o naah, kaminawk loe Aaron khaeah amkhueng o moe, anih khaeah, Angthawk ah; kaicae hmaa ah caeh hanah sithawnawk to na sah pae ah; Izip prae thung hoi kaicae zaehoikung Mosi loe, kawbang maw oh ving boeh, tito a panoek o ai boeh, tiah a naa o.
\v 2 Aaron mah nihcae khaeah, Na zunawk, na capanawk hoi na canunawk ih sui naa tangkraengnawk to angkhring oh loe, kai khaeah na sin oh, tiah a naa.
\v 3 To pongah kaminawk boih mah angmacae ih sui naa tangkraeng to angkring o moe, Aaron khaeah sin pae o.
\v 4 \x - \xo 32:4 \xt 1 Siang 12.28; Tsk 7.41.\x*Nihcae mah paek o ih hmuennawk to anih mah talawk boih moe, a sak pae pacoengah maitaw caa ih krang to a soi pae; Aw Israel, hae sithaw loe Izip prae thung hoiah nangcae zaehoikung sithawnawk boeh ni, tiah a naa.
\v 5 Aaron mah to hmuen to hnuk naah, maitaw caa hmaa ah hmaicam maeto sak moe, Khawnbang loe Angraeng hanah poih sakhaih niah om tih, tiah kaminawk khaeah taphongsak.
\v 6 \x - \xo 32:6 \xt 1 Korin 10.7.\x*To pongah kaminawk loe khawnbang khawnthaw ah angthawk o moe, hmai angbawnhaih hoi angdaeh angbawnhaih to sak o; caak naek hanah anghnut o moe, hnawh hanah angthawk o.
\p 
\v 7 To naah Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah, Caeh tathuk ah, Izip prae thung hoiah na hoih ih kaminawk loe, amro o boih boeh;
\v 8 nihcae han ka thuih pae ih loklam to karangah angqoi o taak moe, angmacae han maitaw caa krang to a sak o boeh; to krang to bok o moe, angbawnhaih to a sak o pacoengah, Aw Israel kaminawk, hae sithaw loe Izip prae thung hoi nangcae zaehoikung sithaw ah ni oh o boeh, tiah a thuih o, tiah a naa.
\v 9 Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah, Hae kaminawk hae ka hnuk boeh; nihcae loe palungthah kami ah oh o;
\v 10 to pongah kaimah bueng na caehtaak ah; hmai baktih kamngaeh palungphuihaih hoiah nihcae to ka kanghsak moe, kam rosak boih han; to pacoengah nang hae kalen parai acaeng ah kang sak han, tiah a naa.
\p 
\v 11 \x - \xo 32:11 \xt NAM 14.13-19.\x*Toe Mosi mah angmah ih Angraeng Sithaw khaeah, Angraeng, tipongah na sak thaihaih, na ban thacakhaih hoiah Izip prae thung hoi na zaehhoih ih nangmah ih kaminawk to palungphuihaih hoiah nam rosak boih han loe?
\v 12 Tipongah Izip kaminawk mah, Sithaw loe kasae poekhaih tawnh, to pongah ni nihcae to mae nuiah hum moe, long pum hoiah tamit boih hanah, a caeh haih, tiah thuih han koi ah oh ving loe? Hmai baktih kamngaeh palungphuihaih to dipsak ah loe, nangmah ih kaminawk nuiah sak han ih kasae poekhaih to dawnpakhuem raeh.
\v 13 \x - \xo 32:13 \xt Genesis 22.16,17; 17.8.\x*Na tamna Abraham, Issak hoi Israel khaeah, Na caanawk loe van ih cakaeh zetto kang pungsak moe, dungzan ah qawk na toep o thai hanah, long nuiah kaom hmuennawk boih kang paek han, tiah na thuih ih lok to pahnet hmah raeh, tiah a naa.
\v 14 To naah Angraeng mah angmah ih kaminawk nuiah kasae sak han poekhaih to dawnpakhuem let.
\p 
\v 15 Mosi loe a ban ah hnukung thlung kangphaek hnetto sin moe, mae nui hoiah anghum tathuk; thlung kangphaek hnetto pongah, ahnuk ahmaa ca to tarik.
\v 16 To thlung kangphaek hnetto loe, Sithaw mah sak ih thlung kangphaek ah oh moe, Sithaw mah ni ca doeh tarik.
\v 17 Kaminawk hanghaih lok to Joshua mah thaih naah, Mosi khaeah, ataihaih ahmuen ah misatukhaih lok to ka thaih, tiah a naa.
\v 18 Mosi mah, To hanghaih lok loe misa pazawhaih lok na ai ni, misa sunghaih lok doeh na ai ah, laasakhaih lok ni ka thaih, tiah a naa.
\v 19 Ataihaih ahmuen taengah phak naah, Mosi mah maitaw caa hoi nawnto hnawh kaminawk to hnuk; hmai kamngaeh baktiah palung to phui pongah, a ban ih thlung kangphaek to a vah; mae tlim ah a vah phaeng.
\v 20 Nihcae mah sak o ih maitaw caa to a lak moe, hmai thungah a vah pae; kadip puengah naep pae pacoengah, tui pongah phuih moe, Israel kaminawk to a naeksak.
\p 
\v 21 Aaron khaeah, Hae tiah kalen zaehaih to sak hanah, nihcae mah na nuiah tih hmuen maw a sak o? tiah a naa.
\v 22 Aaron mah, Ka angraeng, palungphuisak hmah; hae kaminawk loe kasae poekhaih a tawnh o, tito na panoek, tiah a naa.
\v 23 Kai khaeah, Kaicae hmabang ah ka caeh o thai hanah, sithawnawk to na sah paeh, Izip prae thung hoi kaicae zaehoikung Mosi loe, kawbang maw oh boeh, tito a panoek o ai boeh, tiah a thuih o.
\v 24 To pongah kai mah nihcae khaeah, Sui tawn kaminawk boih sui to angkhring oh loe, kai khaeah na paek oh, tiah ka naa. To naah nihcae mah sui to angkhring o moe, ang paek o; kai mah hmai thungah ka vah naah, maitaw caa ah angcoeng, tiah a naa.
\p 
\v 25 (Aaron mah kaminawk to khen laek ai boeh pongah, a misanawk hmaa ah bangkrai ah ohsak), tito Mosi mah hnuk naah,
\v 26 to pongah Mosi loe ataihaih khongkha ah angdoet moe, Angraeng bangah angdoe kaminawk boih, kai khaeah angzo oh, tiah a naa. To naah Levi caanawk boih anih taengah amkhueng o.
\v 27 To pacoengah Mosi mah nihcae khaeah, Israel Angraeng Sithaw mah, Kami boih mah sumsen to avak nasoe; ataihaih ahmuen ih khongkha maeto hoi maeto boenghaih khoek to caeh nasoe loe, kami boih mah angmah ih nawkamya, angmah ih ampuinawk hoi angmah imtaeng kami to hum nasoe, tiah a thuih, tiah a naa.
\v 28 Mosi mah thuih ih lok baktih toengah, Levinawk mah sak o; to na niah kami sang thumto duek o.
\v 29 To pacoengah Mosi mah, Angraeng mah vai hniah tahamhoihaih paek hanah, kami boih angmah ih capa hoi angmah ih nawkamya humhaih rang hoiah, vaihniah nangmah hoi nangmah to Angraeng khaeah nang paek o boeh, tiah a naa.
\p 
\v 30 Khawnbang ah Mosi mah kaminawk khaeah, Kalen parai zaehaih to na sak o boeh; toe vaihi Angraeng khaeah ka caeh tahang moe, nangcae zae loihaih to ka sak thai thung ka sak han, tiah a naa.
\v 31 To pongah Mosi loe Angraeng khaeah caeh let, Aw, hae kaminawk loe kalen parai zaehaih to a sak o moeng boeh! Sui to angmacae hanah sithaw ah a sak o boeh.
\v 32 \x - \xo 32:32 \xt Saam 69.28; Lph 3.5.\x*Toe vaihiah nihcae zaehaih to tahmen raeh; a zae o haih na tahmen ai nahaeloe, na tarik ih cabu thung hoiah kai ih ahmin to phrae ving halat ah, tiah a naa.
\v 33 Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah, Ka hmaa ah zaehaih sah kami loe, anih ih ahmin to ka cabu thung hoiah ka phraek han.
\v 34 Vaihi caeh ah loe, kang thuih ih ahmuen ah kaminawk to caeh haih ah; khenah, kai ih van kami to na hmaa ah caeh tih; nihcae thuitaekhaih atue to phak naah, a zae o haih pongah nihcae to ka thuitaek han, tiah a naa.
\p 
\v 35 Aaron mah sak pae ih maitaw caa pongah, Angraeng mah kaminawk to nathaih hoiah thuitaek.
\c 33
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 33:1 \xt Genesis 12.7; \xt Genesis 26.3; \xt Genesis 28.13.\x*To pacoengah Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah, Hae ahmuen hae caehtaak ah loe, Abraham, Issak hoi Jakob khaeah, Na caanawk khaeah ka paek han, tiah lokkam ih, prae thungah Izip prae thung hoi na zaehhoih ih kaminawk hoi nawnto caeh oh;
\v 2 kai ih van kami to na hmaa ah ka patoeh han, anih mah Kannaan, Amor, Hit, Periz, Hiv hoi Jebus kaminawk to haek boih tih.
\v 3 Khoitui hoi tahnutui longhaih prae ah caeh oh; toe kai loe nangcae salakah ka caeh mak ai; palungthah kami ah na oh o pongah, loklam ah kam rosak boih moeng tih, tiah a naa.
\p 
\v 4 Kaminawk mah to baktih tamthang kasae to thaih o naah, palungset o moe, mi doeh amthoephaih khukbuen to angkhuk o ai.
\v 5 Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah, Israel kaminawk khaeah hae tiah thui paeh; nangcae loe palungthah kami ah na oh o; nangcae hae nawnetta thung kang caeh haih nahaeloe, kam rosak boih moeng tih; nangcae to kawbang maw kang sak han, tiah ka panoek hanah, nam thoep o haih hmuennawk to angkhring oh, tiah a thuih, tiah a naa.
\v 6 To pongah Israel kaminawk mah Horeb mae ah amthoephaih hmuennawk to angkhring o boih.
\s1 Amkhuenghaih kahni im
\p 
\v 7 Mosi mah ataihaih ahmuen tasa bang, kangthla kue ahmuen ah, kahni im to sak moe, kaminawk amkhuenghaih kahni im, tiah a kawk. Angraeng pakrong han koeh kami boih loe, ataihaih ahmuen tasa bangah sak ih kaminawk amkhuenghaih kahni im ah caeh o nasoe.
\v 8 Mosi kahni im ah caeh naah, kaminawk boih angthawk o moe, angmacae kahni im thok taengah angdoet o; Mosi kahni imthung ah akun ai karoek to a khet o.
\v 9 Mosi kahni imthung ah akun naah, tamai tung loe kahni im akunhaih thok taengah krak tathuk; to naah Mosi hoi Angraeng to lok apaeh hoi.
\v 10 Kaminawk boih mah, kahni imthung akunhaih thok taengah angdoe tamai tung to hnuk o naah, kaminawk boih angmacae ih kahni im thok taengah angdoet o moe, a bok o.
\v 11 Kami mah angmah ih ampui hoi lok apaeh baktih toengah, Angraeng hoi Mosi doeh mikhmai kangtong ah lok apaeh hoi; to pacoengah Mosi loe a ohhaih ahmuen ah amlaem let; toe anih bomkung, thendoeng, Nun capa Joshua loe kahni im to caehtaak ai.
\s1 Mosi hoi Angraeng lensawkhaih
\p 
\v 12 Mosi mah Angraeng khaeah, Khenah, Nang mah ih hae kaminawk to zaehhoih hanah nang thuih; toe kai abomh han kaminawk to nang panoeksak ai; na hmin to ka panoek moe, nang loe ka mikhnuk naakrak ah na oh, tiah nang naa.
\v 13 To pongah ka nuiah palung nang hoe nahaeloe, kai nang tahmen, tito ka panoek thai hanah, na loklam to na patuek ah; hae acaengnawk loe nang ih kami ni, tiah panoek poe ah, tiah a hnik.
\v 14 Angraeng mah kang caeh o haih poe moe, anghakhaih kang paek o han, tiah a naa.
\v 15 To naah Mosi mah anih khaeah, Kai nang caeh haih ai nahaeloe, kaicae hae ahmuen hoiah na patoeh hmah.
\v 16 Kai hoi nang ih kaminawk loe, na hmaa ah mikcuk naakrak ah ni kho a sak o, tito kawbang maw panoek thai tih? Kaicae hoi nawnto na caeh naah na ai maw amtueng tih? To tiah ni kai hoi nang ih kaminawk loe long nuiah kaom kaminawk boih thung hoiah kalah ta kami ah om o tih, tiah a naa.
\s1 Mosi mah Angraeng lensawkhaih hnuk
\p 
\v 17 To naah Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah, Na thuih ih lok baktih toengah ka sak han; nang loe ka mikcuk naakrak ah na oh; nang loe nangmah ih ahmin hoiah ni kang panoek boeh, tiah a naa.
\v 18 Mosi mah anih khaeah, Vaihi na lensawkhaih amtuengsak ah, tiah a naa.
\v 19 \x - \xo 33:19 \xt Rom 9.15.\x*Angraeng mah, Na hmaa ah Kaih ih hoihaihnawk boih to ka caehsak moe, Angraeng ih ahmin to na hmaa ah ka taphong han; tahmenhaih ka tawnh ih kaminawk nuiah tahmenhaih ka tawnh moe, tahmenhaih kam tuengsak ih kaminawk nuiah tahmenhaih to kam tuengsak han.
\v 20 Toe ka mikhmai loe na hnu mak ai; ka mikhmai hnu kami loe, hing mak ai, tiah a naa.
\v 21 To pacoengah Angraeng mah, Khenah, ka taengah ahmuen maeto oh; nang loe lungsong nuiah angdoe tih;
\v 22 ka lensawkhaih amtueng naah, nang loe kakoi lungsong thungah kang suek moe, Ka laem ai karoek to, ka ban hoiah kang tamuep han.
\v 23 Ka ban to ka zuh naah loe, ka hnukbang to na hnu tih; toe ka mikhmai loe na hnu mak ai, tiah a naa.
\c 34
\s1 Kangtha thlung kangphaek
\p 
\v 1 Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah, Na vah phaeng ih thlung kangphaek pongah tarik ih ca baktih toengah ka tarik let hanah, hmaloe ih baktih toengah thlung kangphaek hnetto sah ah.
\v 2 Khawnbang khawnthaw ah amsak coek ah loe, Sinai mae ah daw tahang ah; maesom nuiah nangmah hoi nangmah to kai khaeah ang paek ah.
\v 3 Mi doeh angzo haih hmah, mi doeh mae nuiah hnuk han om hmah nasoe; tuu hoi maitawnawk doeh mae hmaa ah toep o hmah nasoe.
\v 4 To pongah anih mah hmaloe ih baktih toengah, thlung kangphaek hnetto a sak; Angraeng mah thuih ih lok baktih toengah, Mosi loe khawnbang khawnthaw ah angthawk moe, a ban ah thlung kangphaek hnetto sin pacoengah, Sinai mae nuiah dawh tahang.
\v 5 To naah Angraeng loe tamai thung hoiah anghum tathuk, to ah anih hoi nawnto angdoet moe, Angraeng ih ahmin to taphong.
\v 6 \x - \xo 34:6 \xt EXO 20.5,6; NAM 14.18; Deu 5.9,10; 7.9,10.\x*Mosi hmaa ah Angraeng to caeh moe, Amlunghaih, palungnathaih hoi kakoi Angraeng, palungsawk, thui laek ai hoihhaih hoi loktang hoiah kakoi,
\v 7 athawng asang kaminawk tahmenkung, zaehaih, sakpazaehaih hoi kahoih ai hmuen sakhaih tahmenkung, toe zaehaih sah kaminawk loe khensut ai ah; ampanawk ih zaehaih pongah a caanawk adung thumto hoi palito karoek to thuitaekkung, Angraeng Sithaw, tiah taphong.
\v 8 Mosi loe karangah long ah akuep moe, a bok.
\v 9 Aw Angraeng, na mikcuk naakrak ah ka oh nahaeloe, Angraeng loe kaicae hoi nawnto caeh nasoe; hae kaminawk loe palungthah o, toe kaicae zaehaih hoi sakpazaehaihnawk to tahmen raeh ah loe, kaicae hae nangmah ih qawktoepkung ah na la ah, tiah a naa.
\v 10 To pacoengah anih mah, Khenah, nangcae hoi lokmaihaih ka sak han; long nuiah kaom kaminawk boih hmaa ah, sak vai ai ih dawnraihaih to nang ih kaminawk boih mikhnuk ah ka sak han; nangcae khaeah ka sak han ih dawnrai hmuen loe zit thoh pongah, nang hoi nawnto kaom kaminawk mah Angraeng mah sak ih hmuen to hnu o tih.
\v 11 Vai hniah kang thuih ih lok hae tahngai ah; khenah, Amor, Kannan, Hit, Periz, Hiv hoi Jebus kaminawk to nangcae hmaa ah ka haek han.
\v 12 Na caeh han ih prae kaminawk hoi lokmaihaih na sak han ai ah, acoe ah; na sak moeng nahaeloe nihcae loe nangcae han thaang ah om o tih.
\v 13 \x - \xo 34:13 \xt Deu 16.21.\x*Nihcae ih hmaicamnawk to phrae pae ah, krangnawk doeh paro pae ah loe, Asherah tungnawk doeh pakhruh pae ah.
\v 14 Kalah sithaw to bok hmah; anih ih ahmin loe, Ut panoek Angraeng; ut panoek Sithaw, tiah oh;
\v 15 to prae thungah kaom kaminawk hoi lokmaihaih na sak nahaeloe, nihcae loe angmacae ih sithawnawk khaeah a takpum to zaw o ueloe, angbawnhaih to sah o tih; nang doeh na kawk o ueloe, nihcae mah sak ih angbawnhaih moi to na caa moeng tih;
\v 16 Na capanawk hanah nihcae ih canunawk zu ah na lak pae nahaeloe, a canunawk loe angmacae ih sithawnawk khaeah takpum zaw o ueloe, na capanawk doeh nihcae ih sithawnawk hoi zaehaih to sah o moeng tih.
\v 17 \x - \xo 34:17 \xt EXO 20.4; LEV 19.4; Deu 5.8; 27.15.\x*Nangmah hanah krang to sah hmah.
\p 
\v 18 \x - \xo 34:18 \xt EXO 12.14-20; LEV 23.6-8; NAM 28.16-25.\x*Taeh thuh ai ih poih to sah ah. Kang paek ih lok baktih toengah, ni sarihto thung taeh thuh ai ih takaw to caa ah; Abib khrah phak naah sah ah; Abib khrah naah ni Izip prae thung hoiah na tacawt.
\v 19 \x - \xo 34:19 \xt EXO 13.2.\x*Zok thung hoi tapen tangsuek calu boih loe kai ih ni; tuu doeh, maitaw doeh, tapen tangsuek atae loe kai ih ni.
\v 20 \x - \xo 34:20 \xt EXO 13.13.\x*Tapen tangsuek laa hrang to tuucaa hoiah akrang ah; na krang ai nahaeloe, laa hrang ih tahnong to khaek paeh. Tapen tangsuek na capanawk to akrang boih ah. Mi kawbaktih doeh ka hmaa ah bangkrai ah angzo hmah nasoe.
\p 
\v 21 \x - \xo 34:21 \xt EXO 20.9,10; 23.12; 31.15; 35.2; LEV 23.3; Deu 5.13,14.\x*Ni tarukto thung toksah ah loe, ni sarihto naah loe anghak ah; laikok atokhaih atue hoi cang aahhaih atue ah doeh, ni sarihto naah loe anghak ah.
\v 22 \x - \xo 34:22 \xt LEV 23.15-21; NAM 28.26-31; \xt LEV 23.39-43.\x*Zarto boeng naah kathai tangsuek cang aahhaih poih to sah ah, cang pakhuenghaih poih doeh saning boeng naah sah ah.
\v 23 Na capa nongpanawk loe Angraeng Sithaw, Israel Sithaw hmaa ah, saningto naah vai thumto angphong o han angaih.
\v 24 Acaeng kaminawk to na hmaa ah ka haek moe, na prae to ka kawksak han; na Angraeng Sithaw hmaa ah angphong hanah, saningto naah vai thumto na caeh naah, mi mah doeh na prae to khit mak ai.
\p 
\v 25 \x - \xo 34:25 \xt EXO 12.10.\x*Moi thii hoi taeh thuh ih hmuen hoiah kai khaeah angbawnhaih to sah hmah; loihaih poih sak ih angbawnhaih moi to akhawnbang khoek to suem hmah.
\v 26 \x - \xo 34:26 \xt Deu 26.2; \xt Deu 14.21.\x*Na lawk thung ih athai tangsuek thingthai qumpo to na Angraeng Sithaw im ah sin ah; Maeh caa to amno ih tahnutui hoi nawnto thong hmah, tiah a naa.
\p 
\v 27 Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah, Hae loknawk hae tarik ah; hae loknawk baktih toengah, nang hoi Israel kaminawk salakah lokmaihaih to ka sak, tiah a naa.
\v 28 Mosi loe buhcaa ai, tui doeh nae ai ah, Angraeng hoi nawnto ni qui pali, qum qui palito thung oh; to naah anih mah kaalok hato, lokmaihaih loknawk to thlung kangphaek pongah tarik.
\s1 Mosi ih mikhmai ampha
\p 
\v 29 \x - \xo 34:29 \xt 2 Kor 3.7-16.\x*Mosi loe hnukung thlung kangphaek hnetto ban ah sin moe, mae nui hoiah anghum tathuk, Angraeng hoi nawnto lok apaeh hoi naah, angmah loe kampha angmah ih mikhmai to panoek ai.
\v 30 Aaron hoi Israel kaminawk boih mah Mosi to hnuk o naah, khenah, anih ih mikhmai loe ampha; to pongah anih khae anghnaih hanah a zit o.
\v 31 Toe nihcae to Mosi mah kawk; to pongah Aaron hoi Israel zaehoikungnawk boih, anih khaeah angzoh o let, to tiah Mosi hoi nihcae to lok aram o.
\v 32 To pacoengah Israel kaminawk boih anih taengah anghnaih o moe, Sinai mae ah Angraeng mah paek ih kaaloknawk to nihcae khaeah thuih pae boih.
\v 33 Mosi mah nihcae khaeah lokthuih pae boih pacoengah, a mikhmai to khuk.
\v 34 Toe Mosi loe Angraeng hoi lok apaeh hanah anih hmaa ah caeh kruek, tasa bang angzo let ai karoek to, a mikhmai khukhaih to takhoe ving; tasa bang angzoh pacoengah, anih khaeah thuih pae ih loknawk to Israel kaminawk khaeah a thuih pae patoeng.
\v 35 To naah kampha Mosi ih mikhmai to Israel kaminawk mah hnuk o; Mosi loe Angraeng hoi lok apaeh hanah caeh karoek to mikhmai to a khuk let.
\c 35
\s1 Sabbath ni zahhaih daan
\p 
\v 1 Mosi mah Israel kaminawk maeto ah pakhueng boih pacoengah, nihcae khaeah, Na sak o hanah, Angraeng mah hae tiah thuih ih lok to oh.
\v 2 \x - \xo 35:2 \xt EXO 20.8-11; 23.12; 31.15; 34.21; LEV 23.3; Deu 5.12-14.\x*Ni tarukto thung toksah oh, toe ni sarihto naah loe nangcae han ciimcai ni, Angraeng ih Sabbath niah oh; mi kawbaktih doeh to niah toksah kami loe paduek han oh.
\v 3 Mi kawbaktih doeh Sabbath niah na ohhaih ahmuen ah hmaitik o hmah, tiah a naa.
\s1 Kahni im ih hmuennawk
\p 
\v 4 Mosi mah amkhueng Israel kaminawk boih khaeah, Angraeng mah hae tiah thuih;
\v 5 na tawnh ih hmuen Angraeng khaeah sin oh; mi kawbaktih doeh palunghuemhaih hoiah paek koeh kami loe sui, sum kanglung hoi sum kamling to Angraeng khaeah sin oh.
\v 6 Rong kamiing, rong kamling hup, rong kathim, puu ngan hoi maeh muinawk,
\v 7 kathim tuu hinnawk, caham hinnawk, shittim thingnawk,
\v 8 hmai paaang hanah olive situi, tak bawhhaih situi hoi hmai thlaek koi hmuihoih,
\v 9 palaeng ah avak ih kahni hoi saoek padaphaih kahni nuiah bet koi thlung hoi onyx thlungnawk to sin oh.
\p 
\v 10 Nangcae thung ih palungha kaminawk to angzo o ueloe, Angraeng mah thuih ih lok baktih toengah hmuennawk,
\v 11 kahni im, buk, buk khukhaih, patomhhaih sumnawk, thingphaeknawk, takraenghaih thingnawk, tungnawk hoi a khok pahnuthaihnawk,
\v 12 lokkamhaih thingkhong, aputhaih thingnawk, palungnathaih tangkhang hoi khukhaih kahni,
\v 13 caboi hoi a khoknawk, a thungah kaom laom sabaenawk boih hoi hmaa bangah suek ih takaw,
\v 14 hmaithawk pa-aanghaih tungnawk, hmuennawk, hmaiimnawk hoi situinawk,
\v 15 hmaicam ah thlaek koi hmuihoih hoi tungnawk, tak bawhhaih situi hoi hmuihoih, kahni im akunhaih thok taengah payang ih kahni,
\v 16 angbawnhaih hmaicam hoi sum kamling vaizoek, a khoknawk hoi hmuennawk boih, tak amsaehhaih sabae kathuk hoi a khok,
\v 17 imthung longhma ah payang ih kahninawk, payanghaih tungnawk hoi a khok pahnuthaih tungnawk, longhma akunhaih ahmuen pakaahaih kahni,
\v 18 kahni im takhinghaih sumnawk, longhma takhinghaih sumnawk hoi quinawk,
\v 19 hmuenciim thungah toksak naah angkhuk ih kahni, qaima Aaron ih kaciim kahninawk hoi a capanawk ih kahninawk to sah pae tih, tiah a naa.
\s1 Kahni im han hmuen paekhaih
\p 
\v 20 To pacoengah amkhueng Israel kaminawk loe Mosi hmaa hoiah amlaem o boih let.
\v 21 Palung angthawk kaminawk, palunghuem kaminawk mah amkhuenghaih kahni im to sak o moe, toksakhaih hoi kaciim khukbuen to sak hanah, Angraeng han paek o ih hmuennawk to a sin o.
\v 22 Palunghuem kaminawk loe nongpa doeh, nongpata doeh angzoh o boih moe, ban lakok, naa tangkraeng, bantuek, bungmunawk, sui hoi sak ih hmuennawk to a sin o; kami boih mah Angraeng paek hanah sui to sin o.
\v 23 Rong kamiing, rong kamling hup, rong kathim, puu ngan, kathim tuu hinnawk, caham hinnawk doeh a sin o.
\v 24 Sum kanglung hoi sum kamling sin kaminawk doeh, Angraeng han paek o; angaihaih ahmuen ah patoh hanah, kami boih mah shittim thing to sin o.
\v 25 Lahat kaeh kop kaminawk mah, tlangqui kamiing, tlangqui kamling hup, tlangqui kathim hoi puu ngan to sin o.
\v 26 Palunghuem moe, sak han koeh nongpatanawk boih mah, maeh mui to kaeh o.
\v 27 Zaehoikungnawk mah atho kaom onyx thlungnawk, qaima ih palaeng ah avak ih kahni nuiah bet hanah kalah thlungnawk to sin o.
\v 28 Hmuihoih, hmai paaang koi situi, tak bawhhaih situi to a sin o.
\v 29 Palunghuemhaih katawn Israel kaminawk thung ih nongpa hoi nongpata boih, Angraeng mah Mosi patohhaih rang hoiah thuih ih tok congca hanah, Angraeng khaeah palunghuemhaih hoiah a paek o.
\s1 Bezalel hoi Aholiah
\r (Exodus 31:1-11)
\p 
\v 30 To pacoengah Mosi mah Israel kaminawk khaeah, Khen oh, Angraeng mah Judah kami Hur capa Uri, Uri capa Bezalel to ahmin hoiah kawk boeh.
\v 31 Anih to Sithaw ih Muithla, palunghahaih, panoek thaihaih hoi congca bantok sak kophaih hoiah koisak boeh.
\v 32 Anih loe sui, sui kanglung hoi sum kamling sak kophaih tok,
\v 33 thlung kangphaek aah kophaih tok, thing nuiah krang thuk kophaih tok, tok congca sak thaihaih hoiah koisak boeh.
\v 34 Dan acaeng, Ahisamak capa, Aholiab hanah to baktih sak kophaih tok hoi kami patuk kophaih to a paek let.
\v 35 Nihcae loe palunghahaih, tok congca sak kophaih, krang thuk kophaih, tlangqui kamiing, tlangqui kamling hup, tlangqui kathim, puu ngan sah kop kami ih tok, tangnaeng sak kophaih, tok congca hoi bantok sak thaihaihnawk boih to paek boeh.
\c 36
\p 
\v 1 Angraeng mah thuih ih lok baktih toengah, kaciim ahmuen ah toksak hanah, Bezalel hoi Aholiab loe Angraeng mah paek ih tok congca kasah thaih kaminawk hoi nawnto toksah hoi tih, tiah a thuih pae.
\v 2 To pacoengah Bazalel hoi Aholiab to Angraeng mah toksak thaihaih paek ih kami, toksak han palung huem kaminawk hoi nawnto Mosi mah kawk.
\v 3 Hmuenciim hoiah tok to sak hanah, Israel kaminawk mah paek o ih hmuennawk boih to Bezalel hoi Aholiab mah Mosi khaeah lak hoi. Kaminawk loe akhawnbang kruek angmacae palung angthawk baktih toengah hmuen to sin o.
\v 4 To pongah bantok sah kop kami, hmuenciim ah toksah kaminawk boih mah, angmacae toksakhaih to caeh o taak moe,
\v 5 nihcae mah Mosi khaeah, Angraeng mah toksak han thuih ih lok pong kamtlai ah, kaminawk mah hmuenmae to sin o, tiah thuih pae o.
\v 6 To pongah Mosi mah kaciim hmuen to sak hanah nongpa doeh, nongpata doeh hmuen sin han angai ai boeh, tiah a ohhhaih ahmuen boih ah taphongsak. To pongah kaminawk mah hmuen to sin o ai boeh.
\v 7 A tawnh o ih hmuennawk loe toksak haih hanah khawt amtlai boeh.
\s1 Kahni im sakhaih
\p 
\v 8 Toksah kaminawk thungah, bantok sah kop kaminawk mah puu kahni, rong kamiing, rong kamling hup, rong kathim hoi payang ih kahni hato sak o moe, to bantok sah kop kaminawk mah kahni nuiah cherubim krang to soi o.
\v 9 To ah payang ih kahninawk loe anghmong o boih; kahni loe dong pumphae, tazetto sawk moe, dong palito kawk.
\p 
\v 10 Payang ih kahni pangato to maeto ah pacong moe, kalah pangato doeh maeto ah pacong let.
\v 11 Payang ih kahni atom ah kahni maeto hoi maeto pacong naah patoh hanah, rong kamiing hoiah kangbuet luet akhaw to a sak, kalah kahni atom pongah doeh to tiah a sak boih.
\v 12 To pacoengah payang ih kahni maeto atom ah kangbuet luet akhaw qui pangato a sak; maeto hoi maeto pacong thai hanah, kalah maeto kahni atom ah doeh akhaw qui pangato a sak let bae.
\v 13 Sui hoiah Kahni maeto hoi maeto paconghaih kangbuet luet akhaw qui pangato a sak moe, kahni to pacong naah kahni im maeto ah angcoeng.
\p 
\v 14 Kahni im ranuih to khuk hanah, payang ih kahni to maeh mui hoiah a sak; payang ih kahni hathlaito a sak.
\v 15 To ah payang ih kahni hathlaito loe anghmong o boih; dong qui thumto sawk moe, dong palito kawk.
\v 16 Payang ih kahni pangato loe maeto ah pacong moe, kalah kahni tarukto doeh maeto ah pacong let.
\v 17 To pacoengah payang ih kahni aqai ah kangbuet luet akhaw qui pangato a sak moe, kalah kahni maeto pongah doeh kangbuet luet akhaw qui pangato a sak let.
\v 18 Kahni im maeto ah pacong hanah, sum kamling hoiah kangbuet luet akhaw qui pangato a sak let.
\v 19 Kahni im ranuih to khuk hanah, rong kathim nok ih tuu tae ahin, to tuu tae ahin ranuih to khuk hanah caham hin to a sak.
\p 
\v 20 Kahni im tapang to shittim thing hoiah a sak.
\v 21 Tapang thingphaek loe dong hato sawk moe, dong maeto pacoeng, ahap len.
\v 22 Thingphaek loe hae bangah akhok maeto, ho bang ah akhok maeto, kangvan ah a sak; to tiah kahni im sakhaih thingphaek nuiah a sak boih.
\v 23 Kahni im aloih bang pakaa hanah, thingphaek pumphaeto a sak moe,
\v 24 thingphaek pumphaeto pongah akhok pahnuthaih kangbuet luet akhaw qui palito sum kanglung hoiah a sak; thingphaek maeto tlim ah akhok hnetto, a khok pahnuthaih akhaw hnetto oh; kalah thingphaek pongah doeh to tiah oh boih.
\v 25 To tiah kahni im aluek bang pakaa hanah thingphaek pumphaeto a sak.
\v 26 Thingphaek maeto pongah akhok pahnuthaih akhaw qui palito sak moe, thingphaek maeto tlim ah akhok hnetto a sak, to tiah kalah thingphaek maeto pongah doeh a sak.
\v 27 Kahni im hnukbang pakaa hanah thingphaek tarukto a sak.
\v 28 Kahni im takii hnetto ah thingphaek hnetto a sak boih.
\v 29 To im takii hnetto pakaahaih thingphaek hnetto, takung hoi tadong paconghaih to a sak moe, aqai paconghaih akhaw maeto pongah caehsak hmaek; to tiah im takii hnetto ah a sak boih.
\v 30 To ah thingphaek tazetto oh moe, sum kanglung hoi sak ih akhok pahnuthaih akhaw hathlai tarukto oh; thingphaek maeto tlim ah akhok pahnuthaih hnetto oh boih.
\p 
\v 31 To pacoengah kahni im takraenghaih to shittim thing hoiah a sak; kahni im hmaa maeto takraeng hanah takraenghaih thing pangato,
\v 32 kahni im maeto bang ih thingphaek takraenghaih thing pangato, a hnukbang ih thingphaek takraeng hanah takraenghaih thing pangato a sak let.
\v 33 A um takraeng haih hanah, hae bang hoi ho bang khoek to kapha thing to a sak.
\v 34 Thingphaek boih sui tui pazut moe, takraenghaih thing qukhaih akhaw doeh sui hoiah a sak; takraenghaih thing doeh sui tui pazut boih.
\p 
\v 35 Payang ih kahni to rong kamiing, rong kamling hup, rong kathim puu ngan hoiah a sak moe, bantok sah kop kaminawk mah a nuiah cherubim krang to soi o.
\v 36 Shittim thing hoiah kahni payanghaih tung palito a sak moe, sui tui pazut boih; tung pongah banghhaih cakoih baktih kaom sum doeh sui hoiah a sak, akhok pahnuthaih akhaw palito loe sum kanglung hoiah a sak.
\v 37 Kahni im akunhaih thok taengah payang hanah, kahni sah kop kaminawk mah, kahni to rong kamiing, rong kamling hup, rong kathim puu ngan hoiah sak o;
\v 38 tung pangato pongah cakoih baktih kaom sumnawk to a sak moe, tung ranuih hoi tungnawk to sui tui hoiah pazut boih; toe akhok pahnuthaih akhaw pangato loe sum kamling hoiah ni a sak.
\c 37
\s1 Lokkamhaih thingkhong
\p 
\v 1 Bazalel mah lokkamhaih thingkhong to shittim thing hoiah sak; to thingkhong loe dong hnetto pacoeng, ahap sawk, dongto pacoeng, ahap kawk moe, dongto pacoeng, ahap sang.
\v 2 Anih mah to thingkhong nui hoi athung boih, kaciim sui tui hoiah pazut moe, aqai to sui hoiah a sak boih.
\v 3 Sui hoiah kangbuet luet akhaw palito a sak moe, thingkhong taki maeto ah akhaw hnetto a suek, to tiah taki palito ah akhaw to sak boih.
\v 4 To pacoengah aputhaih thing to shittim thing hoiah a sak moe, sui tui pazut boih.
\v 5 To thingkhong to aput hanah, hae bang ih akhaw hoi ho bang ih akhaw thungah thing to a hawt.
\v 6 Palungnathaih tangkhang loe kaciim sui hoiah a sak; dong hnetto pacoeng, ahap sawk moe, dongto pacoeng, ahap kawk.
\v 7 To pacoengah palungnathaih tangkhang nui aqai kangtaeng hnetto ah, daengh ih sui hoiah cherubim krang hnetto a sak;
\v 8 hae bang aqai kangtaeng ah cherub maeto, ho bang ih aqai kangtaeng ah cherub maeto a sak moe, palungnathaih tangkhang hoi aqai hnetto ah cherubim krang to a sak.
\v 9 Cherubim hnik loe van bangah pakhraeh phok hoi tahang moe, palungnathaih tangkhang to a khuk hoi, mikhmai kangtong ah a oh hoi moe, palungnathaih tangkhang to khet hoi tathuk.
\s1 Caboi
\p 
\v 10 Shittim thing hoiah caboi to a sak; dong hnetto sawk, dongto kawk moe, dongto pacoeng, ahap sang.
\v 11 Caboi to kaciim sui tui hoiah pazut moe, aqai to sui hoiah a sak boih.
\v 12 Aqai to ban tamsum maeto kakawk ah a sak moe, aqai boih sui hoiah a sak.
\v 13 To caboi pongah akhaw palito sui hoiah a sak moe, a khok palito ranuih, caboi takii palito ah a suek.
\v 14 Sui hoi sak ih akhawnawk loe caboi nuiah oh moe, caboi aputhaih thing hawthaih ahmuen ah oh.
\v 15 Caboi aputhaih loe shittim thing hoiah a sak moe, sui tui to pazut.
\v 16 To caboi nui ih sabaenawk, kathlahnawk, sabae thuknawk hoi tui lawnhaih hmuennawk loe sui hoiah a sak boih.
\s1 Hmaithawk paanghaih tung
\p 
\v 17 Hmaithawk paanghaih tung doeh kaciim sui, daengh ih sui hoiah a sak; tungnawk, tanghangnawk, boengloengnawk, apawk tangmuem hoi kanghmong krangnawk hoi apawknawk doeh to tiah a sak boih;
\v 18 hmaithawk paanghaih tung hoiah loe tanghang tarukto tacawt; hae bangah thumto, ho bang ah doeh thumto tacawt.
\v 19 Tanghang maeto pongah almond thaih, apawk tangmuem, apawk hoi kanghmong boengloeng thumto oh moe, kalah tanghang thumto pongah doeh, to baktih krangnawk to oh boih toeng; to tiah tung maeto pongah tanghang tarukto tacawt.
\v 20 Hmaithawk paanghaih tung pongah loe, almond thaih, apawk tangmuem hoi apawk baktih kaom, boengloeng palito oh.
\v 21 Hmai paanghaih tung maeto pongah, tanghang tarukto tacawt, tanghang hnetto atlim ah loe apawk tangmuem baktih kaom maeto oh, to tiah hnetto haih hoi thumto haih pongah doeh oh boih.
\v 22 Apawk tangmuem hoi tanghangnawk loe, hmai paanghaih tung maeto ah oh o boih moe, sui hoiah a sak boih.
\v 23 Hmaiim to sarihto ah a sak, taitaeh hoi maiphu suekhaih sabaenawk doeh sui hoiah a sak boih.
\v 24 Hmai paanghaih tung hoi hmuennawk boih loe sui talent maeto hoiah a sak.
\s1 Hmuihoih thlaekhaih hmaicam
\p 
\v 25 Hmuihoih thlaekhaih hmaicam loe shittim thing hoiah a sak; dongto sawk, dongto kawk moe, dong hnetto sang; takinawk doeh shittim thing hoiah a sak boih.
\v 26 Hmaicam ranuih, tapang, takinawk to kaciim sui tui hoiah a sak moe, aqainawk doeh sui tui hoiah pazut boih.
\v 27 Hmaicam aqai atlim ah hae bangah maeto, ho bang ah maeto, akhaw hnetto sui hoiah a sak; akhaw loe hmaicam aputhaih thing hawt hanah a sak.
\v 28 Hmaicam aputhaih thing loe, shittim thing hoiah a sak moe, sui tui pazut boih.
\v 29 \x - \xo 37:29 \xt EXO 30.22-38.\x*To pacoengah hmuihoih sah kop kaminawk mah hmuihoih to sak o baktih toengah, tak angnokhaih kaciim situi hoi hmaithlaek hanah kaciim hmuihoih to doeh a sak.
\c 38
\s1 Angbawnhaih hmaicam
\p 
\v 1 Angbawnhaih hmaicam to shittim thing hoiah a sak, hmaicam loe taki palito oh; dong pangato sawk, dong pangato kawk moe, dong thumto sang.
\v 2 Hmaicam taki palito nuiah takii maeto a sak boih; takiinawk doeh shittim thing hoiah a sak moe, sum kamling tui to pazut boih.
\v 3 Hmaicam nui ih laomnawk, maiphu sohhaihnawk, tui bawhhaih boengloengnawk, moi thunhaih cakoih baktih kaom sumnawk, sabaenawk hoi hmuennawk boih loe sum kamling hoiah a sak.
\v 4 Hmaicam ih vaizoek to sum kamling hoiah a sak moe, hmaicam tlim a um ah a suek.
\v 5 Sum kamling vaizoek ih taki palito pongah aputhaih thing to hawt hanah, sum kamling akhawnawk to a sak.
\v 6 Aputhaih thing to shittim thing hoiah a sak moe, sum kamling tui to pazut.
\v 7 Aputhaih thing to hmaicam aqai ih akhaw thungah a hawt; to hmaicam to ranuih hoi atlim akhaw taqawt hanah thingphaek hoiah a sak.
\s1 Pasaehhaih sabae kathuk
\p 
\v 8 \x - \xo 38:8 \xt EXO 30.18.\x*Amkhuenghaih kahni im akunhaih thok taengah kamkhueng nongpatanawk mah patoh ih sum kamling hoi sak ih hmaidan to a lak moe, amsaehhaih sabae kathuk hoi angdoethaih akhok to a sak.
\s1 Kahni im longhmaa
\p 
\v 9 To pacoengah longhmaa to a sak; aloih bang longhma pakaa hanah dong cumvaito kasawk payang ih kahni to puu tlangqui hoiah a sak.
\v 10 Tung pumphaeto oh moe, sum kamling hoi sak ih akhok pahnuthaih akhaw doeh pumphaeto oh; toe tung pong ih cakoih baktih kaom sumnawk hoi cungnawk loe sum kanglung hoiah a sak.
\v 11 Longhmaa aluek bang doeh dong cumvaito kasawk payang ih kahni hoi tung pumphaeto oh moe, sum kamling hoiah sak ih akhok pahnuthaih akhaw doeh pumphaeto oh; tungnawk pong ih cakoih baktih kaom sumnawk hoi cungnawk loe sum kanglung hoiah a sak.
\v 12 Niduem bangah loe dong qui pangato kasawk payang ih kahni to oh; tung hato oh moe, akhok pahnuthaih akhaw hato oh; tungnawk pong ih cakoih baktih kaom sumnawk hoi cungnawk loe sum kanglung hoiah a sak.
\v 13 Ni angyae bangah doeh dong qui pangato oh.
\v 14 Akunhaih khongkha maeto bang pakaa hanah dong hathlai pangato kasawk payang ih kahni to oh moe, tung thumto pacoengah, akhok pahnuthaih akhaw thumto doeh oh.
\v 15 Khongkha hae bang hoi ho bang to pakaa hanah, dong hathlai pangato kasawk payang ih kahni to oh moe, tung thumto hoi akhok pahnuthaih akhaw thumto doeh oh.
\v 16 Longhma kangkui ah payang ih kahninawk loe, puu ngan tlangqui hoiah a sak boih.
\v 17 Tungnawk pahnuthaih akhaw loe, sum kamling hoiah a sak; tungnawk pong ih cakoih baktih kaom sumnawk hoi cungnawk loe sum kanglung hoiah a sak; tung ranuih loe sum kanglung hoiah a sak boih; longhmaa ih tungnawk boih doeh sum kanglung hoiah a sak.
\v 18 Longhmaa akunhaih khongkha taengah payang ih kahni loe, rong kamiing, rong kamling hup, rong kathim puu ngan hoiah a sak; kahni sah kop kaminawk mah a sak o; kahni loe dong pumphaeto sawk moe, longhmaa ah payang ih kahni baktih toengah, dong pangato sang.
\v 19 Tung palito oh moe, sum kamling hoi sak ih a khok pahnuthaih akhaw palito oh; tungnawk pong ih cakoih baktih kaom sumnawk hoi cungnawk loe sum kanglung hoiah a sak moe, tung ranuih to sui tui hoiah pazut.
\v 20 Longhmaa taeng boih ih takhinghaih sumnawk loe sum kamling hoiah a sak boih.
\s1 Kahni imsakhaih hmuenmaenawk
\p 
\v 21 Hae loe Mosi mah thuih ih lok baktih toengah, qaima Aaron ih capa Ithmar zaehhoihaih thungah, Levi kaminawk mah tarik ih kahni im, hnukung kahni im sak naah patoh ih hmuennawk ah oh.
\v 22 Judah acaeng Hur capa Uri, Uri capa Bazalel loe, Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah thuih pae ih loknawk baktih toengah a sak.
\v 23 Anih hoi nawnto toksah kami, Dan acaeng Ahisamak capa Aholiab loe, ban hoiah daengh moe, krang soi thaihaih tok, bantok congca sah kop kami, tlangqui kamiing, tlangqui kamling hup, tlangqui kathim puu ngan nuiah a aem takaekhaih sah kop kami ah oh.
\v 24 Hmuenciim sak naah patoh han paek o ih suinawk boih loe, hmuenciim ih shekel tahhaih hoiah tah naah, talent pumphae takawtto hoi shekel cumvai sarih, qui thumto oh.
\v 25 \x - \xo 38:25 \xt EXO 30.11-16.\x*Kroek ih rangpui kaminawk mah paek o ih sum kanglung loe, hmuenciim ih shekel tahhaih hoiah tah naah, talent cumvaito oh, shekel ah tah naah loe sang cumvai sarih, qui sarih, pangato oh.
\v 26 \x - \xo 38:26 \xt Mathai 17.24.\x*Milu kroek tangcae, saning pumphaeto hoi ranuih bang kami boih mah, hmuenciim ih shekel tahhaih pongah, bekah maeto pacoeng, shekel ahap paek o boih, saning pumphae ranuih nongpa boih kami sang cumvai taruk, sang thum, cumvai pangato pacoeng, qui pangato oh o.
\v 27 Hmuenciim akhok pahnuthaih ahmuen hoi payang ih kahni tung pahnuthaih ahmuen to sak hanah, sum kanglung talent cumvaito patoh; akhok pahnuthaih maeto naah talent maeto, akhok pahnuthaih cumvaito hanah talent cumvaito patoh.
\v 28 Shekel sang, cumvai sarih, qui sarih, pangato loe, tung pong ih cakoih baktih kaom sumnawk hoi cungnawk to sak hanah patoh moe, tung ranuih to kahoih ah a pathoep.
\v 29 Paek o ih sum kamling loe, talent qui sarihto oh moe, shekel sang hnet, cumvai palito oh.
\v 30 Sum kamling loe kami amkhuenghaih kahni im thok tung pahnuthaih akhaw, sum kamling hmaicam, sum kamling vaizoek hoi hmaicam ah patoh ih hmuennawk boih sak naah patoh.
\v 31 Longhmaa pakaahaih tung pahnuthaih akhawnawk, longhmaa ih khongkha tung pahnuthaih akhawnawk, kahni im taeng boih takhuekhaih sumnawk hoi longhmaa kangkui ah takhuekhaih sumnawk boih sak haih hanah doeh patoh.
\c 39
\s1 Qaima ih aphaw
\p 
\v 1 Hmuenciim ah toksak hanah, tlangqui kamiing, tlangqui kamling hup, tlangqui kathim hoi laihaw to a sak o; Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah thuih ih lok baktih toengah, Aaron han kaciim laihaw to sak pae o.
\s1 Palaeng ah avak ih kahni
\p 
\v 2 Palaeng ah avak ih kahni loe sui, rong kamiing, rong kamling hup, rong kathim puu ngan hoiah a sak.
\v 3 Sui to kangphaek daek ah daengh o moe, sui to aqui ah aah pacoengah rong kamiing, rong kamling hup, rong kathim puu ngan pongah a bet o.
\v 4 Palaeng ah avak hanah kahni to sak pae o moe, atom hnetto pacong pae o pacoengah nawnto huih pae o.
\v 5 Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah thuih pae ih lok baktih toengah, kahni sah kop kaminawk mah sak ih kaeng zaenghaih kazii doeh, kahni baktih toengah palaeng ah avak ih kahni nuiah sui to bet o moe, rong kamiing, rong kamling hup, rong kathim puu ngan hoiah a sak o.
\p 
\v 6 Onyx thlung to sak o moe, sui thungah bet o; bantuek nuiah ca tarik ih baktih toengah, Israel caanawk angmathaih ahmin to tarik o.
\v 7 Angraeng mah thuih ih lok baktih toengah, Israel caanawk to panoek poe hanah, palaeng hnetto nuiah avak ih kahni pongah bet o.
\s1 Qaima saoek khukhaih kahni
\p 
\v 8 Kaahni to sui, rong kamiing, rong kamling hup, rong kathim puu ngan hoiah a sak o baktih toengah, saoep khukhaih kahni doeh kahoih ah a sak o.
\v 9 Saoek khukhaih kahni loe hnetto ah pakhraep o; karto sawk moe, karto kawk; ahnuk ahmaa kangvan taki palito oh.
\v 10 To saoek khukhaih kahni nuiah ahmuen palito kangphaeng ah thlung to bet o; ahmuen maeto pongah sardium thlung, topaz thlung, beryl thlung to a bet o.
\v 11 Ahmuen hnetto haih pongah loe emerald thlung, sapphir thlung hoi diamond to a bet o.
\v 12 Ahmuen thumto haih pongah loe, Jacin, anagate hoi amethi thlung to bet o.
\v 13 Ahmuen palito pongah loe beryl, onyx hoi jasper thlungnawk to bet o; to thlungnawk loe sui hoi kacakah bet o boih.
\v 14 Bantuek nuiah ahmin tarik ih baktih toengah, to thlungnawk nuiah doeh Israel acaeng hathlai hnetto ahmin to tarik o; thlung maeto nuiah ahmin maeto, thlung hathlai hnetto nuiah acaeng hathlai hnetto ahmin to tarik o boih.
\v 15 Saoek khukhaih kahni nui ih aqai ah kaciim sui qui to zaeng o.
\v 16 Sui hoi sak ih apawk kaom suiqui hnetto, sui hoi sak ih kangbuet luet akhaw hnetto doeh a sak o moe, kangbuet luet hnetto loe saoek khukhaih kahni aqai ah bangh o.
\v 17 Aqai kangtaeng koek saoek padaphaih nui ih akhaw kangbuet luet hnetto thungah pakhui ih sui qui hnetto a suek o.
\v 18 Aqai ah bangh ih suiqui loe sui hoi sak ih apawk kaom suiqui pongah pathlet o moe, palaeng avak ih kahni hmaa bangah bang o.
\v 19 Sui hoiah kangbuet luet akhaw hnetto sak o moe, kahni tlim ah kaom, palaeng ah avak ih kahni aqai hnetto ah a suek o.
\v 20 Kalah kangbuet luet akhaw hnetto sui hoiah sak o let moe, hmaa bangah avak ih kahni tlim hoi kaengkaeh zaenghaih ranuih paconghaih ahmuen, kahni aqai hnetto ah suek o.
\v 21 Saoek khukhaih palaeng ah avak ih kahni nui ih sui hoi sak ih kangbuet luet hnetto loe, kahni nuiah kaom sui hoi sak ih kangbuet luet hnetto hoi nawnto pacong o moe, rong kamiing qui hoiah pathlet o; Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah thuih pae ih lok baktih toengah, saoek khukhaih avak ih kahni loe, kahni hoi amhoesak han om ai pongah, kaengkaeh zaenghaih kazii ranuih ah suek o.
\s1 Kalah qaima kahni
\p 
\v 22 Palaeng avak ih kahni loe kahni sah kop kami mah, rong kamiing hoiah a sak.
\v 23 Kahni loe lu hawthaih akhaw to oh moe, to akhaw to angsih han ai ah, a taeng boih to a huih.
\v 24 To pacoengah atom ah rong kamiing, rong kamling hup, rong kathim puu ngan hoiah sak ih, pomegranat thingthai krang to a bet thuih.
\v 25 Kaciim sui hoiah dar krangnawk to a sak moe, kahni atom ih pomegranat thaih salakah a bet.
\v 26 Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah thuih ih lok baktih toengah, toksakhaih kahni loe, kahni atom kangkui ah dar krang maeto pacoengah, Pomegranat thaih maeto, dar krang maeto pacoengah, pomegranat maeto, tiah a sak.
\v 27 Aaron hoi a caanawk hanah doeh, a nuiah angkhuk ih laihaw kalen to puu ngan hoiah a sak pae,
\v 28 to pacoengah kahoih puu ngan hoiah sak ih lumuek to a sak pae, kahoih puu ngan hoiah sak ih lu zaenghaih a sak pae moe, a thung ih canghnawh doeh kahoih puu ngan hoiah a sak pae.
\v 29 Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah thuih ih lok baktih toengah, kaeng ah zaeng ih kazii doeh rong kamiing, rong kamling hup, rong kathim puu ngan hoiah a aem sah thaih kami mah a sak pae.
\v 30 Sabae hoi kaciim lumuek to kaciim sui tui hoiah a sak; bantuek nuiah tarik ih ca baktih toengah, a nuiah ca tarik o; ANGRAENG HAN CIIMCAIHAIH, tiah tarik o.
\v 31 Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah thuih ih lok baktih toengah, rong kamiing hoiah lumuek to pathlet o.
\s1 Kahni im sak pacoenghaih
\p 
\v 32 To tiah kaminawk amkhuenghaih kahni im toksakhaih to pacoeng o boih; Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah thuih ih lok baktih toengah, Israel kaminawk boih mah a sak o.
\v 33 To pacoengah Israel kaminawk mah, kahni im, im sakhaih hmuennawk boih, sui hoi sak ih kangbuet luet akhawnawk, thingphaeknawk, takraenghaih thingnawk, tungnawk hoi tung pahnuthaih akhawnawk,
\v 34 khuk hanah kathim rong tui nup ih tuu tae ahinnawk, khukhaih caham hinnawk hoi payang ih kahninawk,
\v 35 hnukung ah kaom thingkhong, thingkhong aputhaih thing hoi palungnathaih tangkhang khukhaih,
\v 36 caboi hoi caboi nui ih hmuennawk boih, hmaa bangah suek ih takaw,
\v 37 kaciim hmaithawk paanghaih tungnawk, hmaiimnawk, to ah kaom hmuennawk boih, hmai paanghaih situi,
\v 38 sui hoi sak ih hmaicam, tak bawhhaih situi, hmaithlaek han ih hmuihoih, kahni im akunhaih thok taengah payang ih kahni,
\v 39 sum kamling hoi sak ih hmaicam, sum kamling hoi sak ih vaizoek, aputhaih thingnawk hoi hmuennawk boih,
\v 40 longhma ah payang ih kahninawk, tungnawk, khok pahnuthaih akhawnawk, longhma akunhaih khongkha taengah payang ih kahni, quinawk hoi takhuekhaih sumnawk, kahni im sak naah patoh ih hmuennawk boih, kaminawk amkhuenghaih kahni im,
\v 41 hmuenciim ah toksak naah angkhuk han ih laihawnawk, qaima tok to sak hanah, qaima Aaron hoi a caanawk hanah kaciim laihawnawk to sak o moe, Mosi khaeah a sin pae o.
\v 42 Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah thuih pae ih lok baktih toengah, Israel kaminawk mah tok to sak o boih.
\v 43 Mosi mah toksakhaih to khet naah, nihcae loe Angraeng mah thuih ih lok baktih toengah, toksak pacoeng o boeh, tiah a hnuk; to pongah Mosi mah nihcae to tahamhoihaih paek.
\c 40
\s1 Kahni im sakhaih
\p 
\v 1 To pacoengah Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah,
\v 2 Kaminawk amkhuenghaih kahni im to, khrah hmaloe koek, ni tangsuek naah sah ah.
\v 3 Hnukung thingkhong loe, to kahni imthung ah suem ah, to thingkhong loe payang ih kahni hoiah khuk ah.
\v 4 A thungah caboi suem ah loe, hmuennawk boih caboi nuiah suem ah; to pacoengah hmaithawk paanghaih tung to suem ah loe, hmai to paaang ah.
\v 5 Hmuihoih thlaekhaih hmaicam to hnukung thingkhong hmaa ah suem ah loe, kahni im akunhaih khongkha ah payang ih kahni hoiah pakaa ah.
\v 6 Amkhuenghaih kahni im akunhaih khongkha hmaa ah, hmai angbawnhaih hmaicam to suem ah.
\v 7 Kaminawk amkhuenghaih kahni im hoi hmaicam salakah sabae kathuk to suem ah loe, a thungah tui to lawn ah.
\v 8 Longhma taeng to paka boih ah loe, longhma akunhaih khongkha taengah kahni to payang ah.
\v 9 Tak bawhhaih situi to la ah loe, kahni im hoi a thungah kaom hmuennawk to nok boih ah; to ih hmuennawk to ciimsak boih ah, to tiah ni kahni im to ciim vop tih.
\v 10 To pacoengah hmai angbawnhaih hmaicam hoi hmuennawk to situi nok boih ah loe, hmaicam to ciimsak ah; to tiah ni kaciim koek hmaicam ah om tih.
\v 11 Kathuk sabae hoi pahnuthaih a khok to situi nok ah loe, ciimsak ah.
\v 12 Aaron hoi a caanawk to amkhuenghaih kahni im khongkha ah caehhaih ah loe, tui amhlusak ah.
\v 13 Aaron hanah kaciim kahni to angkhuksak ah, qaima toksak thai hanah, situi to nok ah loe ciimsak ah.
\v 14 Anih ih caanawk to angzo haih ah loe, laihaw kasawk to angkhuksak ah.
\v 15 Kai khaeah qaima tok a sak o thai hanah, ampa situi hoi na bawh baktih toengah, a caanawk doeh bawh ah; a caanawk dung khoek to qaima ah oh poe han ih ni nihcae to situi hoiah na bawh, tiah a naa.
\p 
\v 16 Angraeng mah thuih ih lok baktih toengah, Mosi mah hmuennawk to sak boih.
\v 17 To pongah saning hnetto haih, khrah tangsuek, ni hmaloe koek ah, Mosi mah kahni im to a sak.
\v 18 Mosi mah kahni im sak naah, akhok pahnuthaih hmuennawk to kacakah a sak, thingphaeknawk to a sak moe, takraenghaih thingnawk to sak pacoengah, tungnawk to a sak.
\v 19 To pacoengah kahni im to payuengh moe, Angraeng mah thuih ih lok baktih toengah, kani im ranuih to a khuk.
\v 20 Hnukung thingkhong to a lak moe, to thingkhong nuiah aputhaih thing to a hawt pacoengah, palungnathaih tangkhang to a nuiah suek.
\v 21 Thingkhong to kahni imthung ah a sin moe, Angraeng mah thuih ih lok baktih toengah, hnukung thingkhong to payang ih kahni hoiah a khuk.
\v 22 Mosi mah caboi to amkhuenghaih kahni imthung aluek bang, payang ih kahni tasa bangah a suek.
\v 23 Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah thuih ih lok baktih toengah, Angraeng hmaa ah takaw to a suek pae.
\v 24 Hmaithawk paaanghaih tung doeh kahni imthung, kahni im aloih bang ah a suek.
\v 25 Angraeng mah thuih ih lok baktih toengah, Angraeng hmaa ah hmaiim to paaang.
\v 26 Mosi mah sui hmaicam to amkhuenghaih kahni imthung, payang ih kahni hmaa ah a suek.
\v 27 Angraeng mah thuih ih lok baktih toengah, to ah hmuihoih to a thlaek.
\v 28 To pacoengah kahni im akunhaih thok taengah kahni to payang.
\v 29 Kaminawk amkhuenghaih kahni im akunhaih thok taengah hmai angbawnhaih hmacam to a suek moe, Angraeng mah thuih ih lok baktih toengah, to hmaicam nuiah hmai angbawnhaih hoi cang angbawnhaih to a sak.
\v 30 Amkhuenghaih kahni im hoi hmaicam salakah, sabae kathuk to a suek moe, amsaehhaih tui to a lawn.
\v 31 Mosi, Aaron hoi a caanawk loe to ih tui hoiah khok bannawk to amsaeh o;
\v 32 amkhuenghaih kahni imthung ah akun o moe, hmaicam taengah a caeh o naah, Angraeng mah Mosi khaeah thuih ih lok baktih toengah, nihcae loe tui hoiah amsaeh o.
\v 33 To pacoengah Mosi mah hmaicam hoi longhma pakaahaih kahni to payang; longhma akunhaih khongkha taengah kahni to payang. To tiah Mosi mah toksakhaih to pacoeng.
\s1 Angraeng lensawkhaih
\p 
\v 34 \x - \xo 40:34 \xt 1 Siang 8.10,11; Isaiah 6.4; Ezek 43.4,5; Lph 15.8.\x*To naah amkhuenghaih kahni im to tamai mah khuk, kahni im loe Angraeng lensawkhaih hoiah koi.
\v 35 Amkhuenghaih kahni im to tamai mah khuk khoep pongah, Mosi loe kahni imthung ah akun thai ai; to naah kahni im loe Angraeng lensawkhaih hoiah koi.
\v 36 Israel kaminawk kholong caeh o naah, kahni im nui hoiah tamai angkhoeng pacoengah ni a caeh o vop;
\v 37 tamai angkhoeng tahang ai nahaeloe, tamai angkhoeng tahang ai karoek to, kholong caeh o ai.
\v 38 Israel kaminawk kholong caeh o nathung, nihcae boih mikhnuk ah, athun naah Angraeng ih tamai to kahni im nuiah oh, khoving naah loe tamai nuiah hmai to oh. 
